\id LUK - KAPIN, Itama draft, Yandabing, Roy
\h Lukas
\toc3 Luk
\toc2 Lukas
\toc1 Xoulek Nimza wei Lukas byex o
\mt2 Xoulek Nimza wei
\mt1 Lukas
\mt2 byex o
\imt1 Qayeeng wei la tax o
\ip Eivek Xoulek Nimza wei Lukas byex eno xey a xei Yesu e tambiy wei qou xel Israel loumelam o me xel amba is ambei nyon. Gyeik ingwei Yesu embei bong e xe xuk, eno neil wou moux alis vex bei, Laweeng Vambuing zeim e lalei lek bei e neil Anutu xe qayeeng nimza wou xel kanyo (wei 4.18). Me zonghek ayang, eivek qapiya tine eno Lukas tul pavulek ngenong en xel wei qalei nimaying leimalei me e wo nimza wou xel o. Lulul wei Yesu wong, eno wong xel wei e yo wo xeind lala en e. Gyeik ingwei Maria wou e eno xomaxoneing wo xeind lala (wei 1.42-48 me 2.10,) me ingwei qapiya la tip lek, gyeik ingwei Yesu lek me la tyoung gheyapu eno xel wo xeind lala ngandoung (wei 24.52).
\ip Lulul ngenong wei mapieing wei Yesu eno Lukas tixemou tul pavulek en. Qayeeng wei lulul on eno se di yeip eivek qapiya bamba. Lukas venaxow tul pavulek en lulul ngenong qandi gyeik ingwei Yesu lam lek tembuing o. Lukas venaxow byex qayeeng pakeing en ingwei tambiy wei Samaria yo ti vind tambiy wei xel leis wou sakwaing o, me qayeeng pakeing tul pavulek en ingwei yak ti la veil ma me mi loung la yo, me Yesu xe qayeeng pakeing valu is. Lukas venaxow tul pavulek en lul wei qandi wou Sakius o, tambiy tiwei mi qou takis o.
\ip Lulul valu eno Lukas luk ngenong en, inye kwa wei zeimeing mema nikanzek o, me xuk wei Laweeng Vambuing o, me kwa wei Anutu mi semaleeng sewokeing wei xomaxoneing o. Lukas neil qayeeng ngenong is en lulul wei vex vex mi wong o.
\ip Qayeeng wei Lukas eno se la tip lek qapiya tine. Ma. Lukas venaxow byex qapiya tiwei xey a neimbei Xuk Sinale yo. Inyon qapiya wei tul pavulek en lulul wei xel sinale wong gyeik ingwei Yesu lek me la tyoung gheyapu yo.
\c 1
\s1 Lukas byex pavulek ne wou Tiopilas
\p 
\v 1 O lei ngandoung Tiopilas, xel ngenong mi byex pavulek lek vatiyeiw wei Anutu wong ela teyei lek eivek xa senghoing o.
\v 2 Xel betiwou eti yeiw wei yei lulul on lek mend atax, gyeik ingwei lulul on qandi lek o. Me xel on xukxe wei Anutu xe xoulek o. Om xel tul pavulek on wou xa.
\v 3 Om ay is ambei nyon ambei byex pavulek on me na bong e nak wou wang. A mi wong xuk endenlek telinyeing lulul on qes wo nimza, om a byex ela teyei lek ingwei lulul on qandi yo.
\v 4 Wa pyaw dom ghe boulek embo nimza bei qayeeng wei xel teyoxe wou wang on neing ayang.
\s1 Angela neil wou Sakalias bei Yoan tyek dumbek
\p 
\v 5 Eivek bouk wei Herot king wei Yudia eno lumuki ti mindei e lei Sakalias, e eivek qendu tiwei Abiya yo. Moxo venei Elisabet yon eivek velei wei Aron o.
\v 6 Luw xouing mindei ewo bombek wou Anutu manghalus. Me luw mi betiwou Tambiy Ngandoung xe petieing dalus me xoulek dalus, me sewokeing ma veil luw.
\v 7 Ekom luw neund ma, en Elisabet mi mouyeeng me luw wo teiv aluw vexta.
\p 
\v 8 Bouk ti gyeik Sakalias xe lumukiyeiw qendu tiyon la wong xuk, eno moxo la wong xuk lumuki wou Anutu manghalus is ambei nyon.
\v 9 Om xel betiwou lumukiyeiw xe kwa wei xel mi nex qakous dee me beyal e, bei ena lalei eivek Tambiy Ngandoung xe xomek vambuing me na besei da wei xeiliy.
\v 10 Gyeik bouk wei seing xound xeiliy eno lam tyip, xel dalusateiv di qekuma nanghei Anutu beeng me zeimemend anghei myayaing.
\p 
\v 11 Woyom Tambiy Ngandoung xe angela ti lam nale wou e, moxo nale wou qeind wei seing xound xeiliy eno nenya valu wei payeiv o.
\v 12 Gyeik Sakalias yei angela, eno etek me yaleeng.
\v 13 Ekom angela neil wou e, “Sakalias wa seng gwaleeng, en Anutu ngo wa xe zeimeing mema. Om veneim Elisabet tyek bou neum moux ti, me tyek wa taxe e lei Yoan.
\v 14 Tyek wang bo xeimlala ngandoung me laleim bo nimza. Me xel ngenong tyek bo xeindlala en e xe umbekeing,
\v 15 en moxo tyek bo lei ngandoung wou Tambiy Ngandoung manghalus. Moxo e se num wain o memiing wei nikanzek o. De gyeik ingwei toukami eivek ta veis eno na pup en Laweeng Vambuing.
\v 16 Moxo tyek na qou xel Israelyeiw ngenongakes me noumenam wou Tambiy Ngandoung xel xe Anutu.
\v 17 Moxo tyek na qou nikanzek wei Laweeng Vambuing o nambei Eliya wei takwei yo me natax en Tambiy Ngandoung. Moxo tyek bong mayeiw laleind pekwi nox wou neuyeiw. Me moxo tyek pepyawexe xel wei mi pyalek qayeeng o me xel a qou lupeyei nimza nambei xel wei mi betiwou sakwaing bombek o. Moxo tyek menyex wou xomaxoneing en xel gyeiwou xow en Tambiy Ngandoung nam o.”
\p 
\v 18 Sakalias teling angela bei, “Tyek a boulek inyon ambei nya? A wo teiv takwei me a veneing wo vexta is ambei nyon.”
\p 
\v 19 Angela lewexe bei, “A Gabriel. A mi nale wou Anutu manghalus, om wong a lam a luk is wang me na neil wou wang en xoulek nimza tine.
\v 20 Om ngo, gweimbeeng kane wa myam tyek na tu me tyek wa se teyei bei baluk, qe ka bouk wei lulti yon neing etyip bole en wa seng wongis a xe qayeeng. Lulti yon tyek bo neing lek e xe bouk bombek.”
\p 
\v 21 Dekalekom xomaxoneing di axe Sakalias me di wou naleind bei nambei nya ekom dei enden eivek xomek vambuing.
\v 22 Gyeik ingwei moxo lam myayaing, eno moxo se teyeimbei baluk wou xel. Om xel woulek bei mapekwi me yei lulti eivek xomek vambuing, en mi talex lulul angya mema wou xel en se teyeimbei baluk.
\p 
\v 23 Gyeik bouk wei moxo xe xuk la wou eivek, moxo lox me la beeng.
\v 24 Kalekom venei Elisabet xei qou veil me e mindei xupekeing teyei lek dentouk qes lim.
\v 25 Vexo neil embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung wong tine wou ay eivek bouk ti beimambei ne, moxo talex e xe lalei nimza me zeim a xe niyalenyeing veil eivek xomaxoneing senghoing.”
\s1 Angela neil wou Maria en Yesu xe umbekeing
\p 
\v 26 Eivek dentouk tiwei limti eno Anutu wong angela Gabriel la Nasaret inyei beyeeng ti eivek Galili.
\v 27 La wou vexawo\f + \fr 1:27 \fq vexawo: virgin (moux ti se yei)\f* wei paleveeng o ti wei xel tup qayeeng lekti bei e na wou moux ti e lei Yosep bei e dii, inyon Dawit buyeiw ti. Vexawo paleveeng on lei Maria.
\v 28 De angela la wou vexo me neil embei, “Bendiyeing vex, Anutu lalei wo nimza wou wang. Tambiy Ngandoung e toumendei is wang.”
\p 
\v 29 Maria lalei wo maying en e xe qayeeng me wounalei bei, “Qayeeng tine inye nambei nya?”
\v 30 Ekom angela neil wou vexo bei, “Maria, wa seng gwaleeng, en Anutu lalei wo nimza wou wang.
\v 31 Wei, tyek wa xeim a qou veil me wang bou neum moux ti, me wa taxe e lei Yesu.
\v 32 Tyek moxo bo lei ngandoung me tyek xel a neimbei Anutu gheyapu neu moux. De Tambiy Ngandoung Anutu tyek bong siaking wei bu Dawit xe eno wou e.
\v 33 Me tyek mendei king en xomek wei Yakop o luta, e xe tete lalei tyek se tip.”
\p 
\v 34 Maria teling wou angela bei, “Ekom inyon tyek bong ambei nya, inye a paleveeng o?”
\p 
\v 35 Angela lewexe, “Laweeng Vambuing tyek nam wou wang me Anutu gheyapu xe nikanzek tyek bo tenu zeyi wang. Om yakyeis tiwei wa being bou yon vambuing, me tyek xel a neimbei inyon Anutu Neu Moux.
\v 36 Me gweimbeeng nimpapu Elisabet tyek bou neu moux ti eivek ingwei wo vexta yo. Takwei eno xel mi neil embei mi mouyeeng ekom wo neu me dentouk qes limti la veil.
\v 37 En lulti tyek se bo pok wou Anutu.”
\p 
\v 38 Maria lewexe, “Ee, a Tambiy Ngandoung xe xukxe vexawo, om e bong wou ay ambei ingwei wang neil on.” Woyom angela la veil e.
\s1 Maria la yei Elisabet
\p 
\v 39 Lek bouk kayon eno Maria yeiwou xow me la daing eivek beyeeng ti lek lukendu wei Yudia nei.
\v 40 De vexo la eivek Sakalias beeng me la neil bendiyeing wou Elisabet.
\v 41 Gyeik ingwei Elisabet ngo Maria xe bendiyeing, eno neu vyeip eivek e veis. De Laweeng Vambuing pup Elisabet.
\v 42 Om taxe xoulekeing me neil embei: “Anutu wo mata ghanaw veil wou wang eivek vex vex senghoing, me wo mata wou yakyeis tiwei wa being bou yon!
\v 43 Ekom ay eti om lalei nimza lam wou ay? Me a xe Tambiy Ngandoung ta lam wou ay?
\v 44 Wei, gyeik ingwei a nenyang ngo wa xe bendiyeing, eno yakyeis wei tumi eivek a veis eno wo xeilala me vyeip.
\v 45 Nimza e na wou vex wei mi wongis bei vati wei Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou e, eno tyek bo neing lek!”
\s1 Maria xe lalo
\p 
\v 46 Me Maria neil ambei nye:
\q1 “A nung pieing e sanghoxe Tambiy Ngandoung
\q2 
\v 47 me axe laweeng wo xeilala en Anutu, en e axe vineing,
\q1 
\v 48 en ay eno e xe xukxe vexawo wei lei maeing
\q2 ekom yei ay me lalei pyaxow en ay.
\q1 Om ngo, gweimbeeng me e mi na eno moux alis vex dalus tyek na mi taxe bei Anutu wong mata wou ay.
\q2 
\v 49 En tambiy nikanzekta ti wong lul ngandoung tine wou ay,
\q2 e lei yon vambuing.
\q1 
\v 50 E lalei mi pyaxow en moux alis vex wei mi yaleeng en e yo,
\q2 tyek bong ambei nyon wou moux alis vex wei gweimbeeng ne yo,
\q2 me moux alis vex wei yusyus o.
\q1 
\v 51 E mema wong xuk wei nikanzek o,
\q2 xel wei mi wou naleind en xow me toxleind eno tiy xel la danghei danghei nei.
\q1 
\v 52 Moxo toung mema lek xel king lox nge xo veil xel xe siaking
\q1 de zeim xel wei leind maeing eno lek la.
\q1 
\v 53 Moxo wong lul nimzamza ngenong pup wou xel wei maxepya xel o, dom wong xel wei lulul ana eno la bandaing.
\q1 
\v 54 Moxo vind e xe xukxeyeiw wei Israel o,
\q2 en mi wounalei en e xe lalei pyaweingxow,
\q1 
\v 55 wei wong wou Apraham me e neumambu takwei takwei, nambei ingwei e neil wou xey mendyeiw o.”
\p 
\v 56 Maria la dei is Elisabet teyei lek dentouk qes yayal o xelti, dekakom lox me la beeng.
\s1 Elisabet wou Yoan Lipekeing
\p 
\v 57 Gyeik bouk la wou eivek ingwei Elisabet embei bou neu yo, om vexo wou neu moux ti.
\v 58 Xel wei Elisabet beeng qes o me nipapu wei toundei paviy e eno ngo ingwei Tambiy Ngandoung lalei pyaxow ngandoung en e yo, om xel wo xeindlala is e.
\p 
\v 59 Lek bouk lim yal eno xel lam en xel embei ghuw yak on ninavi. Me xel embei taxe e lei Sakalias, nambei ma lei.
\v 60 Ekom ta luk me neil embei, “Ma! Tyek xey a taxe e lei Yoan.”
\p 
\v 61 Xel neil wou vexo, “Eivek xel wei wang eno senghoing xelti se lei nambei nyon.”
\p 
\v 62 Woyom xel talex lek memend wou ma, me xel teling ma bei, moxo embei taxe neu lei va.
\v 63 Moxo teling wou xel en tapele, me moxo byex qayeeng bei, “E lei Yoan.” Om xel di wou naleind ngenong.
\v 64 Lutika eno Sakalias mya tax, me e ghas vevop me e luk me sanghoxe Anutu.
\v 65 Xel wei e beeng qes on yei lulti yon om xel etek me luk ngenong en, de eivek xel beyeeng lukendu wei Yudia nei eno xel tul pavulek en lulti beimambei ne dalus.
\v 66 Xel sapa wei ngo pavulek eno xel wou naleind ngenong me teling bei, “Bouk loxyus eno yak tine tyek bong nambei nya?” En Tambiy Ngandoung mema nikanzek toundei is e.
\s1 Sakalias xe lalo
\p 
\v 67 Moxo ma Sakalias pup en Laweeng Vambuing me neil qayeeng poropet bei:
\q1 
\v 68 “Xey a sanghoxe Tambiy Ngandoung, Israel xe Anutu,
\q2 en lam tul xe xomaxoneing veil nilul.
\q1 
\v 69 Moxo wong tambiy nikanzeta wei vind xey veil nilul eno ti qandi
\q2 eivek xomek wei e xe xukxe Dawit o,
\q1 
\v 70 (nambei ingwei e neil eivek e xe xel poropet vambuing myend takwei nei yo),
\q1 
\v 71 Neil embei tyek devind xe veil xel vevek ba memend
\q2 me xel wei mi yei xey a wo nol o memend is,
\q1 
\v 72 de talex e xe lalei pyaweingxow wou xe bundyeiw
\q2 me mi wounalei en e xe qayeeng vambuing wei qokatu yo,
\q1 
\v 73 de qayeeng zonghek wei neil neing wou xe bund Apraham o:
\q1 
\v 74 bei na zeim xe veil xe xe xel vevek ba memend,
\q2 me bong xey a mi bong e xe xuk de xe se ghaleeng.
\q1 
\v 75 Eivek bouk sapa wei xey a mindei mapieing eno xey a mi betiwou kwa wei vambuing o,
\q2 me sakwaing bombek wou e manghalus.
\b
\q1 
\v 76 “De wang, a neung, tyek xel taxe bei wa poropet wei Anutu gheyapu nei yo.
\q2 En tyek wang natax en Tambiy Ngandoung me menyex wou sakwaing en e,
\q1 
\v 77 de ghe bong lupeyei wou e xe xomaxoneing en ingwei embei devind xel veil nilul me semaleeng sewokeing wei xel o,
\q1 
\v 78 en nambei xe xe Anutu lalei pyaxow wo nimzayang en xey,
\q2 om wong xeiyaing ti lam nambei sayeiv qandi me lam wou xey nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\q1 
\v 79 En enam a siing lek xel wei mindei eivek mapetok ngandoung o,
\q2 me mindei eivek yalenyeing en meyeing o.
\q2 De gyeiteyei xe vaxend en xey a betiwou sakwaing wei lalei vevopeing o.”
\p 
\v 80 Me yak moxo wo teiv me Anutu xe Laweeng wong nikanzek wou e me moxo la mindei eivek tembuing bandaing, deka bouk la wou eivek woyom la talex xow wou Israelyeiw.
\c 2
\s1 Yesu umbek
\p 
\v 1 Eivek bouk tiyon eno Sisa Ogastus king wei ngandoung o wong petieing ti la me neil embei xel a qou moux alis vex dalus wei tembuing sapa wei dei xeinghembi eivek Rom eno leind eivek qapiya.
\v 2 (Inye myaxeeng selis wei xel qou xel leind gyeik ingwei Kwirinius wo lei ngandoung wei seyap wei Siria yo.)
\v 3 Me xel dalusateiv la venaxow bend qes bei seyap a qou xel leind.
\p 
\v 4 Yosep on neumambu wei king Dawit o. Om la veil beyeeng Nasaret eivek Galili, me lek me la Yudia, la Dawit beeng wei Betelem o.
\v 5 Moxo la inyei is Maria wei xel tup qayeeng lekti bei e mendei wou e yo bei seyap a qou luw leind, gyeik inyon eno Maria xei qou veil.
\v 6 Ka luw la toundei inyei, eno bouk la wou eivek ingwei yakyeis on embei dumbek o.
\v 7 Om vexo wou neu touk, me beliv e eivek qaeing me liw eivek manghaxo xe dipek, en xomek wei vateivek o pup zeyi xel.
\s1 Xel gyovaxa wei sipsip o me angelayeiw
\p 
\v 8 Me nanghei inyei eno xel gyovaxa wei sipsip eno valu toundei myayaing veil beyeeng, me di yeiteyei xel xe sipsip qendu ngandoung on eivek boukeing tiyon.
\v 9 Dekakom Tambiy Ngandoung xe angela ti lam wou xel, me Tambiy Ngandoung xe xeiyaing ngandoung lam siing e vivekwou xel, om xel yaleeng ngandoung.
\v 10 Ekom angela neil wou xel bei, “Xam seng gwaleeng. En a qou xoulek nimza me na lam wou xam, bei embong xomaxoneing dalus bo xeindlala ngandoung.
\v 11 Gweimbeeng kane eivek beyeeng nayak wei Dawit xe eno tambiy tiwei qou xam ghe lam veil nilul eno umbek en xam. E Kilisi\f + \fr 2:11 \fq Kilisi \ft Eivek qayeeng wei Hibru eno xel neil, Mesia. Qes, tambiy wei Anutu beyal bei e qou xomaxoneing noum o.\f* me Tambiy Ngandoung.
\v 12 Tyek xam ghe boulek dee nambei nye: Tyek xam ghe gwei yakyeis ti xel beliv eivek vetivek mati me liw eivek manghaxo xe dipek.”
\p 
\v 13 De lutika eno angela ngenongakes wei tyoung gheyapu eno lam is angela tiyon, me xel sanghoxe Anutu me neil embei,
\q1 
\v 14 “Xey a sanghoxe Anutu lei na gheyapu nei,
\q2 de nanghei tembuing eno xomaxoneing wei Anutu lalei wo nimza wou xel eno na mi mendei is laleind vevopeing.”
\s1 Xel gyovaxa wei sipsip o la yei Yesu
\p 
\v 15 Gyeik ingwei xel angela lox veil xel me la eivek tyoung gheyapu nei, eno xel gyovaxa wei sipsip o neil wouma bei, “Xey a la Betelem me na xei lul tiwei qandi nei, wei Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou xey en o.”
\p 
\v 16 Om xel la daing me la yeiwou Maria luw Yosep, me yakyeis wei di yeip eivek manghaxo xe dipek o.
\v 17 Gyeik ingwei xel yei e, eno xel neil qayeeng la wo sapa en vatiyeiw wei angela neil wou xel en yakyeis tiyon o.
\v 18 Me xel dalus wei ngo inye, eno etek en vati wei xel gyovaxa wei sipsip o neil wou xel o.
\v 19 Ekom Maria mi zeimaxoun qayeeng ti beimambei yon dalus eivek lalei me mi wounalei en.
\v 20 Xel gyovaxa wei sipsip eno lox me la me di sanghoxe Anutu me wong xeindlala en lulul dalus wei xel ngo me yei yo. Nambei kawei angela neil wou xel o.
\s1 Xel taxe Yesu lei
\p 
\v 21 Lek bouk lim yal, gyeik bouk wei xel embei ghuw yak on ninavi me taxe e lei Yesu. Lei yon angela wong gyeik ingwei se ghei mi eivek ta veis o.
\s1 Simion aluw Ana yei Yesu eivek xomek vambuing
\p 
\v 22 Gyeik bouk lam tyip en ingwei yeing wou xow bo vako wou Anutu manghalus teyei lek Mose xe petieing eno la wou eivek, om Yosep aluw Maria qou Yesu me la Yerusalem en embei na bong e na wou Tambiy Ngandoung.
\v 23 Inyon nambei xel byex eivek Tambiy Ngandoung xe petieing, “Xel yak moux sapa wei umbek atax eno xam ghe bong ena nambei vambuing wou Tambiy Ngandoung nambei e xe.”
\v 24 Me luw la sei xound nambei vati wei xel neil eivek Tambiy Ngandoung xe petieing o, “beliy yayuw o banax lingheing yayuw.”
\p 
\v 25 Gweimbeeng eivek Yerusalem eno tambiy ti mindei e lei Simion, tambiy on mindei bombek me mi wong lalo. Moxo mi axe ingwei Mesia embei bong lalei vevopeing wou Israel o, me Laweeng Vambuing mindei eivek e.
\v 26 Laweeng Vambuing talex wou e bei, tyek se mey qe ka gyei Tambiy Ngandoung xe Kilisi bole.
\v 27 Laweeng Vambuing zeim e lalei lek, me e la eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing, de Yesu ma luw ta qou e me la en embei na bong vati wou e nambei kwa wei petieing neil o.
\v 28 Me Simion qava e me sanghoxe Anutu me neil:
\q1 
\v 29 “Tambiy Ngandoung, wei ghanaw veil, nambei ingwei wang neil zonghek o, wang bong wa xe xukxe na mey eivek lalei vevopeing.
\q1 
\v 30 En a manghalus yei wa xe tambiy wei embei devind xa veil nilul o,
\q2 
\v 31 wei wang xupexe inye wou xomaxoneing dalus mend o.
\q1 
\v 32 E xeiyaing tiwei embei talex enam yanyateiv wou xel amba
\q2 de bong wa xe xel Israel leind zekna.”
\p 
\v 33 Yesu ma luw ta etek en qayeeng vati wei neil lek e yo.
\v 34 Woyom Simion wo mata wou lal me neil wou moxo ta Maria, “Yakyeis tine nambei beyaleing wei tyek bong xel ngenong detei de xel ngenong qandi lek eivek Israel, me tyek mendei nambei dee ti, wei xel ngenong tyek bo vyend wou e yo.
\v 35 En kandek xel ngenong xe laleind peyei eno tyek nam yanyateiv. De ngeyeing vevek ti tyek beum wamaxow num pieing is.”
\p 
\v 36 Nanghei inyon eno poropet vex ti e lei Ana, Penuel neu vex eivek velei wei Asal o. Vexo wo vexta, vexo mindei is leya teyei lek vakovek qes lim yuw takwei gyeik ingwei luw iima yo.
\v 37 De woyom wo vexeiv teyei lek 84 vakovek qes. Vexo se mindei veil xomek vambuing qe mi wong lalo boukeing aluw bendiyeing, me mi vambu yaeing de mi zeimema.
\v 38 Lek bouk kayon eno la paviy xel me wong dange wou Anutu me luk en yakyeis on wou xel dalus wei mi toung mend en ingwei Anutu embei tul xel Yerusalem veil nilul o.
\s1 Yosep lox me la Nasaret
\p 
\v 39 Gyeik ingwei Yosep me Maria wong lulul dalus la teyei lek petieing wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe yo, luw lox Galili me lox me la luw venaxow xe beyeeng nayak Nasaret.
\v 40 Me yakyeis on wo teiv me wo nikanzek. Moxo pup en lupeyei nimza me Anutu xe lalei xeiles toundei eivek e.
\s1 Yak ghavis Yesu la xomek vambuing
\p 
\v 41 Teyei lek vakovek qes sapa eno moxo ma luw ta mi la Yerusalem en embei na gyei mata ngandoung wei Pasova yo.
\v 42 Gyeik Yesu xe vakovek qes xoumeeng yuw, eno xel betiwou xel xe kwa me lek me la yei mata ngandoung wei Pasova yon.
\v 43 Ka bouk ngandoung wei mata dalus la veil, eno ma luw ta lox me la bend, de Yesu nanghei toundei Yerusalem, ekom luw se woulek inye.
\v 44 Luw wou naleind bei la is moux alis vex valu, xel la e teyei lek bouk ti, woyom luw yimexe e eivek nipapu me luw xe gweleeng senghoing.
\v 45 Gyeik ingwei luw se yeiwou e, luw lox me la Yerusalem en embei nox gyimexe e.
\v 46 Ka bouk yayal la veil eno luw yeiwou e nanghei tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o, toundei eivek xel putoung senghoing, di ngo xel me di wo telinyeing wou xel.
\v 47 Xel sapa wei ngo e xe qayeeng eno etek en e xe lupeyei me qayeeng bombek wei di neil elox o.
\v 48 Gyeik ingwei ma luw ta yei e, eno luw etek. Moxo ta neil wou e bei, “Touk, nambei nya wang wong ambei nyon wou uw? Uw mam laleimi wo maying en wang om uw a mi ximexe wang.”
\p 
\v 49 Moxo teling wou luw, “Nambei nya muw ghe mi wimexe ay? Muw seng woulek bei a toundei eivek mang beeng?”
\v 50 Ekom luw se woulek vati wei di neil wou luw o.
\p 
\v 51 Woyom lep me la xo Nasaret nei is luw me mi betiwou luw xe qayeeng. Ekom moxo ta mi toung lulti beimambei yon dalus eivek lalei me mi wounalei en.
\v 52 Me Yesu wo teiv is lupeyei nimza, me Anutu lalei wo nimza wou e me moux alis vex laleind wo nimza wou e is.
\c 3
\s1 Yoan Lipekeing menyex wou sakwaing
\p 
\v 1 Eivek vakovek qes 15 wei Sisa Taibilias wo king wei Rom gyeik Pontias Pailat wo lei ngandoung wei seyap wei distrik Yudia yo de Herot yeiteyei distrik Galili dom li Pilip yeiteyei distrik Itulia me Tlakonaitis, de Lisanias yeiteyei distrik Abilini.
\v 2 Gyeik ingwei Anas aluw Kaiapas wo lumuki lukanzek eno Anutu xe qayeeng lam wou Yoan wei Sakalias neu yo eivek tembuing bandaing.
\v 3 Woyom moxo la eivek tembuing danghei dalus wei toundei memiing Yorodan vivi yo, me la neil xoulek wou moux alis vex bei xel pekwi xow me zipek, en kandek Anutu semaleeng xel xe sewokeing veil.
\v 4 Lulti yon qandi nambei poropet Yesaya byex eivek qapiya yo,
\q1 “Vya taxeing ti lam eivek tembuing bandaing bei,
\q2 ‘Xam menyex wou sakwaing en Tambiy Ngandoung, xam ghe bong sakwaing embo bombek en e.
\q1 
\v 5 Xam samax manya dalus e pup
\q2 me qandax lukendu is qetyei dalus e deteina.
\q1 Sakwaing dalus wei wo xeighekeing eno embo bombek,
\q2 me sakwaing wei wo nol eno embo belin.
\q1 
\v 6 Me xel xomaxoneing dalus tyek gyei Anutu xe sakwaing wei vind xomaxoneing veil nilul o.’” \rq Yesaya 40:3-5\rq*
\p 
\v 7 Yoan neil wou xel qendu ngandoung wei lam bei e zipek xel o, “Xam on myeiy nilul neu xam. Eti peti xam bei tyek xam a pek veil Anutu xe lalei vanei?
\v 8 Xam ghe buk neing me talex bei xam ghe pekwi xow, me xam se neil wou ma bei xa bumi Apraham. En a neil wou xam bei, Anutu teyeimbei neil me qakous ti beimambei ne bong ambei Apraham neuyeiw.
\v 9 Qov di yeip woy wou xax qes, me xax dalus wei se vuk neing nimza, eno tyek buv veil de banex ena eivek nenyex.”
\p 
\v 10 Xel moux alis vex ngenong teling bei, “Om tyek xa bong ambei nya?”
\p 
\v 11 Om Yoan neil elox wou xel bei, “Tambiy ti xe teimb yayuw toundei ond e bong nge wou tambiy wei ning teimb ma yo, de xelti xe yaeing toundei wou e ond e bong ambei nyon.”
\p 
\v 12 Xel wei mi qou takis, eno valu lam is ambei nyon en embei nam zipek, om xel teling wou bei, “Putoung, tyek xa bong ambei nya?”
\p 
\v 13 Moxo neil wou xel bei, “Xam a qou takis teyei lek ingwei seyap toung o, de xam se qou e zekna.”
\v 14 Woyom xel vevek valu teling wou bei, “Dom xa ne bong ambei nya?”
\p Moxo neil elox wou xel bei, “Xam seng bo nol wou xomaxoneing me panax xel xe malew. Me na byex qayeeng tyonyeing lek xomaxoneing en xel xe malew. Qe xam ghe bou naleimim bei malew wei xam ghe mi qou en xuk on teyei woy.”
\p 
\v 15 Xel xomaxoneing wei mindei me axe lulti beimambei yon xel dalus di wou naleind ngenong bei, “Beip Yoan on Kilisi?”
\v 16 Yoan lewexe wou xel dalus bei, “A lipek xam en memiing, ekom tambiy ti nikanzek ghanaw ay eno tyek nam, de a se nimza teyeimbei a tul yis veil e xe vaxalambes. Eno moxo tyek zipek xam en Laweeng Vambuing me nenyex is.
\v 17 Moxo zeim taliv eivek mema, en embei beyal wit neing veil myapapu, de qekuwou me na toung eivek xomek yaeing, ekom moxo tyek besei myapapu lek nenyex wei se mi mey yo.”
\p 
\v 18 Yoan neil qayeeng valu wei embei byex xomaxoneing laleind o de neil Xoulek Nimza wou xel.
\s1 Herot toung Yoan eivek xeitueing
\p 
\v 19 Ekom gyeik Yoan neil xel xe seyap Herot en sewokeing wei luw Herodias wei li venei yo, me kwa nilul dalus wei mi wong eno is.
\v 20 De Herot tetulexe tine is nilul dalus wei mi wong o, dom toung Yoan la eivek xeitueing.
\s1 Yoan lipek Yesu
\p 
\v 21 Gyeik ingwei xomaxoneing dalus di lipek, eno Yesu lipek is. Me ka e di zeimema, eno tyoung gheyapu tax.
\v 22 Me Laweeng Vambuing lep me lam wou e, nambei beliy me lam dei lek e. De vya ti lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei: “Wang on a Neung moux, wei a laleing vind o, a wo xeinglala en wang.”
\s1 Yesu buyeiw leind
\p 
\v 23 Yesu xe vakovek qes la tyip ambei xoumeeng yal (30) gyeik ingwei e wong e xe xuk a tax o. Moxo Yosep neu.
\q1 Yosep on Heli neu,
\q1 
\v 24 de Heli yon Matat neu,
\q1 de Matat on Livai neu,
\q1 de Livai yon Melki neu,
\q1 de Melki yon Janai neu,
\q1 de Janai yon Yosep neu,
\q1 
\v 25 de Yosep on Matatias neu,
\q1 de Matatias on Amos neu,
\q1 de Amos on Nahum neu,
\q1 de Nahum on Esli neu,
\q1 de Esli yon Nagai neu,
\q1 
\v 26 de Nagai yon Mat neu,
\q1 de Mat on Matatias neu,
\q1 de Matatias on Semen neu,
\q1 de Semen on Josek neu,
\q1 de Josek on Joda neu,
\q1 
\v 27 de Joda yon Joanan neu,
\q1 de Joanan on Resa neu,
\q1 de Resa yon Serubabel neu,
\q1 de Serubabel on Seatiel neu,
\q1 de Seatiel on Neri neu,
\q1 
\v 28 de Neri yon Melki neu,
\q1 de Melki yon Adi neu,
\q1 de Adi yon Kosam neu,
\q1 de Kosam on Elmadam neu,
\q1 de Elmadam on Er neu,
\q1 
\v 29 de Er on Yosua neu,
\q1 de Yosua yon Eliese neu,
\q1 de Eliese on Jorim neu,
\q1 de Jorim on Matat neu,
\q1 de Matat on Livai neu,
\q1 
\v 30 de Livai yon Simion neu,
\q1 de Simion on Yuda neu,
\q1 de Yuda yon Yosep neu,
\q1 de Yosep on Jonam neu,
\q1 de Jonam on Eliakim neu,
\q1 
\v 31 de Eliakim on Melea neu,
\q1 de Melea yon Mena neu,
\q1 de Mena yon Matata neu,
\q1 de Matata yon Natan neu,
\q1 de Natan on Dawit neu,
\q1 
\v 32 de Dawit on Jesi neu,
\q1 de Jesi yon Obet neu,
\q1 de Obet on Boas neu,
\q1 de Boas on Salmon neu
\q1 de Salmon on Nason neu,
\q1 
\v 33 de Nason on Aminadap neu,
\q1 de Aminadap on Atmin neu,
\q1 de Atmin on Arni neu,
\q1 de Arni yon Hesron neu,
\q1 de Hesron on Peres neu,
\q1 de Peres on Yuda neu,
\q1 
\v 34 de Yuda yon Yakop neu,
\q1 de Yakop on Isaka neu,
\q1 de Isaka yon Apraham neu,
\q1 de Apraham on Tera neu,
\q1 de Tera yon Nahor neu,
\q1 
\v 35 de Nahor on Seruk neu,
\q1 de Seruk on Reu neu,
\q1 de Reu yon Pelek neu,
\q1 de Pelek on Eber neu,
\q1 de Eber on Sela neu,
\q1 
\v 36 de Sela yon Kainan neu,
\q1 de Kainan on Apaksat neu,
\q1 de Apaksat on Sem neu,
\q1 de Sem on Noaka neu,
\q1 de Noaka yon Lamek neu,
\q1 
\v 37 de Lamek on Metusela neu,
\q1 de Metusela yon Inok neu,
\q1 de Inok on Zaret neu,
\q1 de Zaret on Mahalalel neu,
\q1 de Mahalalel on Kenan neu,
\q1 
\v 38 de Kenan on Enos neu,
\q1 de Enos on Set neu,
\q1 de Set on Adam neu,
\q1 de Adam on Anutu neu moux.
\c 4
\s1 Tambiy mapetok wo axeing wou Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Yesu pup en Laweeng Vambuing, om loumelam anghei memiing Yorodan me Laweeng Vambuing qou e me la tembuing bandaing,
\v 2 teyei lek bouk xoumeeng vey (40) eno tambiy mapetok wo axeing wou e. Moxo se ya bambou lek bouk ti beimambei yon, me lek bouk tiwei la tip lek eno maxepya e.
\p 
\v 3 Om tambiy mapetok neil wou e, “Wangwei wa Anutu Neu Moux nei, ond neil wou qakous tine en e pekwi me bo belet o.”
\p 
\v 4 Yesu lewexe me neil embei, “Xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye: ‘Xomaxoneing tyek se mendei mapieing en belet venaxow.’”
\p 
\v 5 Tambiy mapetok qou e me lek me la lukendu vaxading ti me talex tete lalei dalus wei tembuing sapa eno daing wou e.
\v 6 Me neil wou e, “Tyek am bong lei ngandoung me vunekeing nimzamza ne wou wang, en inye toundei eivek a memang, me ambei bong wou xelti, ond tyek a bong wou e.
\v 7 Om wangwei wang bong lalo wou ay, ond tyek wa xe lulul ne dalus.”
\p 
\v 8 Yesu lewexe bei, “Xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye, ‘Wang bong lalo wou Tambiy Ngandoung wa xe Anutu me na mi bong emaxow xe xuk.’”
\p 
\v 9 Woyom tambiy mapetok qou e me la beyeeng Yerusalem me la lax lek xomek vambuing pundanghou nei. De neil wou e, “Wangwei wa Anutu Neu Moux nei ond wa tetoing anghei inye me ghe na xonei.
\v 10 En xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye,
\q1 “‘Moxo tyek baluk nikanzek wou e xe angela
\q2 en xel nam gyeiteyei wang bo nimza.
\q1 
\v 11 Tyek xel a zeim wang zekna nangya memend en kandek wa seng
\q2 nyeis vaxam lek qakous.’” \rq Qapiya Lalo 91:11-12\rq*
\p 
\v 12 Yesu lewexe bei, “Xoulek neil ambei nye, ‘Wa se toung Tambiy Ngandoung wa xe Anutu eivek axeing.’”
\p 
\v 13 Gyeik ingwei tambiy mapetok wong axeing ti beimambei yon ma eno mema tena e de di axe deka bouk nge le.
\s1 Xel Nasaret pesek Yesu
\p 
\v 14 Laweeng Vambuing wong nikanzek wou Yesu me e lox me la Galili de pavulek wei e eno la teyei lek tembuing danghei tiyon dalus.
\v 15 Moxo mi teyoxe xoulek wou xel eivek xel xe xomek qekueing ama me moux alis vex sapa mi sanghoxe e lei.
\p 
\v 16 Moxo la beyeeng Nasaret, wei wo teiv lek o, de lek bouk wei Sabat eno la eivek xomek qekueing ama wei xel xe eno lalei nambei ingwei mi wong taxombouk o. Me moxo nale ghey en embei pyaw Anutu xe xoulek.
\v 17 Xel wong poropet\f + \fr 4:17 \fq poropet: \ft tambiy wei mi neil Anutu xe xoulek o.\f* Yesaya xe qapiya vambuing wei xel mi vevilexe lek xax eno wou e. Tul me yeiwou senghoing tiwei qayeeng di yeip lek o:
\q1 
\v 18 “Tambiy Ngandoung xe Laweeng Vambuing lam dei lek ay
\q2 en nambei e taw wel lek ay me beyal ay
\q2 bei a neil Xoulek Nimza wou xel kanyo.
\q1 Moxo wong a lam bei a nam a neilteyei wou xel wei la dei eivek xomek xeitueing o bei xel bong xel nam myayaing
\q2 me na neil wou xel wei mend tekeing o bei xel mend gyeina
\q1 me na bong xel wei xomaxoneing mi wo nol wou xel eno nam myayaing veil nimaying,
\q2 
\v 19 de na neil vakovek qes wei Tambiy Ngandoung embei bong lulul nimza wou moux alis vex eno teyei.” \rq Yesaya 62:1-2\rq*
\p 
\v 20 Woyom vevilexe qapiya me wong elox wou xukxe de dei tembuing. Xel wei toundei eivek xomek qekueing ama eno dalusateiv di yei e kanzek.
\p 
\v 21 Me mouk neil wou xel bei, “Gweimbeeng xoulek wei xam ghe ngo ne wo neing lek.”
\p 
\v 22 Xel dalus luk nimza en e, en qayeeng nimzamza wei di neil on om xel etek me teling bei, “Beip inye se Yosep neu ei?”
\p 
\v 23 Yesu neil wou xel bei, “Neing ayang tyek xam a neil qayeeng pakeing tine wou ay: ‘Dokta wamaxow ghe bong xow bo nimzalek! Wang bong lulul vatiyeiw eivek wamaxow bam qes ne, nambei vatiyeiw wei xa ngo wang wong eivek beyeeng Kapenaom o.’”
\p 
\v 24 Moxo tetulexe qayeeng me neil, “A neil zonghek wou xam, xel xomaxoneing se mi lenghek lek poropet ti eivek emaxow beeng qes.
\v 25 A neil neing wou xam no bei inye vexeiv ngenong toundei eivek Israel eivek bouk wei poropet Eliya yo, gyeik ingwei tyoung xey zeyi teyei lek vakovek qes yal me dentouk limti is me sewis wei maxep ngandoung yeip ela teyei lek tembuing tambak.
\v 26 Ekom Anutu se wong Eliya la wou xel Israelyeiw on ti, qe wong e la wou vexeiv ti eivek beyeeng Sarepat eivek tembuing wei Saidon nei.
\v 27 Me inye moux alis vex ngenong toundei eivek Israel eno vanei lepa\f + \fr 4:27 \fq Lepa: \ft Vanei nol wei mi wong xel ninavi mi mey o.\f* wong xel eivek bouk wei poropet Elisa yo, ekom xelti se wo nimzalek, qe Naimang wei Siria nei venaxow.”
\p 
\v 28 Xomaxoneing dalus wei toundei eivek xomek qekueing ama eno laleind wo vanei ngandoung gyeik ingwei xel ngo qayeeng tiyon o.
\v 29 Xel qandi lek, me tiy e la myayaing veil beyeeng wei xel ev lek qetyei. Om xel qou e me la lek bembembek wei lukendu yon en embei tendu e doing.
\v 30 Ekom dembu me la senghoing eivek moux alis vex ngenongakes on de la.
\s1 Yesu tiy laweeng nilaxes la myayaing
\p 
\v 31 Woyom moxo lep me la xo Kapenaom nei, beyeeng on toundei eivek distrik Galili, de lek bouk wei Sabat eno mi teyoxe xomaxoneing.
\v 32 Xel etek en e xe qayeeng wei teyoxe yo, en e xe qayeeng on lam is nikanzek ngandoung.
\p 
\v 33 Eivek xomek qekueing ama eno tambiy ti memo laweeng nilaxes mindei eivek e. Moxo eng ngandoungateiv me neil,
\v 34 “E! Wa being bong vati wou xa, Yesu wei Nasaret o? Wang lam en wa being nam bo nol wou xa? A woulek wang woy bei wa Tambiy Vambuing tiwei Anutu xe yo!”
\p 
\v 35 Om Yesu luk niseikeing wou e me neil, “Denduing ma! De lam myayaing veil moux tiyon!” Om memo yon nex tambiy on la lek tembuing wou xel mend de lam myayaing veil e dom se wo nol wou no.
\p 
\v 36 Xomaxoneing on dalus etek me di neil wouma bei, “Teyoxeing qayeeng tine vati? Om lam is lei ngandoung me nikanzek de luk nikanzek wou laweeng nilaxes me xel lam myayaing!”
\p 
\v 37 Me e xe pavulek wei wong vatiyeiw eno la teyei lek tembuing tiyon dalus.
\s1 Yesu wong Simon yeing wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 38 Yesu la veil xomek qekueing ama me la eivek Simon beeng. Gying ngandoung wo nol wou Simon yeing avexta, me gweimbeeng xel teling wou Yesu bei e devind vexo.
\v 39 Om la paviy vexo me luk niseikeing wou gying, me ema veil e. Vexo qandi lek lutika me la menyex wou lul yaeing wou xel.
\s1 Yesu wong moux alis vex ngenong wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 40 Gyeik ingwei sayeiv teila eno xomaxoneing qou xel dalus wei vanei nelu nelu wong xel o me la wou Yesu me e liw mema lek xel titi, moxo wong xel dalus wo nimzalek.
\p 
\v 41 Xel memo ngenongakes lam myayaing veil xomaxoneing ngenong me di taxe bei, “Wang on Anutu Neu Moux!” Ekom moxo luk nikanzek wou xel me peti xel, en nambei xel woulek bei e Kilisi. \f + \fr 4:41 \fq Kilisi. \ft Eivek qayeeng wei Hibru eno xel neil, Mesia. Qes, tambiy wei Anutu beyal bei e qou xomaxoneing noum o.\f*
\s1 Yesu ghavineeng eivek beyeeng valu
\p 
\v 42 Satiboukeing lul eno Yesu qandi me la ingwei xel ma veil o. Om xomaxoneing mi yimexe e, gyeik ingwei xel la yeiwou e eno xel wong en xel embei neil axound e bei e se na veil xel.
\v 43 Ekom neil embei, “A na neil Xoulek Nimza wei tete lalei wei Anutu yo, wou xel beyeeng bamba nei is, en qes tiyon om wong a lam.”
\v 44 Me moxo la neil xoulek lala eivek xomek qekueing ama dalus wei Yudia nei.
\c 5
\s1 Yesu taxe xel betiyeing tiwei myaxeeng o
\p 
\v 1 Bouk ti eno Yesu la nale wou lounyeing Genesaret\f + \fr 5:1 \fq Genesaret \ft Lounyeing Galili.\f* nenyawes, me xomaxoneing ngenong la vingama e vivekwou e, me di ngo Anutu xe xoulek.
\v 2 Yesu yei bot yayuw di yeip wou lounyeing nenyawes, xel wei mi qou woing eno la veil, en xel la di sekweyexe xel xe lewek.
\v 3 Yesu lek la eivek bot ti, tiyon Simon xe, me teling wou Simon bei e tendu bot na nayaka veil lounyeing nenyawes. Woyom la dei lek bot me teyoxe xel ngenongakes on.
\p 
\v 4 Gyeik ingwei e neil xoulek woy, eno neil wou Simon bei, “Tendu bot e la eivek memiing manghembi me nex lewek teila eivek en kandek na puw woing o.”
\p 
\v 5 Simon lewexe bei, “Teiv, boukeing tine xa wong xuk ngandoung ek xa se qou lulti. Ekom wang neil, om tyek a nox banex lewek na eivek memiing no.”
\p 
\v 6 Gyeik xel wong ambei nyon eno woing ngenong eivek me lewek embei tax.
\v 7 Om xel nex memend en xel wei xel xouing mi wong xuk lekti wei toundei lek bot nge yo me xel lam vind xel me toung woing eivek bot luw xouing me e puplek om wong bot luw xouing di teila eivek memiing lalei.
\p 
\v 8 Gyeik ingwei Simon Petele yei inyon, eno la ev vaxa qatu eivek wou Yesu me neil embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, la veil ay, en a moux wei sewokeing o.”
\v 9 En e is liyeiw dalus wei toundei is e eno etek en ingwei xel qou woing ngenong o.
\v 10 Me Sebedi neu Jems aluw Yoan wei luw mi wong xuk woing is Simon, eno luw yei me etek is.
\p Woyom Yesu neil wou Simon bei, “Wa seng gwaleeng. En gweimbeeng me e mi na eno tyek wang bong xuk me na qou xomaxoneing.”
\v 11 Om xel puw xel xe bot luw xouing la nale yasewis, woyom xel ghanaw lulul dalus toundei de la betiwou Yesu.
\s1 Moux wei vanei lepa yo
\p 
\v 12 Ka Yesu toundei eivek beyeeng ti, eno tambiy ti lam, ninavi pup en vanei lepa. Gyeik ingwei yei Yesu, moxo yeip ma eivek tembuing wou e me tay wou e, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wangwei wa laleim devind ond wang bong am bo nimzalek.”
\p 
\v 13 Yesu tatei mema la me axlek moux tiyon. Moxo neil embei, “A laleing vind, wang bo nimzalek!” De lutika eno lepa ma veil e.
\p 
\v 14 Woyom Yesu luk nikanzek wou embei, “Wa se neil wou xelti, qe la, me talex xow wou lumuki, me ghe bong xound na nambei Mose neil o en e talex bei wang wo nimzalek, en xel boulek bei wa xe vanei ma.”
\p 
\v 15 De pavulek wei Yesu eno la wo ngandoung, om xomaxoneing ngenong lam me ngo e de moxo wong xel xe vanei wo nimzalek.
\v 16 Ekom Yesu venaxow mi la veil xel me la tembuing bandaing me la zeimema.
\s1 Yesu wong tambiy wei bezomb o wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 17 Bouk ti gyeik Yesu di teyoxe moux alis vex me dei, eno xel Parisi\f + \fr 5:17 \fq Parisi \ft xel wei mi betiwou xel xe kwa me Mose xe petieing.\f* me xel putoung wei petieing eno xel lam anghei beyeeng dalus wei Galili me Yudia me beyeeng Yerusalem, me la toundei inyei. Me Tambiy Ngandoung xe nikanzek lam eivek Yesu me e wong moux alis vex xe vanei wo nimzalek.
\v 18 Xel moux valu qalei tambiy wei bezomb o ti lek lelek me lam, xel di wong me yei en xel embei qou e me na xomek lalei me na niw wou Yesu ma.
\v 19 Gyeik ingwei xel lam eno xel ngenongakes toundei zeyi om xel se teyeimbei gyeiwou sakwaing ti me na eivek xomek lalei. Om xel lek xomek demi qetyei me gwang danghei ti me byex yis lek lelek me wong tambiy on di teila kaka eivek moux alis vex senghoing wou Yesu ma.
\p 
\v 20 Gyeik ingwei Yesu yei xel xe wongeingis, moxo neil embei, “Gweleeng, a semaleeng wa xe sewokeing.”
\p 
\v 21 Xel Parisi me xel putoung wei petieing o di wou eivek naleind, “Eti ingwei embei qou Anutu nimbeeng nei? Xelti se teyeimbei semaleeng sewokeing, qe Anutu venaxow.”
\p 
\v 22 Yesu woulek vati wei xel di wou naleind en o me teling, “Nambei nya xam ghe di wou naleimim en lulti beimambei ne eivek laleimim?
\v 23 Qayeeng vati teyei bei neileing, ‘A semaleeng wa xe sewokeing’ o neileing bei, ‘Wa qandi lek me ghe na?’
\v 24 Ekom inyon xam ghe boulek bei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux qou lei ngandoung lek tembuing en embei semaleeng sewokeing.” Moxo neil wou moux ti bezombeing on, “A neil wou wang, qandi lek, qou wa xe lelek me la bam.”
\v 25 Lutika eno moxo qandi lek wou moux alis vex mend me qou e xe vati wei yeip lek o me la beeng de di sanghoxe Anutu.
\v 26 Xomaxoneing dalus etek en ingwei xel yei Anutu xe nikanzek me poux zeng, de sanghoxe Anutu me neil embei, “Xey a xei lulvako ngandoung gweimbeeng.”
\s1 Yesu taxe Livai
\p 
\v 27 Ka tine la veil eno Yesu la myayaing me yei tambiy wei mi qou takis o ti lei Livai eno toundei eivek xomek takis. Yesu neil wou bei, “Wa betiy ay.”
\v 28 Livai qandi lek me ghanaw lulul dalus de betiwou e.
\p 
\v 29 Woyom Livai wong mata ngandoung ti wou Yesu eivek xomek wei e nei me xel qendu ngandoung wei mi qou takis o me xel valu lam ya is xel.
\v 30 Ekom xel Parisi me xel putoung wei petieing o eivek qendu wei Parisi yo di neil Yesu xe xel betiyeing, “Nambei nya xam ghe di wa me ghe num is xel wei mi qou takis me xel wei sewokeing o?”
\p 
\v 31 Yesu lewexe me neil embei, “Xel wei vanei ma eno se mi la wou dokta, qe xel wei vanei yo.
\v 32 A se lam bei taxe xel wei bombek o, qe xel wei sewokeing o en xel pekwi xow.”
\s1 Xel teling Yesu en kwa wei vambueing yaeing o
\p 
\v 33 De xel neil wou embei, “Xel betiyeing wei Yoan o di vambu yaeing me zeimemend me xel betiyeing wei Parisi yo is, ekom ingwei wang eno di wo eisanou lek yaeing me numeing.”
\p 
\v 34 Yesu lewexe bei, “Wang teyei bei bong xel wei lam toundei is tambiy wei embei dii vex eno vambu yaeing gyeik e toundei is xel o?
\v 35 Ekom bouk tyek nam gyeik ingwei xel a qou tambiy tiwei embei dii vex eno me na veil xel, on tyek eivek bouk kayon eno xel vambu yaeing.”
\p 
\v 36 Me Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine wou xel bei, “Xelti se mi qateiv teimb ding myasepu wei vako yo me duw eivek ingwei takwei yo. Wangwei e bong ambei nyon, on tyek zex teimb ding wei vako yo, de ing vako eno tyek se ghok ingwei takwei yo.
\v 37 Me xelti se mi taw wain nilouk vako eivek wain takwei ninavi\f + \fr 5:37 \fq wain takwei ninavi \ft Xel mi duw sipsip me meme ninavi me taw wain nilouk me memiing eivek.\f*. Wangwei e bong ambei nyon on tyek wain vako zex wain ninavi, de wain tyek na taw veil de wain ninavi zex me bo nol.
\v 38 Ma, xel a taw wain vako eivek wain ninavi vako.
\v 39 Me xel tiwei num wain takwei eno tyek laleind se devind bei na num vako, en tyek na neimbei, ‘Takwei nimza.’”
\c 6
\s1 Tambiy Ngandoung wei Sabat o
\p 
\v 1 De Sabat ti eno Yesu la di ghavineeng eivek xuk lalei wei wit o. Me e xe xel betiyeing ul wit neing valu me liyexe eivek memend me wong navi veil de ya neing.
\v 2 Dekakom Parisi valu teling bei, “Xam ghe wong vati wei se la teyei lek o lek Sabat enva?”
\p 
\v 3 Yesu lewexe me neil, “Xam seng pyaw vati wei Dawit wong gyeik ingwei e is e xe xel maxepya xel o?
\v 4 Moxo la eivek Anutu xe xomek, me la qou belet vambuing wei xel mi toung wou Anutu ma yo, moxo ya vati wei petieing lewexe lek bei, xel lumuki venaxow a mi gya yo. De moxo wong valu wou e xe xel me xel ya is.”
\v 5 Woyom Yesu neil wou xel bei, “Xomaxoneing Neu Moux ne Tambiy Ngandoung wei Sabat o.”
\s1 Yesu wong tambiy wei mema bezomb o ti wo nimzalek Sabat
\p 
\v 6 Lek Sabat nge eno moxo la eivek xomek qekueing ama me di teyoxe xel. Tambiy ti toundei inyon eno mema payeiv bezomb.
\v 7 Xel Parisi me xel putoung wei petieing o di yimexe qes wei xel embei byex qayeeng lek Yesu yo, om xel di yei e teyei teyei bei tyek se bong vanei ti bo nimzalek Sabat.
\v 8 Ekom Yesu yei woueing nalei wei xel o, om neil wou tambiy wei mema bezomb bei, “Qandi lek me la nale mya wou xel sapa mend.” Om moxo qandi lek me la nale inyei.
\p 
\v 9 Woyom Yesu neil wou xel, “Ambei teling xam. Nyei vati la teyei lek en bouk wei Sabat o, xey a bong kwa nimza lek, o xey a bong kwa nilul lek? Xey a devind mapieing o xey a bo nol wou?”
\p 
\v 10 Moxo yei e vivekwou xel dalus, dekalekom neil wou tambiy tiyon bei, “Tatei memam.” Moxo wong ambei nyon de mema wo nimzalek.
\v 11 Ekom xel Parisi me xel putoung wei petieing o laleind wo vanei me di neil wouma bei, “Tyek xey a bong vati wou Yesu?”
\s1 Sinale xoumeeng yuw
\p 
\v 12 Lek bouk on ti eno Yesu lek lukendu ti me la en embei na zeimema. Moxo mi zeimema wou Anutu eivek boukeing tiyon dalus.
\v 13 Gyeik ingwei woyaing eno Yesu taxe e xe xel betiyeing dalus lam wou e me beyal xel xoumeeng yuw wei taxe sinale\f + \fr 6:13 \fq sinale \ft Tambiy wei Yesu wong e la bei ena bong xuk o. E na neil xoulek.\f* lek xel o.
\v 14 Ti lei Simon (wei Yesu taxe e lei Petele yo), li Andrias, Jems, Yoan, Pilip, Batolomiu,
\v 15 Matai, Tomas, Jems wei Alpias neu yo, me Simon wei xel taxe bei Selot \f + \fr 6:15 \fq Selot \ft Xel wei nale nikanzek bei embei zeim seyap wei Rom o veil.\f*o,
\v 16 Yudas wei Jems neu me Yudas Iskariot tiwei toung Yesu eivek xel vevek memend o.
\s1 Yesu wong xel wei vanei yo wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 17 Woyom Yesu lep lek lukendu me la xonei is e xe xel betiyeing me la nale lek beyeeng wei sambus o. E xe xel betiyeing ngenong toundei inyon me xomaxoneing ngenong lam anghei Yudia sapa, me nanghei beyeeng Yerusalem, me nanghei mamileeng vi wei paviy beyeeng Taia me Saidon eno lam toundei inyon.
\v 18 Xel lam en embei ngo e xe qayeeng de e bong xel xe vanei bo nimzalek. Me moux alis vex wei xel laweeng nilaxes wo nol wou xel eno Yesu wong xel wo nimzalek.
\v 19 Me xomaxoneing dalus di wong me yei en xel embei daxlek e, en nambei nikanzek di lam eivek e me wong xel dalus wo nimzalek.
\s1 Yesu neil embei xel kanyo bo xeindlala
\p 
\v 20 Yesu yei e xe xel betiyeing, de neil embei,
\q1 “Xam wei kanyo yo ghe bo xeimimlala,
\q2 en Anutu xe tete lalei yon xam xe.
\q1 
\v 21 Xam wei maxep mi ya xam gweimbeeng eno ghe bo xeimimlala
\q2 en loxyus eno tyek xam ghe gwa me enden xam.
\q1 Xam wei ghe mi eng gweimbeeng eno ghe bo xeimimlala
\q2 en tyek loxyus eno xam a mi nap.
\q1 
\v 22 Xam ghe bo xeimimlala gyeik ingwei xel moux laleind bo nol wou xam,
\q2 gyeik ingwei xel a tiy xam me na neil qayeeng nol lek xam,
\q2 me pesek xam leimim nambei nilul, qes en Xomaxoneing Neu Moux.
\p 
\v 23 “Ond lek bouk kayon xam ghe bo xeimimlala me davyeip davyeip is xeilala, en xam xe xouveing ngandoung toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu nei. En nambei nyon eno xel bundyeiw mi wong kwa kayon wou xel poropet.
\q1 
\v 24 “Ekom xam wei lulul ana yo ghe gwaleeng amim,
\q2 en xam ghe qou lulul wei wong xam laleimim wo nimza yo woy.
\q1 
\v 25 Xam wei ghe mi wa ngenong gweimbeeng me enden xam eno xam ghe gwaleeng amim.
\q2 En tyek loxyus eno maxep gya xam. Xam wei ghe mi nap gweimbeeng ne,
\q1 xam ghe gwaleeng amim.
\q2 En tyek loxyus eno xam ghe bo talot me ghe deeng.
\q1 
\v 26 Xam ghe gwaleeng amim gyeik ingwei moux alis vex dalus baluk qayeeng nimza en xam o.
\q2 En takwei eno xel bundyeiw mi wong ambei nyon wou xel poropet wei tyonyeing o.”
\s1 Wa laleim devind xel vevek amba
\p 
\v 27 Yesu neil no bei, “A neil wou xam eti yeiw wei ghe mi ngo axe qayeeng o: Xam laleimim devind xel vevek amba wei xam o, de ghe bong nimza wou eti yeiw wei laleind mi wo nilul wou xam o,
\v 28 Xam ghe bo mata wou eti yeiw wei mi neil vya lek xam o, dom na zeimemamim en xel wei mi wo nol wou xam o.
\v 29 Wangwei xelti petapexe wa ling valu ond wa pekwi valu wou en e petapexe is. De wangwei xelti qou wa xe teimb ding, on wa se neil axound wa xe teimb wei embei qou yo.
\v 30 Xam ghe bong lulul wou xel sapa wei teling xam o, me eti yeiw qou xam xe lulul, on xam se baluk nikanzek bei xel bong enoum.
\v 31 Xam ghe bong wou xel bange nambei ingwei xam ambei xel bong wou xam o.
\p 
\v 32 “Wangwei xam laleimim devind xel wei laleind mi vind xam o venaxow, on tyek xam a qou lul nimza vati en inyon? Xel sewokeing is ambei nyon, xel laleind mi vind xel wei laleind mi vind xel o.
\v 33 Me wangwei xam ghe bong kwa nimza wou xel wei mi wo nimza wou xam o venaxow, on tyek xam a qou lul nimza vati en inyon? Xel sewokeing mi wong ambei nyon is o.
\v 34 Me wangwei xam ghe bong vineing en malew wou moux alis vex valu de ghe wou naleimim bei tyek xel bong xouveing noum wou xam venaxow, ond tyek xam a qou lul nimza vati en inyon? Xel sewokeing is ambei nyon xel mi wong vineing en malew wou xel sewokeing valu en xel woulek bei tyek xel bong xouveing dalus noum zeyi.
\v 35 Ekom xam laleim devind xel vevek amba, me ghe bong nimza wou xel, de ghe bong lul e na bandaing wou xel de xam seng bou kwamim bei na qou lulul ti noumenam. Woyom tyek xam xe xouveing bo ngandoung, me tyek xam ghe bong ambei Anutu gheyapu neu. En mi wong nimza wou xel wei se mi neil dange wou e yo me xel wei nilul o.
\v 36 Xam laleimim e mi pyaxow nambei xam Mamim lalei mi pyaxow en xel o.
\s1 Xam seng gwei xel nge me baluk en e
\p 
\v 37 “Xam seng gwei xel nge me baluk en e, enok Anutu gyei xam me baluk en xam. Xam se byex qayeeng lek xel nge me na neimbei xel wong nilul. Enok Anutu na byex qayeeng lek xam me na neimbei xam ghe wo nilul. Xam semaleeng nilul wei xel nge yo on tyek Anutu semaleeng nilul wei xam o.
\v 38 Xam ghe bong wou xel nge, on tyek Anutu bong enoum wou xam. Tyek bong lul ngenong me na toung mema lek e deteina me na qounghexe e pup me qapyex veil me bong wou xam. En lulul vamva wei xam ghe wong wou xel nge, eno tyek Anutu bong lulul vamva yon noum wou xam nambei nyon.”
\p 
\v 39 De Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine wou xel bei, “Teyeimbei moux matekeing ti natax en moux matekeing nge? Yon tyek luw xouing se deivek leiveeng?
\v 40 Yak qapiya ti se ghanaw e xe putoung, qe ka e gwevek boy on tyek xel titi teyei lek e xe putoung.
\p 
\v 41 “Nambei nya wang wei papu nayaka wei toundei eivek lim ma yon de wa seng wei pelang wei toukale eivek wa venaxow mam on?
\v 42 Nambei nya wang neil wou lim bei, ‘Ling, wong a wo papu kawei toundei eivek wa mam on veil’ de wa seng wei pelang wei toukale eivek wa mam on? Wa tambiy wei myam yuw, myaxeeng eno wa pu pelang wei toukale eivek wa mam on, dekakom ghe gwei embo nimza me ghe bong papu nayak kawei toundei eivek lim ma yon veil.”
\s1 Xax ti me e neing
\p 
\v 43 Yesu neil no bei, “Xax nimza se mi vuk neing nol, o xax wei nol eno se mi vuk neing nimza.
\v 44 Xel xomaxoneing mi yei xaxaneing wole dekakom xel woulek bei inyon xax nimza o inyon xax nol. Xel xomaxoneing se mi la wou yis wei ying o me ul xax basunghek neing lek. Me xel se mi ul wain neing lek xax wei yingying o.
\v 45 Tambiy wei nimza eno mi wong kwa nimzamza wei toundei eivek e lalei yo, de tambiy wei nilul eno kwa nilul ngenong toundei eivek e lalei. Om mi wong kwa nilul. Kwa vati wei pup e lalei lek eno mya mi neil.”
\s1 Kwa yayuw wei eveing xomek o
\p 
\v 46 Yesu neil no bei, “Nambei nya xam ghe mi taxe ay bei, ‘Tambiy Ngandoung, Tambiy Ngandoung,’ de xam seng mi betiwou qayeeng wei a mi neil o?
\v 47 Wangwei xelti nam wou ay me na ngo axe qayeeng me betiwou, on tyek a talex wou xam bei e yon nambei nya.
\v 48 Inyon teyei lek moux ti embei dev xomek o. Moxo ev leiveeng la ghembi me lax mundeeng lek qakous tata eivek tembuing lalei. Dekakom ev xomek lek gheyapu. Gyeik ingwei memiing butek me lam bimexe xomek tiyon, eno xomek se qepei, en tambiy tiyon ev xomek wo nikanzekta.
\v 49 Ekom tambiy tiwei ngo axe qayeeng me se betiwou, eno nambei moux tiwei ev xomek lek tembuing de se ev mundeeng la eivek qakous. Dekakom memiing butekeing lam bimexe lek xomek tiyon eno qepei me lelolexe dalus.”
\c 7
\s1 Beyeiv wei xel vevek o xe wongeingis
\p 
\v 1 Gyeik ingwei Yesu neil qayeeng tiyon dalus ma wou xomaxoneing me xel ngo woy, de moxo la eivek beyeeng Kapenaom.
\v 2 Nanghei inyei eno beyeiv wei xel vevek wei Rom o ti mindei. E xe xukxe tiwei lalei mi vind e ghanaw veil eno vanei wong me embim amey.
\v 3 Gyeik ingwei beyeiv ngo Yesu lam eno wong xel teivateiv wei Yudayeiw eno valu la wou e, me teling wou bei e na bong e xe xukxe bo nimzalek.
\v 4 Gyeik ingwei xel lam wou Yesu, eno xel tay wou e bei, “Tambiy tine nimza, teyeimbei wa devind e,
\v 5 en nambei moxo lalei mi vind xey wei Yuda yo, me ev xa xe xomek qekueing ama.”
\v 6 Om Yesu la is xel.
\p Moxo la paviy xomek, gyeik inyon eno beyeiv wong gweleeng valu la neil wou embei: “Tambiy Ngandoung, wa seng bo pok wou xow en a se teyei lek bei wang nam eivek a bang.
\v 7 Inye qes ambei nye, om a wou naleing bei a se teyei lek bei a maxow a nak wou wang. Qe wa neil qayeeng dom a xe xukxe embo nimzalek.
\v 8 En a maxow is a tambiy wei a mi wevek tambiy wei wo lei ngandoung en ay yo, is axe xel vevek wei mi wevek a xeinghembi yo. A neil wou tine bei, ‘La,’ on moxo la, me nge nei, ‘Lam,’ on moxo lam. A neil wou a xe xukxe bei, ‘Wang bong xuk tine,’ on moxo wong.”
\p 
\v 9 Gyeik Yesu ngo qayeeng tine eno moxo etek en e, me pekwi ma wou moux alis vex ngenong wei di betiy e yon, me neil wou xel bei, “A neil wou xam, a se xei xelti xe wongeingis wei ngandoung o nambei nye eivek Israel sapa.”
\v 10 Woyom xel moux wei beyeiv wong xel la eno loumelam xomek me yeimbei xukxe wo nimzalek.
\s1 Yesu piyexe vexeiv ti neu moux
\p 
\v 11 Ka enden nayaka le eno Yesu la beyeeng ti xel mi neil Nain, me e xe xel betiyeing me moux alis vex ngenong la is e.
\v 12 Ka la paviy tete mya wei beyeeng, eno xel qalei meyeing ti me lam myayaing, vexeiv ti neu moux tixemou yon, de moux alis vex ngenong wei beyeeng eno lam is e.
\v 13 Me gyeik ingwei Tambiy Ngandoung yei vex on eno lalei pyaxow en e me neil wou e, “Wa seng deeng.”
\p 
\v 14 Woyom la paviy me axlek qoupek meyeing, me xel wei di qalei eno nale kanzek. De moxo neil, “Moux ghavis, a neil wou wang, qandi lek!”
\v 15 De moux meyeing on qandi lek me dei ghey me luk atax, dekakom Yesu wong e lox me la wou ta.
\p 
\v 16 Xomaxoneing dalus etek en ingwei xel yei Anutu xe nikanzek me sanghoxe Anutu me neil, “Poropet ngandoung ti qandi eivek xey senghoing, Anutu lam en embei devind e xe xomaxoneing.”
\v 17 Pavulek wei Yesu ne eno xel tul ela wo tambak eivek Yudia me tembuing danghei danghei nei.
\s1 Yesu me Yoan Lipekeing
\p 
\v 18 Yoan xe xel betiyeing neil wou e en lul dalus ti beimambei wei Yesu wong on. Om moxo taxe e xe xel betiyeing yayuw,
\v 19 me wong luw la wou Tambiy Ngandoung bei na teling e, “Inye wa tambiy tiwei embei nam o, o xa mi daxe tambiy nge?”
\p 
\v 20 Gyeik ingwei moux yuw on la wou Yesu, eno luw neil wou e bei, “Yoan Lipekeing wong uw alam wou wang, bei nam a teling, ‘Inye wa tambiy tiwei embei nam o, o xa mi daxe tambiy nge?’”
\p 
\v 21 Lek bouk tiyon eno Yesu wong moux alis vex ngenong xe vanei leimalei wo nimzalek, me tiy xel laweeng nol wei toundei eivek moux alis vex eno veil, me wong xel ngenong wei mend tekeing eno yeila.
\v 22 Om Yesu neil elox wou nenyalesana luw bei, “Muw ghe nox a neil wou Yoan en vati wei muw venaxow ghe wei me ghe ngo yo: Xel wei mend tekeing eno yeila, xel wei vaxend nol eno qeilek me la, xel wei lepa eno wo nimzalek, nenya qatu eno ngowou, de meyeing qandi lek, me xel kanyo eno ngo Xoulek Nimza.
\v 23 Xel wei yei ay me xel xe wongeingis se tei eivek en ay eno xel bo xeindlala.”
\p 
\v 24 Ka Yoan xe nenyales aluw lox veil le, eno Yesu neil wou moux alis vex en Yoan bei, “Xam ghe la eivek tembuing bandaing en xam a being na gwei vati? Ghet tiwei laweeng di vei elox me loum o?
\v 25 Wangwei nama nei, yond xam ghe la bei na gwei vati? Beip xam ghe la di wei tambiy wei byex teimb nimzamza yo? Ma, xel wei mi byex teimb wei malew tata yo me xel xe lul nimzamza wei neing eno mindei eivek xel king bend.
\v 26 Ekom xam ghe la en xam a being na gwei vati? Poropet ti? Ee, a neil wou xam, poropet tiyon ghanaw xel poropet ba.
\v 27 Tambiy tiyon xel byex eivek xoulek ambei nye,
\q1 “‘Wei, tyek a bong axe nenyalesana wei mi neil qayeeng o ti natax en wang,
\q2 me tyek gyeiwou sakwaing en wang.’ \rq Malakai 3:1\rq*
\m 
\v 28 A neil wou xam, eivek xel wei tayeiw wou xel o eno Yoan ghanaw xel. Ekom tambiy wei lei maeing eivek Anutu xe tete lalei eno ghanaw Yoan.\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Xel wei yei Yesu xe xuk me ngo xoulek nimza wei Yesu eno ghanaw Yoan. \f*”
\p 
\v 29 (Xomaxoneing dalus, is xel wei mi qou takis o, gyeik xel ngo Yesu xe qayeeng, eno xel neil embei Anutu xe sakwaing on wo bombek, en nambei Yoan lipek xel.
\v 30 Ekom xel Parisi is xel wei lupeyei ngandoung en petieing wei Mose eno xel pesek Anutu xe woueing nalei en sakwaing nimza wei xel o, en nambei Yoan se lipek xel.)
\p 
\v 31 Yesu neil, “Tyek anghei xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne me talex xel lek vati? Xel on nambei nya?
\v 32 Xel on teyei lek yakyak wei mindei eivek beyeeng wei vateivek o me taxe la wou xel valu bei,
\q1 “ ‘Xa vei sakwep en xam
\q2 ekom xam seng aw,
\q1 xa wo talot
\q2 ekom xam seng eng.’
\m 
\v 33 En Yoan Lipekeing lam eno se ya belet me se num wain, eno xam ghe neimbei, ‘Moxo memo toundei eivek e.’
\v 34 De Xomaxoneing Neu Moux lam ya me num, eno xam ghe neimbei, ‘Tambiy yon mi ya ngenong me mi num wain ngenong de e gweleeng wei xel wei mi qou takis o me sewokeing o.’
\v 35 Ekom lupeyei nimza eno yeip yaing bei inye bombek en mapieing wei xel dalus wei mi betiwou yo.”
\s1 Vex sewokeing ti eno taw wel lek Yesu
\p 
\v 36 De Parisi ti taxe Yesu bei e na gya is e, om moxo la xomek wei Parisi yo me la dei lek zek\f + \fr 7:36 \ft Gyeik tiyon eno tebol ma dom xel mindei lek zek me yeip xokeing me ya. \f* me ya.
\v 37 Gyeik vex wei sewokeing o ti mindei eivek beyeeng tiyon eno ngo Yesu la di ya eivek Parisi beeng, vexo qou botol qakous nimza is wel xeimangou toukale eivek o me la.
\v 38 Vexo la nale wou Yesu demi paviy e vaxa de eng, me malouk taw lek Yesu vaxa. Woyom tul luvelus me vu Yesu vaxa luw angya, me sesuvexe Yesu vaxa lumama de taw wel lek e vaxa luw.
\p 
\v 39 Gyeik ingwei Parisi tiwei taxe Yesu la eno yei vex tiyon wong ambei nyon, eno luk wou xow bei, “Wangwei tambiy tine poropet ti on tyek boulek bei eti axlek e me vex tiyon nambei nya, vex on sewokeing.”
\p 
\v 40 Yesu lewexe lek e bei, “Simon, axe qayeeng ti om ambei neil wou wang.”
\p Moxo neil embei, “Putoung wa neil wou ay.”
\p 
\v 41 Woyom Yesu neil wou e, “Moux yayuw qou malew vateivek wou tambiy ti, nge qou selewa vaxak xoumeeng de nge qou selewa vaxak ti.
\v 42 Luw malew ma en ingwei luw embei bong enox zeyi yo, om tambiy on semaleeng malew vateivek wei luw xouing o. Om luw nge na laleind vind e ghanaw veil?”
\p 
\v 43 Simon neil elox, “A wou naleing bei, tambiy tiwei e xe malew vateivek ngandoung wei e semaleeng veil o.” Yesu neil embei, “Wang wei me ghe neil bombek.”
\p 
\v 44 Woyom moxo pekwi ma wou vex me neil wou Simon bei, “Wang wei vex tine? A lam eivek wa bam. Eno wa seng wong memiing valu bei a sekweyexe vaxang, qe vex tine sekweyexe a vaxang en malouk me vu gya luvelus.
\v 45 Wa seng sesuvexe ay. Qe gyeik a eivek a lam wa bam eno vex tine se tip sesuvexeing a vaxang.
\v 46 Wa seng taw wel lek a lung, qe vexo taw wel xeimangou yo lek a vaxang.
\v 47 Om nambei nyon a neil wou wang, vexo xe sewokeing ngenong eno semaleeng veil, om vexo lalei vind a ghanaw veil. Ekom tambiy wei Anutu semaleeng e xe sewokeing nayaka eno e xe lalei vineing nayaka.”
\p 
\v 48 Woyom Yesu neil wou vexo, “A semaleeng wa xe sewokeing veil.”
\v 49 Xel bamba wei toundei lek zek me ya eno di neil eivek ama senghoing bei, “Eti inye om teyeimbei semaleeng sewokeing veil?”
\p 
\v 50 Yesu neil wou vex on, “Wa xe wongeingis eno vind wang. Lak is laleim vevopeing.”
\c 8
\s1 Vex valu mi betiy Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Ka tine lak veil Yesu la ghavineeng eivek beyeeng nge me la nge me la valu is me neil Xoulek Nimza wei Anutu xe tete lalei eno teyei. Xel xoumeeng yuw la is e.
\v 2 Me vex valu wei Yesu tiy laweeng nol veil xel me wong xel xe vanei wo nimzalek o: Maria (xel mi taxe e bei Makdala) wei memo lim yuw lam myayaing veil e yo,
\v 3 Joana ne Kuza venei, inyon tambiy wei wo lei ngandoung en Herot beeng o, Susana, me vex ngenong is. Vex ti beimambei yon mi wong xel venaxow xe lulul bei na mi devind Yesu lis e xe betiyeing.
\s1 Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing lek vuweing wit
\p 
\v 4 Dekalekom xomaxoneing wei beyeeng sapa eno lam wou Yesu me xel qendu ngandoung qekuma me lam dei. De moxo neil qayeeng pakeing tine:
\v 5 “Tambiy tiwei mema xuk eno di vuw wit vei eivek xuk. Ka di vuw vei eivek xuk, eno valu teila lek sakwaing, me xel qeilek de menek lam ya.
\v 6 Valu teila lek qakous, om gyeik ingwei xel tyip eno xel mey en tembuing nilouk ma.
\v 7 De vei valu teila eivek yis senghoing wei yingying o, me xel dalus tyip me ding dekakom yis sevunexe wit.
\v 8 De vei valu teila eivek tembuing wei nimza yo, om tyip me vuk neing ngenong teyei lek vaxak ngenong ghanaw ingwei vuw o.”
\p Gyeik ingwei moxo neil qayeeng pakeing tiyon ma, eno taxe bei, “Eti yeiw nenya nale lek e en ngoeing qayeeng, ond wong e ngo.”
\s1 Yesu wounalei bei nya ekom mi neil qayeeng pakeing
\p 
\v 9 Moxo xe xel betiyeing teling e, “Qayeeng pakeing tine qes ambei nya?”
\v 10 De Yesu neil wou xel, “Lupeyei ngandoung wei qayeeng xupekeing qes wei Anutu xe tete lalei yo, Anutu wong wou xam. Ekom wou xel valu eno a mi luk eivek qayeeng pakeing en kandek,
\q1 “ ‘xel gyei lumama, ekom xel se gyeiwou,
\q2 de xel a ngo, ekom xel se boulek e qes.’ \rq Yesaya 6:9\rq*
\p 
\v 11 “Tine inye qayeeng pakeing qes: Vei yon Anutu xe xoulek.
\v 12 Vei wei teila lek sakwaing eno nambei xel wei ngo Anutu xe xoulek dekakom tambiy mapetok lam zeim veil xel laleind, en kandek xel se bongis me e devind xel.
\v 13 De vei wei tei lek qakous eno nambei xel wei qou xoulek is xeindlala gyeik ingwei xel ngo yo, ekom xel xe luselis se evla eivek tembuing. Xel wongis nayaka, deka bouk wei axeing lam eno xel tei veil.
\v 14 De vei wei teila eivek yis wei yingying o senghoing eno xel teyei lek xel wei ngo Anutu xe qayeeng me betiwou, ekom gyeik xel la eno xel wou naleind en lulul wei deing mapieing wei xel o, me malew ngenongakes me xeilala wei tembuing ne wou xel zeyi om xel xe neing se doung.
\v 15 Ekom vei wei teila lek tembuing nimza yo, eno teyei lek moux alis vex wei ngo xoulek me zeimaxoun o. Xel laleind nimza me bombek, me xel mi nale nikanzek me vuk neing lek.
\s1 Lam wei nale lek vaxa yo
\p 
\v 16 “Xelti se mi byex eivek lam me vun eivek deng o mi toung eivek lelek yeipeing lek o xeinghembi. Qe moxo mi toung lek lam vaxa, en kandek xel wei eivek la lalei eno na mi gyei xeiyaing.
\v 17 En lul dalus wei xupek eno tyek xel boulek, me lul dalus wei xel beliv eno tyek nam mendei yanyateiv.
\p 
\v 18 “Nambei nyon xam ghe bou naleimim bo nimza en vati wei xam ambei ngo yo. Xelti xe lupeyei toundei on tyek Anutu bong valu is, ek xelti lupeyei e ma yon vati wei wounalei bei di qou eno tyek Anutu na zeim veil e.”
\s1 Yesu ta me liyeiw
\p 
\v 19 Yesu ta is liyeiw embei nam gyei e, ekom xel se teyeimbei na paviy e, en nambei moux alis vex ngenong qekuma me toundei.
\v 20 Xelti neil wou e, “Tam alis limyeiw lam toukale myayaing, me axe en xel embei gyei wang.”
\p 
\v 21 Moxo neil elox bei, “Moux alis vex wei mi ngo Anutu xe xoulek me betiwou eno inye a tang me a lingyeiw.”
\s1 Yesu neil laweeng valeivek me ema
\p 
\v 22 Bouk ti eno Yesu neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei, “Xey ambei na lounyeing loxalu nei.” Om xel la eivek bot ti me la.
\v 23 Ka bot di la eno Yesu yeip. Laweeng ngandoung ti lam lek lounyeing me vei memiing la eivek bot om xel la eivek nimaying ngandoung.
\p 
\v 24 Xel betiyeing la piyexe Yesu, me neil embei, “Teiv, teiv, xey ambei zepna ne!”
\p Moxo qandi lek me neil laweeng me memiing wei di vuklek o, me laweeng valeivek ma de memiing yeip kanzek.
\v 25 Yesu teling e xe xel betiyeing bei, “Xam amim wongeingis inya?”
\p Xel yaleeng me etek om xel di teling wouma bei, “Tambiy tine e eti? Om luk nikanzek wou laweeng me memiing me xel ngo me betiwou?”
\s1 Yesu tiy memo veil moux ti
\p 
\v 26 Xel la loxalu nanghei danghei tiwei Gerasa nei, beyeeng wei toundei lounyeing loxalu wei Galili yo.
\v 27 Gyeik Yesu teila me la yasewis eno moux wei memo nale eivek o ti nanghei beyeeng nayak on lam wou e. Takwei yeileing nei eno tambiy tine se mi byex teimb o se mindei eivek xomek ti, qe mindei eivek leiveeng meyeing.
\v 28 Gyeik tambiy on yei Yesu, eno nyayek me teila yeip wou Yesu vaxa, de taxe xoulekeing bei, “Yesu, Anutu gheyapu Neu Moux, wa being bong vati wou ay? A tay wou wang bei wa seng bo nol wou ay!”
\v 29 En Yesu luk niseikeing wou laweeng nilaxes bei enam myayaing veil moux on. Lumama eno laweeng nilaxes mi zeimaxoun e, de xomaxoneing mi qo e mema vaxa nangya sen me xel mi yei e teyei, ekom moxo mi tax sen veil xow de memo mi qou e me la ingwei xel ma veil o.
\p 
\v 30 Yesu teling e, “Wa leim vati?”
\p Moxo neil elox bei, “Qendu ngandoung.” En nambei memo ngenong la eivek e.
\v 31 Me xel tay wou Yesu lumama bei e se tiy xel na eivek leiveeng tiwei qes maeing o.
\p 
\v 32 Bok qendu ti di ya me nale wou qetyei nenyawes nanghei inyon. Xel memo tay wou Yesu bei e bong xel na eivek xel bok on, om lenghek lek xel.
\v 33 Gyeik ingwei xel memo lam myayaing veil moux on, xel la eivek xel bok on, me bok qendu dalus on veimyend me la oing bembembek me heivek lounyeing me mey.
\p 
\v 34 Gyeik ingwei xel wei mi yeiteyei xel bok on yei vati wei qandi, eno xel veimyend me la neil lulti yon teyei wou xel wei beyeeng nayak, me beyeeng beimambei nei is,
\v 35 me xomaxoneing la yei vati wei qandi yo. Gyeik ingwei xel lam wou Yesu eno xel yei moux tiwei xel memo la veil e yo. De moxo byex teimb me lupeyei wo nimza, me toundei wou Yesu vaxa. De xel yaleeng.
\v 36 Xel wei yei lul on qandi, eno xel tul pavulek en wou xomaxoneing en ingwei memo la veil e nambei nya yo me e wo nimzalek o.
\v 37 Woyom xomaxoneing dalus wei danghei ti Gerasa yon dalus teling Yesu bei e na veil xel, en nambei xel yaleeng ngandoung. Om lox eivek bot me la.
\p 
\v 38 Moux tiwei memo la veil on tay wou bei na is e, ekom Yesu wong e la de neil wou bei,
\v 39 “Wang nox bam me ghe nox a neil vati wei Anutu wong wou wang o teyei.” Om tambiy on la me neil vati wei Yesu wong wou e yo dalus teyei wou moux alis vex wei beyeeng nayak on.
\s1 Vex yak wei mey o ti me vex wei vanei yo ti
\p 
\v 40 Gyeik ingwei Yesu lox me la lounyeing loxalu eno moux alis vex qou e is xeindlala, en xel di axe e.
\v 41 Woyom moux ti lei Yairus, inyon gyovaxa wei xomek qekueing ama yo, eno lam me ev vaxa qatu eivek wou Yesu vaxa, me wo nikanzek wou e bei Yesu na e beeng,
\v 42 en nambei e neu vex tixemou yon e xe vakovek qes nambei xoumeeng yuw eno e bim a mey.
\p Ka Yesu di la eno moux alis vex nale vingama zeyi e.
\v 43 Me vex ti toukale inyon eno gyand mi lam eivek e teyei lek vakovek qes xoumeeng yuw, me vex tiyon mi saing e xe malew la wou dokta ekom xelti se wong e wo nimzalek.
\v 44 Vexo la nale wou Yesu demi me axlek e xe teimb ding myasepu, lutika eno gyand touk veil e.
\p 
\v 45 Yesu teling bei, “Eti axlek ay?”
\p Gyeik xomaxoneing axvun, eno Petele neil, “Teiv, xomaxoneing ngenong nale vingama zeyi wang o.”
\p 
\v 46 Ekom Yesu neil embei, “Xelti axlek ay. A woulek ingwei nikanzek lam myayaing veil ay yo.”
\p 
\v 47 Woyom vexo yei bei tyek se ghupek, om la is nietekeing me ev vaxa qatu eivek wou Yesu vaxa eivek xomaxoneing dalus mend, vexo neil ingwei nambei nya axlek Yesu me nambei nya wo nimzalek luti.
\v 48 Woyom Yesu neil wou vexo, “Neung vex, wa xe wongeingis wong wang wo nimzalek. La is laleim vevopeing.”
\p 
\v 49 Ka Yesu nanghei di luk, eno xelti lam anghei Yairus beeng nei, inyon gyovaxa wei xomek qekueing ama yo. Moxo neil embei, “Neum vex mey om wa seng bo pok wou putoung no.”
\p 
\v 50 Gyeik Yesu ngo tine eno neil wou Yairus bei, “Wa seng gwaleeng, qe wang bongis, en vexo tyek bo nimzalek.”
\p 
\v 51 Gyeik ingwei Yesu la tyip Yairus beeng, eno se wong xel valu la lalei is e qe Petele, Yoan me Jems, me vex yak on ma luw ta.
\v 52 Dekalekom xomaxoneing dalus di eng me wo talot en e. Yesu neil, “Xam tip engeing. En vexo se mey qe di yeip.”
\p 
\v 53 Xel napexe e, en xel woulek bei vexo mey.
\v 54 Ekom moxo zeim vexo mema me neil embei, “A neung yak, qandi lek!”
\v 55 Vexo nu loumelam eivek, me lutika eno vexo qandi lek. Woyom Yesu neil wou xel bei xel bong lul yaeing me e gya.
\v 56 Vexo ma luw ta etek, ekom Yesu peti luw nikanzek bei, “Muw se neil wou xelti en lul tiwei qandi yon.”
\c 9
\s1 Yesu wong xel xoumeeng yuw la
\p 
\v 1 Gyeik ingwei Yesu taxe sinaleyeiw xoumeeng yuw qekuma, eno wong nikanzek me lei ngandoung wou xel bei xel a tiy memo dalus na myayaing veil moux alis vex me bong xel wei vanei wong eno bo nimzalek.
\v 2 Me moxo wong xel la bei na neil xoulek wei Anutu xe tete lalei yo me bong xel wei vanei eno bo nimzalek.
\v 3 Moxo neil wou xel, “Xam a being na eno xam se qou lulti, patongeeng me vaxak me belet me malew, me xam se qou teimb nge is.
\v 4 Xomek tiwei xam ghe la eivek eno xam a mi mendei eivek deka xam ghe na veil beyeeng tiyon le.
\v 5 Wangwei xomaxoneing wei beyeeng ti eno se qou xam, ond xam pepa vegyuveeng veil vaxamim gyeik ingwei xam ghe na veil xel xe beyeeng o, en xel boulek bei xel wo kwa yon nol wou xow.”
\v 6 Om xel betiyeing la myayaing veil inyon me la beyeeng danghei danghei nei me neil Xoulek Nimza me wong xomaxoneing wei vanei yo wo nimzalek nanghei danghei danghei nei.
\s1 Herot embei boulek Yesu bei e eti
\p 
\v 7 Seyap Herot ngo lul vatiyeiw dalus wei qandi yon. Me di wounalei ngenong, en nambei xel valu neil embei Yoan qandi lek veil meyeing,
\v 8 de xel valu neil embei Eliya lam tyip, de valu neil embei poropet wei takwei yo ti loumelam qou mapieing no.
\v 9 Ekom Herot neil embei, “A qateiv Yoan kwa tip. De eti ingwei di wong lulti beimambei yon me a ngo ne?” Me di wong me yei en embei gyei Yesu.
\s1 Yesu vet xel 5,000
\p 
\v 10 Gyeik sinaleyeiw loumelam, eno xel neil wou Yesu en vatiyeiw wei xel wong o. Woyom qou xel me xel venaxow la veil moux alis vex me la beyeeng tiwei xel mi neil Betsaida nei,
\v 11 ekom moux alis vex ngenong on woulek en ingwei Yesu la om xel betiy e. Moxo wo xeilala en xel lam o me luk wou xel en Anutu xe tete lalei, me wong moux alis vex wei vanei yo wo nimzalek.
\p 
\v 12 Soukeinglul eno xel xoumeeng yuw lam wou e me neil, “Wang bong moux alis vex na beyeeng danghei danghei nei en xel na gyei xend lul yaeing me beyeeng wei yeipeing o, en nambei beyeeng wei xey a toundei eivek ne eno xel ma veil.”
\p 
\v 13 Moxo neil elox bei, “Xam ghe bong lul valu wou xel en xel gya.”
\p Xel lewexe bei, “Xa di qou belet lim ka de woing yayuw, wambei xa na bou lulul yaeing wou xel ngenong ne?”
\v 14 (Nambei 5,000 moux toundei inyon.)
\p Ekom moxo neil wou e xe xel betiyeing, “Xam ghe bong xel mendei tembuing, e teyei lek 50 eivek qendu titi.”
\v 15 Xel betiyeing wong ambei nyon, me xel dalus dei tembuing.
\v 16 Woyom Yesu qou belet lim on is woing yuw on me yeima lekla tyoung gheyapu nei, me wong dange wou Anutu. De dembu belet is woing me wong wou xel betiyeing bei xel bong wou xomaxoneing.
\v 17 Xel dalus ya me enden xel, de xel betiyeing qekuwou myapapu wei toundei yo me sei e pup eivek pasik xoumeeng yuw.
\s1 Petele neil Yesu teyeimbei e Kilisi
\p 
\v 18 Bouk ti Yesu venaxow di zeimema me e xe xel betiyeing toundei is e, moxo teling wou xel bei, “Moux alis vex ngenong mi neil embei ay eti?”
\p 
\v 19 Xel neil elox bei, “Xel valu neil embei wa Yoan Lipekeing, de valu neil embei Eliya, de valu neil embei poropet wei takwei eno ti loumelam dei mapieing.”
\p 
\v 20 Moxo teling wou xel, “De xam ambei inya? Xam ghe neimbei ay eti?”
\p Petele lewexe, “Wa Kilisi wei Anutu yo.”
\p 
\v 21 Yesu peti xel nikanzek bei xel se neil inyon wou xelti.
\v 22 Me moxo neil embei, “Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek na qou myavanei ngenong, me xel teivateiv me xel lumuki leitata yo me xel putoung wei petieing o tyek pesek e me nyeis e mey deka bouk yayal na veil om qandi lek.”
\p 
\v 23 Woyom moxo neil wou xel dalus bei, “Wangwei xelti embei betiy ay, ond e dax xow vun me qalei e xe xax pepeeng taxombouk me betiwou ay.
\v 24 En xelti embei zeimaxoun mapieing wei e yo ond tyek na saing e xe mapieing, ekom wangwei xelti saing mapieing wei e yo en ay on tyek mendei mapieing luta.
\v 25 Wangwei xomaxoneing a qou lulul wei tembuing sapa ne ekom na saing mapieing wei e yo? Yon tyek bo nimza wou e nambei nya?
\v 26 Wangwei xelti embei nigyaleeng en ay me axe qayeeng, on tyek Xomaxoneing Neu Moux nigyaleeng en e gyeik ingwei embei nam is e xe xeiyaing ngandoung me eivek xeiyaing wei Ma xe yo me xel angela vambuing o.
\v 27 A neil wou xam zonghek, xel wei toukale inye yo valu tyek se daxe meyeing, qe tyek xel gyei Anutu xe tete lalei.”
\s1 Yesu neing pekwi bange
\p 
\v 28 Nambei bouk lim yal la veil en ingwei Yesu neil inyon o, moxo qou Petele, Yoan me Jems is xow me xel lek lukendu ti me la en embei na zeimema.
\v 29 Ka e di zeimema, eno mapekwi me e xe teimb teltyip nambei zivip mi nex mema yo.
\v 30 Moux yayuw, Mose luw Eliya,
\v 31 luw lam is xeiyaing ngandoung me di luk is Yesu. Luw di luklek ingwei tyek na veil tembuing ne yo, me embim bong e xe xuk bo neing lek nanghei Yerusalem o.
\v 32 Petele me luyuw wei la is e eno lal mend yeip om lal yeip, ekom gyeik ingwei lal qandi lek, lal yei e xe xeiyaing ngandoung me moux yuw wei toukale is e yon.
\v 33 Ka moux yuw on di la veil Yesu, Petele neil wou e, “Teiv, inye nimza bei xey a toumendei inye. Wong xa ev xomek sel yayal, ti wou wang, ti wou Mose de ti wou Eliya.” (Moxo se woulek vati wei neil on.)
\p 
\v 34 Ka moxo di luk eno laxap ti lam me sevunexe xel, me xel yaleeng en ingwei xel la eivek laxap o.
\v 35 Vya ti lam eivek laxap, me neil embei, “Tine a Neung, wei a beyal o, xam a mi ngo e.”
\v 36 Gyeik vya tiyon luk woy eno xel yei bei inye Yesu venaxow. De xel betiyeing venaxow di wou naleind en inyon, de lek bouk tiyon eno xel se neil wou xelti en vati wei xel yei yo.
\s1 Yesu wong yak wei memo dei eivek o wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 37 De bouk nge, gyeik ingwei Yesu lis e xe xel betiyeing lep me loum veil lukendu, eno moux alis vex ngenongakes lam wou e.
\v 38 Moux ti eivek xel ngenong on senghoing eno taxe, “Putoung a tay wou wang bei, wang gwei a neung moux, en inyon a neung tixemou ne.
\v 39 Laweeng ti mi la eivek e me lutika eno mi nyayek me nex e la di puw mema vaxa lek tembuing de wong myapeleis mi qandi eivek e mya. De laweeng tiyon se mi la veil e qe mi wo nol wou e.
\v 40 A tay wou wa xe xel betiyeing bei xel a tiy laweeng nol e na veil. Ekom xel se teyei.”
\p 
\v 41 Yesu neil elox, “Xam xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne xam amim wongeingis ma, me xam xe woueing nalei me kwa ne se nimza, tyek a mi mendei is xam teyei lek bouk vamva me qalei xam xe maying? Qou neum me lam inye.”
\p 
\v 42 Ka yak on di lam, memo yon nex e la lek tembuing me di puw mema vaxa eivek. Ekom Yesu neil laweeng nilaxes on, me wong yak on wo nimzalek de wong e lox wou ma.
\v 43 Me xomaxoneing dalus on etek en Anutu xe nikanzek ngandoung on.
\s1 Yesu neil luyuw bei tyek na mey
\p Ka xel dalus di wou naleind en vati wei Yesu wong o, moxo neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei,
\v 44 “Xam a ngo embo nimza en vati wei am bim a neil wou xam o. Tyek xel a neil Xomaxoneing Neu Moux teyei me na toung e na eivek xomaxoneing memend.”
\v 45 Ekom xel se woulek qayeeng on qes. En inyon yeip xupekeing en xel, om xel se woulek, me xel yaleeng en ingwei xel embei teling e yo.
\s1 Eti tyek bo lei ngandoung
\p 
\v 46 Woyom xel betiyeing pyalek ama bei eti tyek bo lei ngandoung en xel.
\v 47 Yesu yei xel laleind, om qou yak ti me wong e nale wou e wes.
\v 48 Woyom moxo neil wou xel betiyeing bei, “Xelti embei zenghek lek yak kane en a leing on lenghek lek ay, me tiwei lenghek lek ay eno lenghek lek tambiy tiwei wong a lam o. En tambiy tiwei lei maeing eivek xam dalus senghoing eno tiyon lei ngandoung.”
\s1 Tambiy ti embei se bo nol wou xam, ond inyon xam xe gweleeng
\p 
\v 49 Yoan neil embei, “Teiv, xa xei tambiy ti di tiy memo en wa leim, om xa peti e en inyon se tambiy wei xey o ti.”
\p 
\v 50 Ekom Yesu neil wou embei, “Xam se peti e, en xelti embei se bo nol wou xam ond inyon xam xe.”
\s1 Xel Samaria pesek Yesu
\p 
\v 51 Ka bouk lam paviy ingwei Anutu embei qou Yesu me zek me nox me na tyoung gheyapu nei, om Yesu wounalei wo nikanzek en embei na Yerusalem.
\v 52 Me moxo wong nenyalesana valu qou qayeeng me la tax, xel la eivek beyeeng wei Samaria yo ti en xel embei gyeiwou lulul dalus wou e,
\v 53 ekom xomaxoneing wei inyon o se lenghek lek e, en embei na Yerusalem.
\v 54 Gyeik ingwei betiyeing yuw, Jems aluw Yoan, yei kwa tine, eno luw teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wambei uw a taxe nenyex nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei nam gya xel ne?”
\v 55 Ekom Yesu pekwi ma me neil luw,
\v 56 de xel la beyeeng bange.
\s1 Nimaying wei betiyeing Yesu yo
\p 
\v 57 Ka xel di la wou sakwaing, eno tambiy ti neil wou e, “Beyeeng dalus wei wambei mi na, eno tyek a mi betiwou wang.”
\p 
\v 58 Yesu neil elox bei, “Naw bemeeng eeng toundei me menek lewis toundei, ekom Xomaxoneing Neu Moux beeng wei embei ni lu lek eno ma.”
\p 
\v 59 Moxo neil wou moux nge, “Wa betiy ay.”
\p Ekom moux on neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wong a lox a ev mang wole.”
\p 
\v 60 Yesu neil wou e bei, “Wong eyeip, de xel wei meyeing eno venaxow di ev xel xe meyeing, dom wang na neil Anutu xe qayeeng wei tete lalei yo teyei.”
\p 
\v 61 Xel nge neil embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, tyek a mi betiy wang, ekom teyeimbei a nox a neil woyo wou mangha tang me lingyeiw bole?”
\p 
\v 62 Yesu neil elox wou e bei, “Tambiy wei mi zeim taliv ekom mi yei lox demi, eno se teyeimbei bong xuk eivek Anutu xe tete lalei.”
\c 10
\s1 Yesu wong xel 72 la
\p 
\v 1 Kalekom Tambiy Ngandoung beyal xel 72 is me wong xel mi la yuyuw, me xel la tax en e eivek beyeeng nayak me beyeeng sapa wei embim na eivek o.
\v 2 Moxo neil wou xel, “Lulul wo neing ngenong woy en qoueing, ekom xel xukxe eno nuyuw. Om xam teling wou Tambiy Ngandoung wei e xe lulul yaeing on, dekakom embong xukxe na eivek e mema xuk on me na qou neing.
\v 3 Xam la! A wong xam ghe la nambei sipsip lingheing eivek naw bemeeng senghoing.
\v 4 Xam se qou vaxak malew, o vaxak, o vaxalambes, me xam se neil bendiyeing wou xel wei di la wou sakwaing o.
\p 
\v 5 “Gyeik xam ghe na eivek xomek ti, myaxeeng eno xam a neil, ‘Lalei vevopeing e nak wou xomek tiyon.’
\v 6 Wangwei tambiy wei lalei vevopeing eno ti na toumendei eivek xomek tiyon, ond tyek wa xe lalei vevopeing na mendei is e, ek wangwei na ma on tyek lalei vevopeing on noumenam wou wang.
\v 7 Xam a mi mendei eivek xomek tiyon, me xam ghe gwa me na num vatiyeiw wei xel wong wou xam o, en tambiy wei mi wong xuk eno tyek na qou e xe xouveing. Dom xam seng na ghavineeng eivek xomek nge me ghe na nge.
\p 
\v 8 “Wangwei xam ghe na eivek beyeeng ti me xel a qou xam, ond xam ghe gwa vatiyeiw wei xel yeiwou me toung elam wou xam o.
\v 9 Me xam ghe bong xel wei toundei eivek beyeeng on xe vanei bo nimzalek. De na neil wou xel bei, ‘Anutu xe tete lalei lam paviy xam.’
\v 10 Ekom wangwei xam ghe na eivek beyeeng ti ek xel se qou xam, ond xam ghe na bale eivek xel xe sakwaing memama me na neimbei,
\v 11 ‘Vegyuveeng wei xam xe beyeeng on, wei mil xa vaxami eno xa pepa veil bei e nouk lek xam me talex xam xe nilul. De xam ghe boulek neing bei, Anutu xe tete lalei lam paviy.’
\v 12 A neil wou xam, lek bouk wei wongeing qayeeng eno nimaying wei embei qandi wou beyeeng tiyon eno tyek ghanaw nimaying wei Sodom o.
\s1 Lalei maying en moux alis vex wei se pekwi xow o
\p 
\v 13 “Inye wo nimaying en xam Korasin! Inye wo nimaying en xam Betsaida! En wangwei lulvako wei a wong eivek xam bamim eno xelti bong eivek Taia luw Saidon, on tyek xel pekwi xow takwei nei, me na byex teimb wei talot me dev vewev lek xow.
\v 14 Ekom lek bouk wei wongeing qayeeng, eno nimaying wei xam eno tyek ghanaw nimaying wei Taia luw Saidon o.
\v 15 Me Kapenaom wang, tyek xel sanghoxe wang zekna tyoung? Ma, tyek wang na xonei eivek beyeeng wei meyeing o.”
\p 
\v 16 Yesu neil wou xel betiyeing bei, “Xelti embei ngo xam ond ngo ay, o xelti embei pesek xam ond pesek ay, ekom xel tiwei pesek ay eno pesek tambiy tiwei wong a lam o.”
\s1 Xel 72 loumelam
\p 
\v 17 Xel 72 loumelam is xeilala me neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, xel memo betiwou xa vyami en wa leim.”
\p 
\v 18 Moxo neil elox wou xel, “A xei Sandang tei me lam nambei zivip nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 19 Xam ngo, a wong nikanzek wou xam bei xam bakei lek myeiy, me boklevek, me nikanzek wei xam o tyek ghanaw nikanzek dalus wei tambiy mapetok wei mi wo vevek o, de lulti tyek se bo nol wou xam.
\v 20 De xam seng bo xeimlala bei laweeng nol betiwou xam xe qayeeng, qe xam ghe bo xeimlala bei Anutu byex xam leimim nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei.”
\s1 Yesu wo xeilala
\p 
\v 21 Lek bouk tiyon eno Laweeng Vambuing wong Yesu pup en xeilala, me neil, “Mang a sanghoxe wang, wa Tambiy Ngandoung wei tyoung gheyapu luw tembuing o, en nambei wang vun lulul ti beimambei ne en xel wei lupeyei me kwa nimza yo, de wang talex wou xel wei nambei yakyak o. Ee, Mang, en inyon wang betiwou wamaxow xe woueing nalei me ghe wong ambei nyon.
\p 
\v 22 “Mang wong lulul dalusateiv wou ay, xelti se woulek Neu Moux qe Ma venaxow, me xelti se woulek Ma qe Neu Moux venaxow is xel wei beyal bei tyek talex e wou xel o.”
\p 
\v 23 Woyom moxo pekwi ma wou e xe xel betiyeing me neil wou xel venaxow xupekeing, “Nimzayang ena wou xel wei yei vati wei xam ghe wei yo.
\v 24 En a neil wou xam bei, poropet ngenong me xel king embei gyei vati wei xam ghe wei yon, ekom xel se yei. Me xel embei ngo qayeeng tiwei xam ghe ngo yon, ekom xel se ngo.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei Samaria nimza ti yo
\p 
\v 25 Woyom xel wei lupeyei ngandoung en petieing wei Mose yo ti nale ghey bei daxe Yesu. Om teling, “Putoung, tyek a bong vati me na qou deing mapieing luta luta?”
\p 
\v 26 Yesu neil elox, “Xel byex vati eivek petieing? Wang pyaw ambei nya?”
\p 
\v 27 Moxo lewexe bei: “‘Wa laleim devind Tambiy Ngandoung wa xe Anutu is laleim dalus me is num pieing dalus me is wa nimkanzek dalus me is wa lumpeyei dalus,’ me ‘Wa laleim devind nimpapu nambei wa laleim vind xow o.’ ”
\p 
\v 28 Yesu neil elox wou e, “Wang neil e wo bombek, wang bong ambei nyon ond tyek wa mendei mapieing.”
\p 
\v 29 Ekom tambiy on embei talex xow wou Yesu bei e xe deing on bombek, om teling Yesu, “A ningpapu eti?”
\p 
\v 30 Woyom Yesu neil, “Moux ti la veil Yerusalem me lep me la Jeriko, gyeik la eno la eivek xel panaxeing memend. Xel kwax e xe teimb veil e me qou de leis e wo nol me e mey pesiv de xel la.
\v 31 De lek bouk kayon eno lumuki ti betiwou sakwaing kayon me la xonei, de gyeik moxo yei moux tiyon di yeip wou sakwaing om ghanaw e, de tanewou sakwaing nenyawes valu me la.
\v 32 Om Livai\f + \fr 10:32 \ft Livai yon velei wei Israelyeiw eno ti. Anutu beyal xel bei xel mi bong xuk eivek xomek qekueing ama.\f* ti is ambei nyon gyeik e lam tei wou beyeeng wei moxo di yeip lek o me yei e, eno ghanaw e me tanewou sakwaing nenyawes valu me la.
\v 33 Ekom Samaria ti di lam anghei ingwei moux on di yeip o, gyeik ingwei yei e eno lalei pyaxow en e.
\v 34 Moxo la wou e me taw wel me wain eivek xel qatyex on me tup en banis. Woyom zeim moux on me toung lek emaxow xe dongi, me qou me la eivek xomek wei vateivek o ti me mi yeiteyei e wo nimza.
\v 35 De yanyeing eno wong selewa yayuw wou xomek vateivek ma, de neil wou e bei, ‘Wa mi gweiteyei embo nimza, deka a noum on tyek a bong malew noum zeyi wa xe malew wei wang wong lek mapu yo.’
\p 
\v 36 “Wang wou naleim ambei nya, lal yal on eti nipapu ingwei la eivek xel panaxeing memend on?”
\p 
\v 37 Tambiy lupeyei ngandoung wei petieing o neil elox bei, “Tambiy tiwei lalei pyaxow me vind e yo.”
\p Yesu neil wou e, “Wang na me ghe na bong ambei nyon.”
\s1 Yesu toundei eivek Marata luw Maria bend
\p 
\v 38 Ka Yesu is e xe xel betiyeing di la wou sakwaing, eno la eivek beyeeng ti, wei vex ti lei Marata eno tax beeng wou e.
\v 39 Vexo li vex ti, lei Maria eno la dei paviy Tambiy Ngandoung vaxa me di ngo qayeeng wei e di neil o.
\v 40 Ekom Marata di wounalei ngenong en xuk dalus wei di yeiwou lul yaeing o. Vexo lam wou Yesu me teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wa seng wou kwam en ingwei a ling vex toundei bandaing de a maxow andi wong xuk ne? Neil wou e en e nam devind ay yo.”
\p 
\v 41 Ekom Tambiy Ngandoung lewexe lek bei, “Marata, Marata, wang di wou kwam ngenong me nimseik en lulul ngenong.
\v 42 Ekom lulti kawei wa bei qou eno Maria beyal vati wei nimza yo, om tyek xelti se teyeimbei bouveil e.”
\c 11
\s1 Yesu teyoxe xel en zeimeing mema
\p 
\v 1 Bouk ti eno Yesu la di zeimema nanghei danghei ti. Gyeik ingwei zeimema woy, eno e xe xel betiyeing ti neil wou e bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, teyoxe xa en zeimeing mema, nambei Yoan mi teyoxe e xe xel betiyeing o.”
\p 
\v 2 Moxo neil wou xel, “Gyeik ingwei xam ambei zeimemamim eno xam a neil ambei nye:
\q1 “‘Mang,
\q1 wa leim e mi mendei vambuing,
\q1 wa xe tete lalei enam.
\q1 
\v 3 Wa mi bong xa mi lul yaeing wou xa e teyei lek bouk titi.
\q1 
\v 4 Me wa semaleeng sewokeing wei xa yo,
\q2 en xa is ambei nyon xa mi semaleeng sewokeing wei xel sapa wong wou xa yo.
\q1 Me wa seng bong xa na eivek axeing.’”
\p 
\v 5 Woyom moxo neil wou xel, “Wangwei xam on ti xe gweleeng ti, me e la wou moxo eivek boukeing masenghoing me neil wou, ‘Gweleeng, wang bong belet yayal wou ay,
\v 6 en nambei a xe gweleeng ti mi tupwou sakwaing me lam wou ay, ekom lul yaeing wei ambei bong wou e eno ma.’
\p 
\v 7 “Woyom tambiy tiwei toundei lalei eno lewexe bei, ‘Wa seng bo pok wou ay. En xomek mya a xey woy, me yakyak di yeip is a lek zek. A se teyeimbei qandi lek me na bong lulul ti wou wang.’
\v 8 A neil wou xam, moxo tyek se qandi lek me bong belet wou e en nambei inyei e xe gweleeng o, qe en ingwei toungale nikanzek wou e yo, moxo tyek qandi me bong lulul wou e teyei lek ingwei e lalei vind o.
\p 
\v 9 “Om a neil wou xam: Xam teling on tyek bong wou xam, xam ghe gwimexe on tyek xam ghe gweiwou, xam ghe nyeis memamim lek qapomb on tyek natax en xam.
\v 10 En xel sapa wei mi teling en vatiyeiw eno xel mi qou, xel eti yeiw wei mi yimexe eno mi yeiwou, me eti yeiw wei mi leis memend lek qapomb eno mi tax.
\p 
\v 11 “Xam mayeiyeiw on, eti wangwei neum embei teling wang en woing ti, tyek wang bong myeiy wou e?
\v 12 O wangwei e teling en neughalus ti, tyek wang bong boklevek wou e?
\v 13 Nambei nyon xam wei sewokeing on, ekom xam ghe mi woulek lul nimza wei xam a being bong wou neumyeiw o. Yond xam ghe boulek bei xam Mamim wei toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu nei tyek bong Laweeng Vambuing wou xel wei mi teling e yo.”
\s1 Yesu me Belsebul
\p 
\v 14 Yesu tiy memo wei myatu yo veil tambiy ti. Gyeik ingwei memo la veil eno tambiy wei myatu eno luk, om moux alis vex ngenong yei me etek.
\v 15 Ekom xel on valu neil embei, “En nikanzek wei Belsebul, gyovaxa wei memo, eno e mi tiy memo nangya.”
\v 16 Xel valu axe moxo me neil, “Wang bong dee wei lulvako yo ti en xa boulek bei Anutu wong wang lam.”
\p 
\v 17 Yesu yei woueing nalei wei xel o me neil wou xel, “Tete lalei wei eti yeiw dembuma me wong vevek wou emaxow eno tyek bo nol, me wangwei xomek ti dembuma me bong vevek wouma eno tyek detei eivek.
\v 18 Wangwei Sandang xe xel dembuma me bong vevek wouma, on tyek e xe tete lalei bale nikanzek ambei nya? A neil tine en nambei xam ghe neimbei a tiy memo nangya Belsebul.
\v 19 Ekom wangwei a tiy memo na veil angya Belsebul nikanzek nei, ond eti mi vind xel wei xam o me xel mi tiy memo yon la myayaing? Om xel wei xam eno tyek talex wou xam bei qayeeng wei xam on se la wo bombek.
\v 20 Ekom wangwei a tiy memo nangya Anutu mema deyis, on Anutu xe tete lalei lam wou xam.
\p 
\v 21 “Wangwei moux wei nikanzek o ti bale zeyi beeng is lulul wei vevek o, on tyek e xe lulul a toumendei embo nimza.
\v 22 Ekom wangwei xelti nikanzek ghanaw e veil, on tyek na bo vevek wou e me bou lul vevek wei di qou nikanzek eivek o veil e, de dembu e ning lulul wou xel ba.
\p 
\v 23 “Xel eti yeiw wei se mindei is ay eno mi wo vevek wou ay, me eti yeiw wei se mi qeku moux alis vex wou is ay, eno mi tiy xel lala.”
\s1 Laweeng nilaxes loumelam no
\p 
\v 24 “Gyeik ingwei laweeng nilaxes ti lam myayaing veil moux ti, on tyek na ghavineeng eivek tembuing wei memiing ma veil o. Me gyei beyeeng wei embei na qou laweeng o, ek se gyeiwou ti. Woyom tyek na neil, ‘Tyek a nox me na eivek xomek wei a lam veil o.’
\v 25 Gyeik ingwei loum tei eno yei xomek xel pepa e wo vako me menyex wou.
\v 26 Woyom la qou laweeng amba lim yuw wei xel ghanaw e veil en kwa nol o, me xel la dei eivek xomek lalei tiyon. Om deing wei tambiy tiyon eno wo nol ghanaw ingwei tax o.”
\s1 Sakwaing wei xomaxoneing bo xeindlala yo
\p 
\v 27 Ka Yesu di neil ti beimambei ne, eno vex wei toundei eivek qekueing ama yon ti taxe la wou e, “Vex tiwei wou wang me wo luul wou wang eno e mi bo xeilala.”
\p 
\v 28 Moxo byex e mya leit bei, “Embong ondek xey a neimbei xel wei mi ngo Anutu xe xoulek me betiwou eno na mi bo xeindlala.”
\s1 Dee wei Yona yo
\p 
\v 29 Ka moux alis vex ngenong di lam me nyouk, om Yesu neil, “Xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne nilul ayang. Xel teling en embei gyei dee wei lulvako yo, ekom tyek xel se gyei ti, qe tyek xel gyei lulvako wei Yona yo.
\v 30 En Yona wong ambei dee wou Niniweyeiw, om nambei nyon is, Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek bong ambei dee wou xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne.
\p 
\v 31 “De kwin wei xonei eno tyek qandi lek bouk wei wongeing qayeeng me bo qayeeng en xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne me na neil xel xe nilul teyei, en lam anghei tembuing myasepu en embei ngo Salomo xe lupeyei, me gweimbeeng ne tambiy ti ghanaw Salomo eno toundei inye.
\v 32 Lek bouk wei ngoeing qayeeng eno xel wei Niniwe tyek qandi me bale me bo qayeeng en xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne me na neil xel xe nilul teyei, en xel pekwi xow gyeik ingwei Yona la neil xoulek o. Wei, gweimbeeng ne tambiy ti ghanaw Yona veil eno lam toundei inye.
\s1 Lam wei neing o
\p 
\v 33 “Xelti se mi byex eivek lam me toung eivek beyeeng wei embei bund xeiyaing o, o toung eivek deng lalei. Qe xel mi toung leklam vaxa gheyapu, om xel wei la lalei eno mi yei xeiyaing.
\v 34 Wa mamghalus on lam wei wa neing o. Wangwei wa mamghalus luw xouing a toumendei embo nimza, on tyek wa neing dalus na pup en xeiyaing. Ekom wangwei luw xouing bo nol on tyek wa neing na pup en mapetok ngandoung.
\v 35 Om wang gweiteyei, en xeiyaing wei toundei eivek wang on se bo mapetok.
\v 36 Nambei nyon wangwei wa neing dalus on na pup en xeiyaing, me boukeing e ma veil wa neing danghei ti, on wa neing dalus wo xeiyaing, nambei ingwei xeiyaing wei lam mi byex lek wang o.”
\s1 Kwa nilul wei xel Parisi me putoung wei petieing o
\p 
\v 37 Gyeik ingwei Yesu neil xoulek ma yo, Parisi ti teling bei e na gya is e, om moxo eivek la lalei me la yeip pepeeng lek zek me ya.
\v 38 Ekom Parisi yei ingwei Yesu se lipek atax ekom ya, om di wounalei ngenong.
\p 
\v 39 Woyom Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou e, “Xam Parisi ghe mi sekweyexe mayamya luw dipek demi, ekom xam laleimim on pup en kwa eivekeing me nilul.
\v 40 Xam xomaxoneing on bandol! Beip tambiy tiwei betiy lulul on demi eno se betiy lalei is?
\v 41 Ekom xam ghe bong vati wei toundei eivek dipek lalei eno wou xel wei kanyo yo, on tyek xam ghe bo vako yang wou Anutu manghalus.
\p 
\v 42 “Xam Parisi ghe gwaleeng amim en nimaying, en xam ghe mi wong ti eivek xoumeeng xoing senyeing me lulul eivek xuk wei xam o, ekom xam ghe saing kwa wei bombek me kwa wei lalei vineing Anutu yo, om xam betiwou kwa ti beimambei yon de xam ghe bong luw xouing bo nimza.
\p 
\v 43 “Xam Parisi ghe gwaleeng amim en nimaying, en nambei xam laleimim mi vind sia nimza wei xomek qekueing ama yo, me xam ambei xel a mi neil bendiyeing teiv wou xam eivek beyeeng wei xel mi wo vateivek lek lulul o.
\p 
\v 44 “Xam ghe gwaleeng amim en nimaying, en xam ghe xok leiveeng meyeing xupekeing wei xomaxoneing qeilek en xel se woulek.”
\p 
\v 45 Xel wei lupeyei ngandoung en petieing wei Mose yo ti neil wou Yesu, “Putoung, gyeik wang neil qayeeng ambei nyon, eno wang neil xa is.”
\p 
\v 46 Yesu byex e vya leit bei, “Xam wei lumimpeyei ngandoung en petieing wei Mose eno xam ghe gwaleeng amim en nimaying, en nambei xam ghe mi qou lul nimaying me ghe toung lek xomaxoneing me xel mi wo pok lek qaleing, dom xam memamim ti se mi vind xel.”
\p 
\v 47 “Xam ghe gwaleeng amim en nimaying, en nambei xam ghe mi ev leiveeng meyeing wei xel poropet, wei bumyeiw leis xel mey o.
\v 48 Om xam ghe talex lek bei xam ghe lenghek lek vati wei bumyeiw wong o, xel leis xel poropet mey, de xam ghe kwelexe xel xe eeng wei meyeing o.
\p 
\v 49 “En nambei tiyon, om eivek Anutu xe lupeyei nimza eno neil, ‘Tyek a bong xel poropet me sinaleyeiw wou xel, tyek xel nyeis xel valu mey de bo nol wou xel valu.’
\v 50 Nambei nyon xam xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne tyek na qou myaveweeng lek gyand wei xel poropet, wei xel leis gyeik bouk wei Anutu toung tembuing o,
\v 51 nanghei Abel gyand me e mi la Sakalias gyand, tiwei xel leis e mey eivek qeind aluw xomek vambuing senghoing o. Ee, a neil wou xam, xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne tyek na qou myaveweeng tiyon dalus.
\p 
\v 52 “Xam wei lumimpeyei ngandoung en petieing wei Mose yo ghe gwaleeng amim en nimaying. En xam ghe zeim ki wei qoueing lupeyei nimza yo veil. Xam venaxow seng la eivek, de xam ghe nale zeyi xel wei embei na eivek o.”
\p 
\v 53 Gyeik ingwei Yesu la veil inyon, eno xel Parisi me xel putoung wei petieing o laleind wo nol wou e, om xel nale zeyi e nangya teling wei nikanzek o.
\v 54 Xel di axe e en embei bo qayeeng en e, en ingwei e neil qayeeng ti na sewok o.
\c 12
\s1 Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en Parisi xe tyonyeing
\p 
\v 1 Dekalekom xomaxoneing tausen ngenongakes qekuma, omva xel di qeilekama, om Yesu neil wou e xe xel betiyeing atax bei, “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en yis wei Parisi mi wong o, en xel on myend yuw.
\v 2 Lul dalus wei xel vun eno tyek gyeip yaing wou xel, me lul dalus wei mi yeip xupekeing eno tyek nam myayaing.
\v 3 Qayeeng dalus wei xam ghe neil eivek mapetok eno tyek moux alis vex a ngo wou xeiyaing. Me qayeeng dalus wei xam ghe ngoung wouma eivek xomek lalei, eno tyek xel bale lek xomek demi me taxe na wou xel sapa.”
\s1 Xomaxoneing a mi gyaleeng en Anutu venaxow
\p 
\v 4 “Xam wei axe gweleeng o, a neil wou xam bei, xam seng gwaleeng en xomaxoneing wei mi leis neing mey yo, dom tyek xel se nox me na bong lulti no.
\v 5 Ekom tyek a talex wou xam en tambiy tiwei xam a mi gwaleeng en e yo. Xam waleeng en e tiwei tyek nyeis neing a mey, dekakom e xe nikanzek teyeimbei banex xam ghe na eivek nenyex wei luta yo. Ee, a neil wou xam, xam ghe gwaleeng en e.
\v 6 Beip xel mi wong vateivek lek menek tetoung lim en selewa gyand nayak yuw? Ekom Anutu nalei se mi ma xel on titi.
\v 7 Neing, xam lumim velus on Anutu pyaw memawou dalus. Xam seng gwaleeng, en xam ghe ghanaw tetoung ngenongakes veil.
\s1 Xe nind se gyaleeng en neileing bei Yesu xe xey
\p 
\v 8 “A neil wou xam, xelti embei neilteyei wou moux alis vex en ay, ond Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek na neil e teyei wou Anutu xe angela.
\v 9 Ekom xelti embei dax a vun wou moux alis vex, ond tyek a dax e vun wou Anutu xe angela mendghalus.
\v 10 Me xel sapa wei embei neil qayeeng nilul lek Xomaxoneing Neu Moux ond tyek Anutu semaleeng sewokeing wei xel o. Ekom xelti embei baluk yak lek Laweeng Vambuing on tyek Anutu se semaleeng sewokeing wei e yo veil.
\p 
\v 11 “Gyeik ingwei xel a qou xam me na eivek xomek qekueing ama wou xel gyovaxa me xel wei lei ngandoung o, ond xam seng bo lalei maying bei, ‘Tyek xa bale zeyi xow ambei nya, o tyek xa neil vati?’
\v 12 Lek bouk kayon eno Laweeng Vambuing tyek talex wou xam en vati wei xam ambei neil o.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei lulul ana ti wo kwa wei bandol o
\p 
\v 13 Xel wei toundei eivek qendu ngandoung on ti neil wou e, “Putoung, wa neil wou a ling en e pum lulul wei mang ghanaw eno is ay.”
\p 
\v 14 Yesu neil elox, “Moux, eti beyal ay en ngoeing qayeeng bei a pum lulul eivek senghoing wou muw?”
\v 15 Woyom moxo neil wou xel, “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow, en xam seng gweimam lek lulul leimalei. En mapieing wei xomaxoneing eno se toundei eivek e xe lulul ngenong on.”
\p 
\v 16 Me moxo neil wou xel en qayeeng pakeing tine: “Tambiy wei lulul ana eno xe tembuing wong lulul ngenong wo neing nimza.
\v 17 Moxo venaxow wounalei bei, ‘Om tyek a bo vati? A xomek ma en ingwei ambei qeku a xe lulul yaeing eivek o.’
\p 
\v 18 “Woyom moxo neil embei, ‘Inye vati wei ambei bong o. Tyek a lelolexe xomek yaeing, dom na dev ingwei ngandoung ngandoung o, me nanghei inyon eno tyek a qeku a xe lulul neing dalus me a xe lulul nimzamza dalus eivek.
\v 19 Me tyek a neil wou xow bei, “A teyei woy, a xe lulul nimzamza ngenong a toung e toundei teyei lek vakovek qeskes. Tyek a mendei embo nimza, me mendi bong mangha me na num lek me na bong xeinglala.” ’
\p 
\v 20 “Ekom Anutu neil wou e, ‘Wa bandol! Boukeing tine tyek wa mey. De woyom tyek eti na qou lulul wei wang mi qekuwou xow on?’
\p 
\v 21 “Tiyon tyek na teyei lek xel eti yeiw wei mi qeku lulul wou venaxow o de se wo lulul ana en lulul wei Anutu yo.”
\s1 Wa seng bounaleim ngenong
\p 
\v 22 Woyom Yesu neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei, “A neil wou xam, xam seng bou naleimim en mapieing wei xam o me na neimbei, ‘Tyek xey a gha vati?’ O xam seng bou naleimim en neing wei xam o me na neimbei, ‘Tyek xey a byex vati?’
\v 23 Mapieing on ghanaw lulul yaeing me neing on ghanaw teimb.
\v 24 Xam ghe gwei aoho xel se mi wong xuk o qeku lulul yaeing. Xel se mi ev xomek yaeing, o xomek wei qekueing lulul yaeing eivek o, qe Anutu mi vet xel. De xam xomaxoneing on ghe ghanaw menek veil.
\v 25 Wangwei xam ti me di bou naleimim ngenong nei, on tyek wa tetulexe seivma nayaka wou wa xe mapieing?
\v 26 Wangwei xam seng bong lulul nayak ambei nyon, ond xam ghe di wou naleimim ngenong en lulul valu betiy en va?
\p 
\v 27 “Xam ghe gwei qapaing, bei xel mi tyip ambei nya. Xel se mi wong pok, o xel se mi duw teimb. Ekom a neil wou xam Salomo byex e xe teimb nimzamza, ekom se wo nimza nambei qapaing beimambei ne ti.
\v 28 Wangwei Anutu mi vunekwou qapaing wei mi nale lek beyeeng nambei nyon, wei toungale gweimbeeng de yanyeing eno tyek xel banex ena eivek nenyex, om lu vamva eno Anutu se mi vunekwou xam? Xam xe wongeingis on nayaka.
\v 29 Me xam seng bou naleimim ngenong bei tyek xam ghe gwa vati, me tyek xam a num vati. Om xam seng bou naleimim ngenong.
\v 30 Xel amba wei tembuing tambak o mi wong me yei en xel embei qou lulul tiyon dalus, de xam mamim woulek lulul wei xam naleimim vind o.
\v 31 Ekom xam a mi gwimexe Anutu xe tete lalei bole, dekakom e bong lulul on lek mapu wou xam is ambei inyon.
\s1 Kwa wei qekueing lulul nimza yo
\p 
\v 32 “Xam sipsip neuyeiw nayak on seng gwaleeng, en xam mamim lalei wo nimza en embei bong tete lalei wou xam.
\v 33 Xam ghe bong vateivek lek lulul wei xam o de ghe bong malew on wou xel wei kanyo yo. Xam a qou xam xe vaxak malew wei se mi wo nol o. Xam qeku lulul nimzamza wei tyoung gheyapu wei mindei luta yo, nanghei inyei xel panaxeing se mi la paviy, de xevek se mi qateiv.
\v 34 Nanghei ingwei wa xe lulul nimzamza toundei ghei nei, eno wa laleim tyek na mendei is nanghei inyon.
\s1 Xel wei mi nale me yeiwou xow o
\p 
\v 35 “Xam davex qaeing lek me ghe gweiwou xow en xuk de mendi gweiteyei xam xe lam en emdi tum,
\v 36 nambei xel moux wei mi a xe xel xe teiv wei embei noum nanghei mata ngandoung wei iingama yo. En kandek gyeik ingwei embei noum nyeis mema lek qapomb, ond xel a tax qapomb daing en e.
\v 37 Inyon tyek bo nimza en xel xukxe wei toundei me yeiwou xow me axe xel xe teiv gyeik ingwei e noum me gyei xel o. A neil wou xam zonghek, teiv on tyek bunekwou xow en teimb wei xuk o de na neil wou xel me xel mendei qendu ti lek lelek de bet xel.
\v 38 Xel xukxe wei toundei me axe xel xe teiv wei loum yei xel yeiwou xow, o gyeik ingwei la boukeing masenghoing, o ingwei xeiyaing nexla yo ond xel bo xeindlala.
\v 39 Ekom xam ghe boulek tine bei wangwei xomek ma boulek seivma wei xel panaxeing embei nam o, on tyek se bong xel dembu e beeng me na lalei.
\v 40 Xam is ambei nyon xam ghe gweiwou xow boy, en Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek nam lek seivma gyeik ingwei xam seng wou naleimim bei tyek nam o.”
\p 
\v 41 Petele teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung, inye wang di neil qayeeng pakeing on wou xa maxow o wou xel sapa?”
\p 
\v 42 Tambiy Ngandoung lewexe me neil embei, “Xukxe eti ingwei lupeyei nimza me mi wong xuk wo nimza yo? Wei e xe teiv beyal e la tax bei e gyeiteyei e xe xukxe me na mi dembu lulul yaeing wou xel lek bouk bombek.
\v 43 Wangwei xukxe tiyon di wong xuk me teiv loumelam yei e di wong o yond embo xeilala.
\v 44 A neil wou xam zonghek, moxo tyek beyal xukxe tiyon bo lei ngandoung me gyeiteyei e xe lulul dalus.
\v 45 Ekom xukxe tiyon se neil wou xow bei, ‘Axe teiv la dei enden de se loum,’ om di leis xel xukxe moux me xukxe vex de di ya me num me num memiing nikanzek me wo nol.
\v 46 Xukxe tiyon xe teiv tyek noum lek bouk ti gyeik ingwei se di toung ma en e yo me seivma wei se woulek o. Teiv tyek qateiv xukxe tiyon bo tiptip me na toung e na is xel wei se mi wongis o.
\p 
\v 47 “Xukxe wei woulek e xe teiv lalei, ekom se yeiwou xow me se wong vati wei e xe teiv neil on tyek xel nyeis e lumama.
\v 48 Ekom xukxe wei se woulek e xe teiv lalei ekom wong lulti sewok eno tyek na qou myaveweeng de xel nyeis e nayaka. Xel wei qou lulul ngenong eno tyek xel bong lulul ngenong nox zeyi. Wangwei xel bong lulul ngenong wou tambiy ti on tyek xel teling bei embong lulul ngenong nox zeyi.
\s1 Se lalei vevopeing qe dembueing ama
\p 
\v 49 “A lam me na qou nenyex me na lam me na nex e la lek tembuing, de a laleing vind bei e tum.
\v 50 Ambei qou lipekeing nelu ti ekom a laleing wo nimaying en a seng ghei qou.
\v 51 Xam ghe wou naleimim bei a qou lalei vevopeing me na lam lek tembuing? Ma, a neil wou xam bei a lam en ambei dembu xomaxoneing.
\v 52 Dom gweimbeeng ne me e mi na, eno moux alis vex lim e toumendei eivek xomek ti, ond tyek xel dembuma na yuw, yal tyek bo nol wou yuw de yuw tyek bo nol wou yal.
\v 53 Tyek xel dembuma, ma tyek bo nol wou neu moux de neu moux tyek bo nol wou ma, ta tyek bo nol wou neu vex de neu vex tyek bo nol wou ta, yeing avexta tyek bo nol wou yeing vexawo de yeing vexawo tyek bo nol wou yeing avexta.”
\s1 Xomaxoneing se yeimend wou vatiyeiw wei di qandi lek o qes
\p 
\v 54 Woyom Yesu neil wou moux alis vex ngenong on bei, “Gyeik ingwei xam ghe wei laxap ti lam tyip inya xeinei, lutika eno xam ghe neimbei ‘Luing tyek nam,’ eno luing lam.
\v 55 Me gyeik ingwei laweeng vei nanghei inya xonei eno xam ghe neimbei, ‘Inye bouk wei seiv tyek bo myavanei yo,’ eno wo neing lek.
\v 56 Xam wei myamim yuw o! Xam ghe mi wei mamim wou lulul wei tembuing ne me tyoung o. Nambei nya ekom xam seng wei mamim wou lulul wei di qandi lek gweimbeeng ne yo?
\p 
\v 57 “Nambei nya wa seng mi wou kwam en xow me ghe woulek bei vati la wo bombek bei wang bong?
\v 58 Wangwei wam di na wou sakwaing is tambiy wei embei bong qayeeng en wang wou tambiy wei mi zeim qayeeng yon wang bo nimkanzek me menyex wou qayeeng is e. Enok na qou wang me na wou tambiy wei mi zeim qayeeng de zeim qayeeng me bo wang na wou beyeiv de beyeiv na toung wang na eivek xeitueing.
\v 59 A neil wou wang, wa seng teyei being na myayaing qe ka wang bo malew dalus wei xel lax wou wang o zeyi bole.”
\c 13
\s1 Xam pekwi xow o xam a qou nilul
\p 
\v 1 Lek bouk kayon eno xel valu wei toundei inyon eno neil wou Yesu en ingwei Pailat leis moux wei Galili nei valu mey gyeik xel di sei xound o. Me xel gyand semaleeng is leliy gyand.
\v 2 Yesu neil wou xel bei, “Xam ghe wou naleimim bei xel Galili yon wong sewokeing ngenong ghanaw Galili valu dalus omek lulti yon qandi wou xel?
\v 3 Ma, a neil wou xam, xam pekwi xow, ek na ma on xam dalus tyek na mey is ambei nyon.
\v 4 De nambei nya en 18 moux alis vex wei xomek vaxading pek me leis xel mey anghei Siloam o? Xam ghe wou naleimim bei xel wong sewokeing ghanaw xel valu dalus wei toundei eivek Yerusalem nei?
\v 5 A neil wou xam bei, ma! Ekom wangwei xam se pekwi xow, on tyek xam dalus na mey is ambei nyon.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei xax basunghek se vuk o
\p 
\v 6 Woyom Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine, “Tambiy ti ev xax basunghek eivek e xe xuk wain, me moxo la en embei gyei xax on neing wei toukami lek o, ekom se yei neing ti,
\v 7 om neil wou tambiy wei mi yeiteyei xuk wain o, ‘Eivek vakovek qes yal eno a mi lam a xei xax basunghek on neing, ekom a se xei neing ti, om vuv veil! Nambei nya e puw tembuing denzi bandaing?’
\p 
\v 8 “Ekom xukxe neil e lox wou bei, ‘Teiv, wong e toukale vakovek qes tine is me a ev tembuing vivekwou me na toung lul denzi yo eivek e qes.
\v 9 Wangwei e buk neing lek vakovek qes nge yus on nimza, ek na ma ond wang buv veil.’”
\s1 Vex demi qendu ti wo nimzalek Sabat
\p 
\v 10 Lek Sabat ti eno Yesu di teyoxe xel eivek xomek qekueing ama ti,
\v 11 me vex ti toundei inyon, eno laweeng ti wong e demi wo qendu teyei lek vakovek qes 18. Me vexo se teyeimbei bale bombek no.
\v 12 Gyeik ingwei Yesu yei vexo eno taxe e lam de neil wou e, “Vex, wa xe vanei ma veil wang.”
\v 13 Woyom moxo li mema lek e, de lutika eno vexo nale bombek me di sanghoxe Anutu.
\p 
\v 14 Ekom gyovaxa wei xomek qekueing ama eno lalei wo vanei, en ingwei Yesu wong vanei wo nimzalek Sabat o, om neil wou xomaxoneing bei, “Inye bouk wei wongeing xuk eno limti toundei, om xam ghe nam en e gyeiwou xam lek bouk on ti, ek se lek bouk wei Sabat o.”
\p 
\v 15 Tambiy Ngandoung lewexe wou e, “Xam wei myamim yuw o, xam titi seng la mi tul yis veil xam xe manghaxo o dongi lek Sabat eivek xomek leliy, me dandiy me la bei na bong memiing wou xel?
\v 16 De vex tine nye Apraham neu, Sandang qo e xoun teyei lek vakovek qes 18, om se teyeimbei a tul lul tiwei qo e xoun on lek bouk wei Sabat o de ena nivax?”
\p 
\v 17 Gyeik ingwei moxo neil tine, eno xel dalus wei pesek e yon ninyaleeng, de xomaxoneing wo xeindlala en lul nimza maseim dalus wei Yesu wong o.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei mastet vei me yis o
\p 
\v 18 Woyom Yesu teling bei, “Anutu xe tete lalei teyei lek vati? Tyek a neil lek vati?
\v 19 Inyon nambei mastet vei, wei tambiy ti qou me ev eivek e xe xuk yaeing. Mastet on ling me wo ngandoung nambei xax teta me menek lam mi qo lewis lek memama.”
\p 
\v 20 Moxo lox teling no, “Tyek a neil Anutu xe tete lalei lek vati?
\v 21 Inyon nambei yis wei vex ti qou me semaleeng is palawa ngandoung wei dipekta yo, me e wong palawa dalus on vuk lek.”
\s1 Qapomb wei nayak o
\p 
\v 22 Woyom Yesu di tupwou sakwaing me la Yerusalem. Om la eivek beyeeng dalus me beyeeng nayak me teyoxe xomaxoneing.
\v 23 Xelti teling wou embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, inye xomaxoneing nuyuw tyek Anutu devind xel?”
\p Moxo neil wou xel,
\v 24 “Xam ghe bong nimkanzek me ghe na eivek xomek mya wei nayak o. A neil wou xam bei, xel ngenongakes wong me yei en embei na eivek, ekom xel se teyei.
\v 25 Gyeik xomek ma qandi lek me xey qapomb zeyi, tyek xam bale myayaing me ghe nyeis memamim lek qapomb me taxe bei, ‘Teiv, tax qapomb veil xa.’
\p “Ekom tyek na neil wou xam bei, ‘A loung en xam, xam ghe lam anghei inya?’
\p 
\v 26 “Woyom tyek xam a neil wou bei, ‘Xa xa me na num is wang, me wang nale eivek xa xe sakwaing mema nayak me ghe teyoxe wou xa.’
\p 
\v 27 “Ekom moxo tyek na neil enoum bei, ‘A loung en xam, xam ghe lam anghei inya. Xam la veil ay en xam on ghe wong kwa nilul!’
\p 
\v 28 “Tyek xam ghe deeng me zanga newoumim bo nyiknyik nanghei inyon, gyeik ingwei xam ghe gwei Apraham, me Isaka me Yakop me xel poropet dalus eivek Anutu xe tete lalei yo, dom xam venaxow eno tyek Anutu banex xam ghe na myayaing.
\v 29 Xomaxoneing tyek nam anghei ninei me xeinei me punei me xonei, me tyek nam mendei me gya mata eivek Anutu xe tete lalei.
\v 30 De ngo le, xel wei dei yus eno tyek na mendei mya de xel wei dei mya eno tyek nox mendei yus.”
\s1 Yesu lalei pyaxow en Yerusalem
\p 
\v 31 Lek bouk kayon eno Parisi valu lam neil wou Yesu bei, “Wang na bange veil beyeeng ne en Herot embei nyeis wa mey.”
\p 
\v 32 Yesu neil elox wou xel, “Xam ghe na neil wou naw bemeeng on bei, ‘Gweimbeeng me yanyeing eno tyek a tiy memo na me na bong xomaxoneing wei vanei yo bo nimzalek. De bouk yal eno tyek a bong axe xuk dalus na ma.’
\v 33 Ee gweimbeeng me yanyeing, me yanyeing nge eno tyek a na, me neing ayang inye se nimza bei poropet ti e mey anghei myayaing veil Yerusalem!
\p 
\v 34 “Yerusalem, Yerusalem, wang mi leis xel poropet mey, me ghe nex xel wei Anutu wong e lam wou wang o en qakous, taxombouk eno a mi wong en ambei qeku neumyeiw dalus lekti nambei qouklex ta mi qeku neuyeiw eivek banis o. Ekom xam laleimim se mi vind.
\v 35 Wei, kale tyek wa bam lelolexe me gyeip bandaing. A neil wou xam bei, tyek xam seng gwei a no, qe ka xam a neimbei, ‘Anutu bong mata wou tambiy tiwei lam lek Tambiy Ngandoung lei yo.’”
\c 14
\s1 Yesu wong tambiy nivukeing ti wo nimzalek Sabat
\p 
\v 1 Sabat ti, eno Yesu la ya eivek xomek wei lei ngandoung wei Parisi eno ti, de xel di yei e teyei teyei.
\v 2 Tambiy nivukeing ti eno toundei mya en e nanghei inyon.
\v 3 Yesu teling wou xel Parisi is xel lupeyei ngandoung wei petieing o bei, “Beip inyei teyei lek bei xey a bong xel wei vanei eno bo nimzalek Sabat, o ma?”
\v 4 Ekom xel toundei kanzek. Om zeim tambiy on me wong e wo nimzalek de wong e la.
\p 
\v 5 Woyom moxo teling xel. “Wangwei xam on ti neum moux ti o manghaxo ti deivek leiveeng memiing lek bouk wei Sabat o, on tyek wa seng na puw enoum myayaing daing?”
\v 6 De xel se neil lulti.
\s1 Yesu teyoxe bei xomaxoneing a mi beoux xow
\p 
\v 7 Gyeik Yesu yei xel wei di lam en mata eno di beyal beyeeng nimza wei mya yo, om moxo neil qayeeng pakeing tine wou xel:
\v 8 “Gyeik xelti embei taxe wang en mata wei iingama yo, on wa seng na mendei lek leitata bend. Enok ambei nyon tambiy wei e xe mata yon taxe tambiy nge wei lei ghanaw wang o.
\v 9 Wangwei tambiy wei taxe muw on, tyek nam a neil wou wang, ‘Wong beyeeng wei wang on wou tambiy tine,’ woyom tyek wa nim gyaleeng de ghe na mendei demiyang.
\v 10 Ekom wangwei xelti taxe wang en mata ond wang na mendei demi, deka tambiy tiwei taxe wang o nam, ond tyek na neil wou wang, ‘Gweleeng wang na mendei lek beyeeng nimza wei mya nei.’ Woyom tyek wa qou leim ngandoung eivek laxousyeiw dalus mend.
\v 11 En xel sapa wei mi qoxexow eno tyek Anutu beoux xel, de eti yeiw wei mi beoux xow eno Anutu tyek sanghoxe xel.”
\p 
\v 12 Woyom Yesu neil wou tambiy tiwei taxe e yo bei, “Wangwei wang bong mata ti nei, on wa se taxe wa xe gweleeng, o limyeiw o nimpapu, o xel wei lulul ana wei wa bam qes o. Wangwei wang bong ambei nyon nei on tyek xel taxe wang nox me na gwa is xel no, ond inyon xel wong xouveing loum zeyi wou wang.
\v 13 Ekom gyeik ingwei wa being bo mata, yon wa taxe xel kanyo, xel wei bezomb o, xel wei vaxa nol o me matekeing o.
\v 14 On tyek wa mendei eivek mata lalei. Xel on tyek se bong xouveing noum wou wang no. Qe Anutu tyek bo xouveing noum wou wang gyeik ingwei xel wei bombek o embei qandi lek veil meyeing o.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei mata ngandoung o
\p 
\v 15 Gyeik xel wei di ya is e lek lelek on ti ngo inyon om neil wou Yesu, “Mata e gyeip wou tambiy wei tyek na gya eivek Anutu xe tete lalei yo.”
\p 
\v 16 Yesu neil elox wou e bei, “Tambiy ti embei bong mata ngandoung ti me wong qayeeng la wou xel ngenongakes.
\v 17 Lek bouk kawei mata eno moxo wong e xe xukxe la neil wou xel wei wong qayeeng la wou xel o. Om xukxe neil, ‘Wei, xam lam. En gweimbeeng xa menyex wou lulul dalus woy.’
\p 
\v 18 “Ekom xel dalus pakei me neil embei se na. Ti myaxeeng neil embei, ‘A mouk a xouv xuk yaeing ti, om tyek a na ghei, om tyek a se nak.’
\p 
\v 19 “Nge neil embei, ‘A mouk a xouv manghaxo xoumeeng om ambei na teyoxe xel me na ghei bei xel wo xuk wo nimza, om tyek a se nak.’
\p 
\v 20 “Ti neil embei, ‘A mouk a ii vex om tyek a se nak.’
\p 
\v 21 “Xukxe loumelam neil inyon wou e xe teiv. Woyom xomek ma yon lalei wo vanei me luk niseikeing wou e xe xukxe, ‘Wang na daing me betiwou sakwaing ngandoung me nayak eivek beyeeng tine me na qou xel kanyo, me xel wei bezomb o, me xel wei mend tekeing o, me xel wei vaxend nol o.’
\p 
\v 22 “Xukxe neil embei, ‘Teiv, a wong ambei ingwei wang neil o, ekom xomek lalei valu nanghei di yeip bandaing.’
\p 
\v 23 “Woyom teiv on neil wou e xe xukxe, ‘Wang na betiwou sakwaing mema mema me betiwou tete wei xuk o, me baluk nikanzek wou moux alis vex me na qou xel me ghe nam en kandek axe xomek e pup.
\v 24 A neil wou xam bei, xel wei a wong qayeeng la wou xel eno ti tyek se daxe a xe mata nayak ti.’”
\s1 Wang bounaleim bo nimza bole ekom betiy Yesu
\p 
\v 25 Xel qendu ngandoung di betiy Yesu, om pekwi ma me neil wou xel:
\v 26 “Wangwei xelti embei nam wou ay, ekom se toung demi wou ma luw ta me venei is neuyeiw, me li moux me li vex, ee, de emaxow xe mapieing, on tyek se bong ambei a xe betiyeing.
\v 27 Me xelti embei se qalei e xe xax pepeeng me betiy ay, eno tyek se bong ambei a xe betiyeing.
\p 
\v 28 “Wangwei xel wei xam on ti embei dev xomek vaxading ti. On tyek se na mendei tax me gyei e xe malew wei embei dev xomek o teyei, bei malew teyeimbei tyek dev xomek ema?
\v 29 Ek wangwei se bong ambei nyon nei, qe balax mundeeng bandaing, de se teyeimbei dev epyap, on tyek xel sapa wei yei eno bo vyend wou e,
\v 30 me na neimbei, ‘Tambiy tine ev xomek atax ekom se teyeimbei dev epyap.’
\p 
\v 31 “O wangwei king ti embei na bong vevek wou king nge, on tyek se mendei tax me bounalei bo nimza, beip emaxow xe xel vevek on 10,000, de king nge yon lam is 20,000, om embei gyei bei e teyei?
\v 32 Ek wangwei bounalei bei se teyei, on tyek beyal xel valu na baluk is king nge yon nanghei ingwei di lam dingta yo me teling wou e en xel gyeiwou qayeeng wei embei bo lalei vevopeing o.
\v 33 Nambei nyon is, wangwei xel wei xam on ti embei se toung demi wou e xe lulul dalus, on tyek se mendei nambei a xe betiyeing.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei mileeng o
\p 
\v 34 “Mileeng on nimza, ekom wangwei nenyeing na veil, on tyek wang bong enox bo nenyeing ambei nya no?
\v 35 Mileeng ambei nyon eno se nimza bei xey a toung eivek tembuing wei xuk o is manghaxo xei qe wa banex ena.
\p “Xomaxoneing ti nenya bale lek e, ond wong e ngo qayeeng tine.”
\c 15
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei sipsip lati yo
\p 
\v 1 Xel wei mi qou takis o me xel wei sewokeing o xel xouing dalus la qekuma vivekwou Yesu me di ngo e xe qayeeng.
\v 2 Ekom xel Parisi lis xel putoung wei petieing o neil e, “Tambiy tine mi qou xel wei sewokeing o is xeilala me mi ya is xel.”
\p 
\v 3 Woyom Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine wou xel:
\v 4 “Wangwei xam on ti xe sipsip 100, ekom ti nati on tyek se bong 99 on na toumbale eivek beyeeng wei myasapa yo dom na gyimexe tiwei lati yo deka gyeiwou le?
\v 5 Me gyeik ingwei yeiwou eno wo xeilala de qalei lek ghandiwek me la beyeeng.
\v 6 Woyom taxe e xe xel gweleeng me nipapu wei toundei paviy e yo qekuma me neil wou xel, ‘Xam ghe bong xeimlala is ay, en a xeiwou axe sipsip wei lati yo.’
\v 7 A neil wou xam eivek sakwaing ambei nyon eno xeilala ngandoung mi qandi eivek tyoung gheyapu nei en sewokeing ti embei pekwi xow o, ghanaw 99 xomaxoneing wei bombek me xuk ma en ingwei embei pekwi xow o.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei malew lati yo
\p 
\v 8 “O wangwei vex ti xe malew selewa xoumeeng ekom ti nati. On tyek vexo se byex eivek lam, me pepa xomek me gyimexe embo nimza deka gyeiwou le?
\v 9 Me gyeik ingwei vexo yeiwou, eno taxe e xe gweleeng me nipapu qekuma me neil embei, ‘Xam ghe bong xeimlala is ay, en a xeiwou axe selewa wei lati yo.’
\v 10 Eivek sakwaing ambei nyon, eno a neil wou xam, xeilala ngandoung mi qandi wou Anutu xe xel angela mendghalus en ingwei sewokeing ti pekwi xow o.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei yak moux ti lati yo
\p 
\v 11 Yesu neil no, “Inye tambiy ti neu moux yayuw.
\v 12 Nge moun neil wou ma bei, ‘Mang, wa pum wa xe lulul na yuw me ghe bong veweeng wei wambei bong eno wou ay.’ Woyom moxo pum e xe lulul la yuw wou luw.
\p 
\v 13 “Se denlek qe neu nge ghavis qou e xe lulul dalusateiv me la tembuing ba wei dingta yo. Nanghei inyon eno saing ning malew lek kwa nilul wei mi wong o.
\v 14 Ka e saing ning lulul la ma, eno maxep ngandoung qandi wou tembuing sapa tiyon, om maxepya moxo.
\v 15 Om moxo la wong xuk wou tambiy wei tembuing qes o ti, tambiy tiyon wong e la mi yeiteyei e xe xel bok me mi vet.
\v 16 Moxo bambou ma om embei gya pil ninavi wei bok di ya yon, ekom xelti se wong lulul ti wou e.
\p 
\v 17 “Gyeik ingwei moxo lu yeipyaing en xow om neil, ‘Mang xe xukxe dalus di qou lulul yaeing ngenong, de nanghei inye eno ambei mey en maxep.
\v 18 Tyek a nox me na wou mang me na neil wou e bei: Mang, a wo sewokeing wou Anutu me wou wang is.
\v 19 Me a se nimza bei wa taxe neum lek ay, qe wang gwei ay ambei wa xe xukxe ti.’
\v 20 Om moxo qandi lek me la wou ma.
\p “Ekom gyeik ingwei nanghei di la dingta eno ma yei e me lalei pyaxow en e. Om moxo veimya me la wou neu me sei mema eivek e de sesuvexe e.
\p 
\v 21 “De neu neil wou e, ‘Mang, a wo sewokeing wou Anutu me wou wang is. A se nimza bei wa taxe neum lek ay.’
\p 
\v 22 “Ekom ma neil wou e xe xel xukxe bei, ‘Xam la daing! Me qou teimb ding nimza me byex lek e. De byex ring lek e mema deyis me byex vaxalambes lek e vaxa.
\v 23 De xam ghe na qou manghaxo wei ling tata nei me ghe nyeis e mey. En xey a bo mata me na gha me na bong xeindlala.
\v 24 En a neung ne mey ekom loum wou xey mapieing no. Moxo lati ekom xey a xeiwou e.’ Om xel wo mata me di wo xeindlala.
\p 
\v 25 “Dekalekom neu touk la toundei eivek xuk, gyeik ingwei lam paviy xomek, moxo ngo yengheeng me aweing.
\v 26 Om moxo taxe xukxe ti lam me teling wou e, ‘Xel di wong vati?’
\v 27 Xukxe neil wou bei, ‘Lim loumelam om mam leis manghaxo lingheing wei ling tata yo ti en nambei mam qou lim loum nimza.’
\p 
\v 28 “Neu touk lalei wo vanei om pesek bei se na lalei. Om ma la myayaing me lam neil qayeeng xeiles wou e.
\v 29 Ekom moxo neil elox wou ma bei, ‘Wei! Vakovek qes dalus eno a mi wong xuk bandaing wou wang me a se mi pyalek wa xe qayeeng. Ekom wa seng wong meme lingheing ti wou ay en a bong xeilala is axe xel gweleeng.
\v 30 Ekom gyeik wa neum tiwei la saing wa xe lulul lek vex wei mi wong kwapesiv o loum beyeeng, wang leis manghaxo wei ling tata yo wou e!’
\p 
\v 31 “Ma neil wou bei, ‘A neung, wang mindei is ay taxombouk, om lulul dalus wei a ne inye wa xe.
\v 32 Ekom xey ambei bo xeindlala, me laleind bo nimza en nambei lim mey, ekom toundei mapieing no, moxo lati ekom xey a xeiwou.’”
\c 16
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei lei ngandoung pepyawexe lulul vateivek o
\p 
\v 1 Yesu neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei, “Tambiy wei lulul ana yo ti xe lei ngandoung wei mi yeiteyei xuk o ti mindei. Om xel valu lam me byex qayeeng lek e bei, ‘Wa xe lei ngandoung wo nol wou wa xe lulul.’
\v 2 Om moxo taxe e la lalei me teling wou e, ‘Vati ingwei a ngo en wa xe kwa ne? Wang na menyex wou qayeeng wei xuk wei wang o me na neil wou ay, en tyek wa seng bo lei ngandoung no.’
\p 
\v 3 “De lei ngandoung neil wou xow bei, ‘Tyek a bong vati gweimbeeng? Axe teiv zeim xuk veil ay. A ninkanzek ma en ingwei ambei bong xuk wou xel nge me qandax tembuing o, de a ning yaleeng en tayeing lulul.
\v 4 A woulek vati wei ambei bong o, om gyeik ingwei a noum veil xuk eno tyek xomaxoneing na qou a me na eivek bend.’
\p 
\v 5 “Om moxo taxe xel wei qou lul vateivek wou e xe teiv ekom se wong zeyi yo, xel titi mi la lalei, moxo teling tambiy tiwei tax o, ‘Wang qou a xe teiv xe lulul vamva?’
\p 
\v 6 “Moxo neil embei, ‘800 deng oliv wel.’
\p “Lei ngandoung neil wou e, ‘Wa qou wa xe qapiya me mendei daing me na byex bei 400 deng.’
\p 
\v 7 “Woyom moxo teling nge wei yuw o, ‘De wang qou vamva?’
\p “Tambiy on neil elox bei, ‘1,000 bek wit.’
\p “Lei ngandoung neil wou e, ‘Wa qou wa xe qapiya me na byex bei 800 bek.’
\p 
\v 8 “De teiv woulek vati wei lei ngandoung nilul on wong o, om sanghoxe e lei en wong kwa yon nambei xel wei lupeyei nimza yo. En xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne eno kwa ghanaw veil, eno xel mi woulek sakwaing mema mema wei xel mi wong wou xel venaxow xe xel o, me xel ghanaw xel wei mi betiwou kwa wei xeiyaing o.
\v 9 A neil wou xam, xam ghe bo xuk en malew wei tembuing ne en na puw xel nam me ghe bong gweleeng lek xel en kandek bouk wei qoueing malew ema, on xel a qou xam me na eivek xomek wei deing nimza luta luta yo.
\p 
\v 10 “Wangwei xelti mi gyeiteyei lulul wei nayak o bo nimza on tyek gyeiteyei lulul wei ngandoung o bo nimza. Ek wangwei xelti se mi gyeiteyei lulul wei nayak eno bo bombek on tyek se gyeiteyei lulul wei ngandoung eno bo bombek is.
\v 11 Om wangwei xam seng gweiteyei malew wei tembuing ne bo bombek, ond tyek eti bong lulul nimza wei tyoung gheyapu yo wou xam en xam ghe gweiteyei?
\v 12 Me wangwei xam seng gweiteyei xel nge xe lulul bo nimza, on eti tyek bong wamaxow xe lulul wou wang?
\p 
\v 13 “Xukxe ti se mi wong xuk wou teiv yayuw. En tyek lalei bo nol wou nge de lalei devind nge. O moxo tyek betiwou nge de na toung demi wou nge. Xam seng teyei bei bo xuk wou Anutu de malew is.”
\s1 Qayeeng petieing me tete lalei
\p 
\v 14 Xel Parisi laleind mi vind malew, om xel ngo qayeeng tiyon dalus eno xel wo vyend wou Yesu.
\v 15 Moxo neil wou xel bei, “Xam ghe mi wong xow wo nimza wou moux alis vex mend, ekom Anutu woulek xam laleimim. Lul vatiyeiw wei moux alis vex wou naleind bei inyon nimza maseim, eno inyon nilul ayang wou Anutu manghalus.
\p 
\v 16 “Qayeeng petieing me qayeeng wei xel poropet o mi yeip me elam tyip wou bouk wei Yoan o. Eivek bouk kayon eno Xoulek Nimza wei Anutu xe tete lalei eno xel di neil e la teyei lek beyeeng sapa, me xel dalusateiv di wo ninkanzek me la eivek.
\v 17 Inye se wo pok en ingwei tyoung aluw tembuing malang o. Ekom qayeeng wei xel byex eivek petieing eno ti tyek se nati.
\p 
\v 18 “Xelti embei qateiv iingama wei luw venei de dii vex nge, on wo kwapesiv, de wangwei moux ti dii vex wei leya qateiv e veil iingama yo, on wo kwapesiv.”
\s1 Lulul ana me Laserus
\p 
\v 19 Yesu neil no bei, “Inyei tambiy wei lulul ana yo ti mi vunek en teimb teleing me mateyek nimzamza de teyei lek bouk eno mi ya lulul nimza.
\v 20 Nanghei lulul ana xe tete mya eno kanyo ti eno mindei inyon. E lei Laserus, qatyex sevunexe e ninavi.
\v 21 Moxo mi wounalei bei gya lulul myapapu wei mi teila eivek lelek xeinghembi wei lulul ana xe yo, de woyom xel naw la mi myeil e xe qatyex.
\p 
\v 22 “De bouk la wou eivek om kanyo tiwei mi tay eno mey me xel angela lam qou e me la toung wou Apraham byek. De tambiy wei lulul ana eno mey is me xel ev.
\v 23 Eivek beyeeng wei meyeing xe yo eno moxo valwou myavanei ngandoung. Lulul ana moxo yeila Apraham toundei dingta me Laserus toundei wou e byek.
\v 24 Om moxo taxe la wou e bei, ‘Mang Apraham, wa laleim e pyaxow en ay! Wang bong Laserus a toung mema deyis na eivek memiing me nam a toung lek a ghas en embo nityuweing nayaka, en a toundei eivek nenyex tine eno a axe myavanei ngandoung.’
\p 
\v 25 “Ekom Apraham neil elox wou e, ‘Neung, wang bounaleim en ingwei wang mindei mapieing o, bei wang mi qou lul nimzamza de Laserus mi qou lulul wei nilul o, ekom gweimbeeng ne eno lalei wo nimza nanghei inye de wang valwou myavanei.
\v 26 De lulti nge is, senghoing eivek xa de xam eno Anutu toung vul manghembi ti yeip zeyi woy. En kandek xel ne ti se teyeimbei qayil me nak wou xam de xam on ti se teyeimbei qayil me ghe nam inye wou xa.’
\p 
\v 27 “Woyom moxo neil, ‘Nambei nyon a tay wou wang, mang, wang bong Laserus na mang beeng.
\v 28 En a lingyeiw lim, om wong Laserus la peti xel en kandek xel se nam eivek beyeeng wei myavanei ngandoung ne is.’
\p 
\v 29 “Ekom Apraham neil elox, ‘Mose xe petieing me xel poropet xe qayeeng eno di yeip wou xel om xel a mi ngo.’
\p 
\v 30 “Lulul ana neil, ‘Ma, mang Apraham, ekom wangwei xel meyeing ti qandi lek me na wou xel on tyek xel bongis me pekwi xow.’
\p 
\v 31 “Apraham neil wou embei, ‘Wangwei xel embei se ngo wou Mose me xel poropet, on tyek xel se teyei bei bongis tambiy wei qandi lek veil meyeing o.’”
\c 17
\s1 Kwa nilul mi wo nol wou wongeingis
\p 
\v 1 Yesu neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei: “Lul leimalei wei embei bong xomaxoneing detei en sewokeing eno tyek qandi. Ekom tambiy tiwei wong etyip eno e gyaleeng.
\v 2 Wangwei tambiy ti embei bong yakyak on ti detei en sewokeing, on inyon nimza bei xel banex e na eivek mamileeng is qakous ngandoung wei xel tup e vivekwou e kwa yo en e se bong kwa yon. Anutu tyek bong myaveweeng ngandoung ghanaw veil en ingwei xel wong o.
\v 3 Om xam ghe gweiteyei xow.
\p “Wangwei lim bong sewokeing ond wang na pepyawexe e, ek wangwei e pekwi xow ond wa semaleeng sewokeing wei e yo.
\v 4 De wangwei e bong sewokeing lim yuw wou wang lek bouk tixemou, de lu lim yuw eno loumelam wou wang me neil embei, ‘A pekwi xow,’ ond wa semaleeng sewokeing wei e yo.”
\s1 Yesu neil kwa wei wongeingis o
\p 
\v 5 Xel sinale neil wou Tambiy Ngandoung bei, “Wa tetulexe xa xe wongeingis ena bo ngandoung!”
\p 
\v 6 Moxo neil elox bei, “Wangwei wongeingis wei xam eno nayaka nambei xax mastet vei on tyek wa neil wou xax ngandoung tine bei wa puw xow me ghe na dev xow eivek mamileeng on tyek betiwou wa xe qayeeng.”
\s1 Xuk nimza wei xukxe yo
\p 
\v 7 “Wangwei xam on ti xe xukxe la qandax tembuing o la yeiteyei sipsip, gyeik ingwei xukxe loumelam, on tyek wa se teyei bei neil wou bei, ‘Lam dei me wa.’
\v 8 Ekom tyek wa neil wou wa xe xukxe bei, ‘Wang gweiwou lul yaeing wou ay atax me ghe gweiwou xow me na duw lul yaeing en a gha me na num lek boy, dekakom wang gwa me na num lek.’
\v 9 De tyek e neil dange wou xukxe en ingwei wo xuk ambei ingwei neil wou e yo? Ma.
\v 10 Om xam is ambei nyon, gyeik ingwei xam ghe bong xuk dalus wei Anutu neil wou xam bei xam ghe bong o na ma, ond xam a neimbei, ‘Xa xukxe ne se nimza teyei lek. Xuk wei xa mi wong ne inye xuk wei xa mi yo.’”
\s1 Yesu wong vanei lepa ma veil moux xoumeeng
\p 
\v 11 Yesu betiwou sakwaing wei la Yerusalem o, om la wou sakwaing wei di yeip senghoing eivek distrik Samaria me Galili yo.
\v 12 Ka moxo la eivek beyeeng ti eno moux xoumeeng wei vanei lepa wong xel eno la tyip wou e nanghei inyon, xel nale dingta,
\v 13 me taxe xoulekeing bei, “Yesu! Teiv! Pyanaleim en xa!”
\p 
\v 14 Gyeik ingwei Yesu yei xel, eno neil wou xel, “Xam la talex xow wou xel lumuki.” Ka xel di la eno xel ninavi wo nimzalek.
\p 
\v 15 Gyeik xel on ti yei ingwei wo nimzalek, om loumelam wou Yesu, moxo di taxe me sanghoxe Anutu.
\v 16 Moxo ev vaxakatu eivek me ma la eivek tembuing wou Yesu vaxa me wo dange wou e, inyon Samaria ti.
\p 
\v 17 Yesu teling, “Inye xel xoumeeng dalus se wo nimzalek? Xel limvey la nya?
\v 18 Xelti se pekwi ma me loumelam sanghoxe Anutu, qe tambiy ba tine venaxow.”
\v 19 Woyom Yesu neil wou, “Qandi lek me la. Wa xe wongeingis wong wang wo nimzalek.”
\s1 Anutu xe tete lalei tyek nam
\p 
\v 20 Xel Parisi valu teling wou Yesu bei, “Gyeik inya Anutu xe tete lalei nam?” Yesu neil elox wou xel, “Anutu xe tete lalei embei nam, on tyek lulti se nam mendei nambei dee me xam ghe gwei lek mamim.
\v 21 O tyek xomaxoneing se neimbei, ‘Toundei inye,’ o ‘Toundei inyei,’ en nambei Anutu xe tete lalei toundei eivek xam.”
\p 
\v 22 Woyom moxo neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei, “Bouk di lam gyeik ingwei xam ghe wou naleimim being gwei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux xe bouk ti. Ekom tyek xam seng gwei.
\v 23 Xomaxoneing tyek na neil wou xam bei, ‘Moxo toundei inyei’ o ‘Moxo toundei inye!’ On xam se daveimyamim me ghe na betiy xel.
\v 24 En bouk wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei noum eno tyek nambei zivip mi nex mema nanghei tyoung myasepu valu me ela valu yo.
\v 25 Ekom myaxeeng eno tyek na qou myavanei ngenong, me xomaxoneing wei bouk tine eno tyek pesek e.
\p 
\v 26 “Kwa wei xel wong gyeik bouk wei Noaka yo, on nambei nyon tyek xel nox bong kwa kayon lek bouk wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei noum o.
\v 27 Xomaxoneing di ya me num lek me di iima, me neuyeiw di iima lox me loum deka ela tyip wou bouk wei Noaka la eivek sip, woyom memiing butek me lam leis xel dalus.
\p 
\v 28 “Xel wong kwa kayon nambei nyon eivek bouk wei Lot o, xomaxoneing di ya me num lek, me di xouv lulul, me di wong vateivek, xel di ev lulul vei eivek xuk, me xel di ev xomek.
\v 29 Ekom ka bouk wei Lot la veil Sodom, nenyex is qakous wei wo gyand en nenyex tum lek o tei nambei luing nanghei tyoung nei me ya moux alis vex dalus.
\p 
\v 30 “Tyek xel bong kwa nambei nyon lek bouk wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei noum yanyateiv o.
\v 31 Lek bouk kayon, xelti embei toumendei lek xomek demi qetyei de e xe lulul nimza na toumendei eivek xomek lalei on tyek se douk me nox a qou lulul. De nambei nyon is, xelti embei toumendei eivek xuk on tyek se nox a qou e xe lulul ti.
\v 32 Xam ghe bou naleimim en Lot venei!
\v 33 Xelti embei zeimaxoun mapieing wei e yo, on tyek na saing e xe mapieing, ek xelti embei saing mapieing wei e yo, on tyek na zeimaxoun e xe mapieing.
\v 34 A neil wou xam, lek boukeing tiyon eno tambiy yayuw di yeip lek zek tixemou, tyek Anutu na qou nge de nge na toumendei.
\v 35-36 Vex yayuw di louk wit neing bei embo palawa wei belet o. Tyek Anutu na qou nge de nge na toumendei.”\f + \fr 17:35-36 \ft Xel lupeyei valu wounalei bei qayeeng veweeng toundei is, lek danghei tine. Qayeeng tine eno nambei nye, “Moux yayuw di wong xuk. Tyek Anutu a qou nge de nge na toumendei.”\f*
\p 
\v 37 Xel betiyeing teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung, lul on tyek qandi nanghei inya?”
\p Moxo neil elox, “Lek beyeeng wei meyeing neing mi yeip lek o, inyon tyek xel menek tuw qeku nak inyon.”
\c 18
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei vexeiv ti mi wo lukendu wou tambiy wei mi zeim qayeeng o
\p 
\v 1 Woyom Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine wou e xe xel betiyeing, bei e talex wou xel en xel a mi zeimemend taxombouk, de xel se bo nimaing.
\v 2 Moxo neil embei, “Eivek beyeeng ti eno tambiy wei mi zeim qayeeng o ti mindei, wei se mi yaleeng en Anutu, me se mi wounalei en moux alis vex.
\v 3 De vexeiv ti mindei eivek beyeeng tiyon. Om mi qatoloum wou tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng o. Vexo neil, ‘Tambiy ti embei bo vevek wou ay. Om wa menyex wou qayeeng eivek uw senghoing.’
\p 
\v 4 “Myaxeeng eno tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng eno se vind vexo. Dekakom moxo wounalei bei, ‘A se xaleeng en Anutu me a se wou kwang en xomaxoneing ti.
\v 5 Ekom a xei vexeiv tiyon mi wo maying wou ay me qou e xe nimaying me lam wou ay, om a menyex wou qayeeng enok bo nimbayaing wou ay.’”
\p 
\v 6 De Tambiy Ngandoung neil embei, “Xam ngo qayeeng wei tambiy nilul wei mi zeim qayeeng eno neil o.
\v 7 De tyek Anutu menyex wou xomaxoneing wei e beyal o, me xel mi eng wou e bendiyeing aluw boukeing o, tyek na mi daxe de se devind xel daing?
\v 8 A neil wou xam, tyek gyei me menyex wou xel daing. Ekom gyeik bouk wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei noum eno tyek gyei bei moux alis vex wei tembuing ne di wongis e?”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei Parisi me tambiy wei mi qou takis o
\p 
\v 9 Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine en xel valu wei mi wou naleind bei xel venaxow bombek de xel valu se nimza nambei xel.
\v 10 “Tambiy yayuw lek me la eivek xomek vambuing en embei na zeimemend, nge Parisi ti de nge xel wei mi qou takis o.
\v 11 Parisi tiyon nale me zeimema en xow: ‘O Anutu, a wong dange lak wou wang, en a se nambei moux amba, xel mi panax me mi wo nilul me mi wong kwapesiv, de a se nambei tambiy tiwei mi qou takis ne.
\v 12 Bouk yayuw eivek sounda sapa eno a mi vambu yaeing, me na mi wong ti eivek xoumeeng en lul dalus wei a mi qou eno wou wang.’
\p 
\v 13 “Ekom tambiy wei mi qou takis eno qandi lek me nale kwanding de se yeima la tyoung gheyapu nei, qe qatu bambou me neil embei, ‘Anutu, a mi wong sewokeing om wa laleim e pyaxow en ay.’
\p 
\v 14 “A neil wou xam en tambiy tiwei mi qou takis on bei, gyeik lox beeng nei eno Anutu yei bei e bombek wou e manghalus. Dom Parisi eno ma. En xelti embei sanghoxe xow eno Anutu tyek beoux e, de xelti embei beoux xow eno Anutu tyek sanghoxe e.”
\s1 Yesu is xel yakyak
\p 
\v 15 Xomaxoneing valu qou yakyak me la wou Yesu, xel embei e ni mema lek xel. Ekom gyeik ingwei xel betiyeing yei, eno xel neil xel.
\v 16 Ekom Yesu taxe yakyak lam wou e de neil embei, “Xam ghe bong yakyak nam wou ay, xam se bale zeyi xel, en Anutu xe tete lalei nei eno xel wei xok ambei yakyak eno xel xe.
\v 17 A neil wou xam zonghek, xelti embei se qou Anutu xe tete lalei nambei yakyak ne, eno tyek se na eivek.”
\s1 Gyovaxa wei lulul ana yo ti luk is Yesu
\p 
\v 18 Gyovaxa ti teling wou Yesu bei, “Putoung nimza, tyek a bong vati de na qou deing mapieing luta luta?”
\p 
\v 19 Yesu lewexe, “Nambei nya wang neimbei a nimza? Xelti se nimza qe Anutu venaxow.
\v 20 Wang woulek qayeeng petieing: ‘Wa seng bo kwapesiv is xel nge, wa seng nyeis xel nge na mey, wa se panax, wa seng bong qayeeng tyonyeing en xel nge. Wa mi gwevek mam aluw tam xeinghembi.’”
\p 
\v 21 Gyovaxa neil, “Gyeik a yak me elam tyip gweimbeeng ne, eno a mi betiwou petieing on dalus.”
\p 
\v 22 Gyeik ingwei Yesu ngo inyon, eno neil wou e bei, “Wang ghei ma en lulti. Wang bo vateivek lek lulul dalus wei wang o, de ghe bong malew on wou xel kanyo, on tyek wa qou lulul nimzamza eivek tyoung gheyapu nei, woyom wang nam betiwou ay.”
\p 
\v 23 Gyeik ingwei moxo ngo inyon eno lalei wo maying, en nambei tambiy yon xe lulul ngenong.
\v 24 Yesu yei e me neil embei, “Inye wo pok en xel wei lulul ana embei na eivek Anutu xe tete lalei yo!
\v 25 Wangwei kamel embei na eivek ying manghalus wei duweing lulul o ond tyek bo pok wou e? Ekom xel wei lulul ana embei na eivek Anutu xe tete lalei eno tyek bo pok ngandoung.”
\p 
\v 26 Xel wei ngo inyon eno teling bei, “Wangwei nambei nyon nei ond tyek eti na mendei mapieing luta luta?”
\p 
\v 27 Yesu neil elox bei, “Lulul wei xomaxoneing se teyeimbei bong eno Anutu teyeimbei tyek bong.”
\p 
\v 28 Petele neil wou embei, “Wei, xa ghanaw xa xe lulul dalus de betiy wang.”
\p 
\v 29 Yesu neil wou xel bei, “A neil wou xam zonghek, xelti embei saing beeng o venei o liyeiw o mamata o neuyeiw en Anutu xe tete lalei
\v 30 on tyek xel a qou lul ngenong lumama lek bouk tine, me bouk wei embei nam eno tyek xel a qou deing mapieing luta luta.”
\s1 Yesu neil e xe meyeing teyei no
\p 
\v 31 Yesu qou xel xoumeeng yuw me la nale beyaleing me neil wou xel. “Xey ambei zek me nana Yerusalem, me lulul dalus wei xel poropet byex lek Xomaxoneing Neu Moux eno tyek bo neing lek.
\v 32 Tyek xel toung moxo na eivek xel amba memend. Tyek xel baluk seloukeing wou e, me bo nol wou e, me pesuv myenlouk lek e,
\v 33 me sesa e, de nyeis e mey. Ekom lek bouk yal eno tyek qandi lek no.”
\p 
\v 34 Xel betiyeing se woulek qayeeng tine qes en qes xupek en xel, me xel se woulek vati wei di neil o.
\s1 Yesu wong tambiy wei matekeing o ti ma wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 35 Ka Yesu la paviy beyeeng Jeriko, eno tambiy wei matekeing o ti mindei wou sakwaing nenyawes me mi tay lulul me malew wou xel.
\v 36 Gyeik ingwei moxo ngo moux alis vex ngenongakes di lam, om teling wou xel bei, “Inyei xel di wo vati?”
\v 37 Xel neil wou embei, “Yesu wei Nasaret eno di lamela.”
\p 
\v 38 Matekeing moxo taxe bei, “Yesu, Dawit Neu Moux,\f + \fr 18:38 \ft Qayeeng tine, “Dawit Neu Moux”, qes nge nambei nye Mesia.\f* wa laleim e pyaxow en ay.”
\p 
\v 39 Xel wei di lam atax eno neil e me neil embei e mendei kanzek, ekom moxo taxe xoulekeing, “Dawit Neu moux, wa laleim e pyaxow en ay.”
\p 
\v 40 Yesu nale me neil nikanzek bei xel a qou moux tiyon me na wou e. Gyeik ingwei moxo la paviy, Yesu teling e,
\v 41 “Wambei am bong vati wou wang?”
\p Moxo neil embei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, ambei gheina yo.”
\p 
\v 42 Yesu neil wou moxo bei, “Wa mam e gyeina en wa xe wongeingis wong wang wo nimzalek.”
\v 43 Lutika eno moxo ma yeila de betiwou Yesu, me di sanghoxe Anutu. Gyeik ingwei xomaxoneing dalus yei inyon eno xel sanghoxe Anutu.
\c 19
\s1 Yesu la Sakius beeng
\p 
\v 1 Yesu la eivek Jeriko me di la.
\v 2 Tambiy ti mindei inyon e lei Sakius. Moxo lei ngandoung wei xel wei mi qou takis o, me tambiy on lulul ana.
\v 3 Moxo embei gyei bei Yesu yon nambei nya. Ekom moxo sepika om se teyeimbei gyei, en inye moux alis vex ngenongakes.
\v 4 Om moxo veimya me la tax wou sakwaing wei Yesu embei na nox me lek xax basounghek ti en embei gyei e.
\p 
\v 5 Ka Yesu la paviy xax qes eno veilma lek me neil embei, “Sakius, ouk me lam daing, en ambei na mendei eivek wa bam gweimbeeng.”
\v 6 Om moxo ouk me lam daing me qou e is xeilala.
\p 
\v 7 Xomaxoneing dalus wei yei inyon eno xel ngoung wouma me neil embei, “Moxo la dei is xel wei sewokeing o.”
\p 
\v 8 Kalekom Sakius nale me neil wou Tambiy Ngandoung, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wei! Tyek a dembu lul wei ay eno na yuw de na bong veweeng wou xel kanyo. De wangwei a qou xelti xe lulti en tyonyeing on tyek a bong malew nox zeyi wou e lu vey.”
\p 
\v 9 Yesu neil wou e bei, “Gweimbeeng Anutu vind xel wei xomek tine yo veil nilul, en nambei tambiy tine inye Apraham neu is.
\v 10 En Xomaxoneing Neu Moux lam en embei gyimexe me devind moux alis vex wei lati yo noumenam.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei xukxe xoumeeng qou malew o
\p 
\v 11 Ka xomaxoneing ngo tiyon, Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine no is wou xel, en nambei la paviy Yerusalem, om xel wou naleind bei Anutu xe tete lalei tyek nam atyip daing.
\v 12 Moxo neil embei, “Tambiy wei lei ngandoung eno neu ti la tembuing wei dingta yo, en embei xel balax embo king de woyom e noumenam beyeeng.
\v 13 Om moxo taxe e xe xukxe xoumeeng me wong malew ghol\f + \fr 19:13 \ft Ghol malew wei tambiy wei lei ngandoung eno neu toung eivek e xe xukxe titi memend, inye nambei xouveing wei dentouk qes yal o. \f* titi wou xel, de neil embei, ‘Xam mendi bong vateivek lek malew on deka a noum le.’
\p 
\v 14 “Ekom xel wei e beeng qes eno laleind wo nol wou e, me wong xel wei xel beyal o valu betiy e me la neil embei, ‘Xa bei tambiy tiyon e se bong xa xe king.’
\p 
\v 15 “Ekom e wo king, me loumelam beyeeng. Woyom moxo wo qayeeng la wou xel xukxe wei wong malew wou xel o, en embei gyei bei xel titi wong xuk lek me qou malew vamva is lek mapu.
\p 
\v 16 “Tambiy tiwei myaxeeng o lam me neil, ‘Teiv, a wong xuk lek wa xe malew ghol tiwei yo me na qou malew ghol xoumeeng is.’
\p 
\v 17 “De moxo neil wou bei, ‘Wang on a xe xukxe nimza me wang wo xuk nimza. Wang weiteyei lul wei nayak o, om tyek wang gweiteyei beyeeng ngandoung xoumeeng.’
\p 
\v 18 “Xukxe nge wei yayuw eno lam neil embei, ‘Teiv, a wong xuk lek wa xe malew ghol tiwei yo me na qou malew ghol lim is.’
\p 
\v 19 “E xe teiv lewexe, ‘Nimza, wang gweiteyei beyeeng ngandoung lim.’
\p 
\v 20 “Woyom xukxe nge lam, me neil embei, ‘Teiv, wa xe malew ghol tiyo inye, a toung eivek qaeing myasepu ti.
\v 21 En a xaleeng en wang, en wa tambiy wei niseikeing o, wang mi qou vati wei wa seng toung o, me wang mi qou lul yaeing wei wa seng ev o.’
\p 
\v 22 “Woyom king neil wou e xe xukxe, ‘Wa xukxe nilul. Tyek a bong qayeeng en wang en wamaxow xe qayeeng. Wang wei bei a tambiy wei niseikeing, a mi qou vati wei a se toung me na qou lulul yaeing wei a se ev o?
\v 23 Nambei nya wa seng toung axe malew eivek xomek malew, en kandek gyeik ingwei a noum ond a qou is malew wei xel toung lek mapu yo?’
\p 
\v 24 “Woyom king neil wou xel wei toukale paviy e yo, ‘Xam qou malew ghol tiyon veil e me wong wou tambiy wei e xe malew ghol xoumeeng o.’
\p 
\v 25 “Xel neil wou e, ‘Teiv, xukxe yon qou malew ghol xoumeeng woy!’
\p 
\v 26 “Moxo neil elox, ‘A neil wou xam, xel eti yeiw wei qou lulul, eno tyek am bong valu is wou xel, ekom wangwei xelti se qou lulul ti, on lul nayak kawei toundei wou e yon, tyek am bouveil e.
\v 27 Ekom xel vevek amba wei ay yo embei a se bong king wei xel, eno xam a qou xel me ghe nam inye me ghe nyeis xel amey wou a mang.’”
\s1 Yesu la eivek Yerusalem nambei king
\p 
\v 28 Ka Yesu neil qayeeng on woy, om betiwou sakwaing me lek me la Yerusalem.
\v 29 Ka Yesu la paviy Betpage me Betani lek qetyei wei xel mi neil embei lukendu Oliv, eno moxo wong e xe xel betiyeing yayuw la me neil wou luw,
\v 30 “Muw ghe na eivek beyeeng tinei, wangwei muw ghe na, tyek muw ghe gwei dongi lingheing ti xel qoxoun nanghei inyon, xelti seng ghei dei lek. Muw a tul me na qou me ghe nam inye.
\v 31 Wangwei xelti teling muw, ‘Muw ghe tul dongi yon enva?’ On muw a neil wou e bei, ‘Tambiy Ngandoung embei bong xuk en.’”
\p 
\v 32 Betiyeing yuw wei wong luw la eno luw yei lul nambei ingwei e neil wou luw o.
\v 33 Ka luw di tul yis veil dongi eno mayeiw teling wou luw bei, “Muw ghe tul dongi ne enva?”
\p 
\v 34 Luw neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung embei bong xuk en.”
\p 
\v 35 Om luw qou dongi me la wou Yesu. Xel toung xel xe teimb lek dongi demi de toung Yesu la dei lek.
\v 36 Ka e di la, eno xomaxoneing liw xel xe teimb me teteyexe wou sakwaing.
\p 
\v 37 Gyeik ingwei moxo la paviy beyeeng wei sakwaing lep me la lukendu Oliv nei, eno e xe xel betiyeing ngenongakes di wong xeindlala me sanghoxe Anutu me wo denduing en lulvako wei xel yei woy o. Xel neil,
\q1 
\v 38 “Mata ena wou king tiwei lam lek Tambiy Ngandoung lei yo!” \rq Qapiya Lalo 118:26\rq*
\q2 “Lalei vevopeing e gyeip senghoing eivek Anutu wei tyoung gheyapu nei me xey de lei laeing ena wou Anutu.”
\p 
\v 39 De xel Parisi valu toundei eivek xel ngenong on lalei, xel neil wou Yesu bei, “Putoung, wa neil wa xe xel betiyeing on, en xel se neil qayeeng on.”
\p 
\v 40 Yesu neil wou xel, “A neil wou xam! Wangwei xel mendei kanzek, on tyek xel qakous ne taxe xoulekeing.”
\s1 Yesu eng en Yerusalem
\p 
\v 41 Ka Yesu la paviy Yerusalem me yei beyeeng ngandoung on, eno moxo eng en.
\v 42 Me neil embei, “Wangwei wamaxow ghe boulek bouk tine, en sakwaing wei lalei vevopeing lam wou wang ne, ekom gweimbeeng xupek en wa mam.
\v 43 Bouk ti tyek nam, gyeik wa xe xel vevek nam a poux tembuing apup me bivekwou tete wei wang on. Me tyek xel bale ebivekwou danghei danghei nei zeyi wang.
\v 44 Tyek xel lelolexe wang na lek tembuing, wang is neumyeiw wei toundei eivek wang on. Tyek xel se bong qakous nge na toumendei lek nge mapu, en nambei wa seng woulek bouk wei Anutu lam en embei devind wang o.”
\s1 Yesu tiy xel veil xomek vambuing
\p 
\v 45 Woyom Yesu la eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o me tiy xel wei di wong vateivek lek lulul o.
\v 46 Moxo neil wou xel, “Xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye, ‘Axe xomek ne, inye xomek wei zeimeing mema eivek o.’\f + \fr 19:46 \ft Yesaya 56.7\f* Ekom xam ghe wong e wong ambei ‘beyeeng xupekeing wei xel panaxeing o.’\f + \fr 19:46 \ft Yelemia 7.11\f*”
\p 
\v 47 Taxombouk eno Yesu mi teyoxe xel eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o. Ekom xel lumuki leitata yo, me putoung wei petieing o me gyovaxa wei xomaxoneing o, di wong me yei en xel embei nyeis e mey.
\v 48 Ekom xel se yeiwou sakwaing ti, en nambei xomaxoneing wei toundei me ngo e xe qayeeng eno wo nikanzek.
\c 20
\s1 Xel teling Yesu en e xe nikanzek
\p 
\v 1 Bouk ti eno Yesu di teyoxe xomaxoneing eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o me neil Xoulek Nimza wou xel, de xel lumuki leitata me putoung wei petieing o dalus is teivateiv lam tyip wou e.
\v 2 Xel neil wou e bei, “Neil wou xa, wang qou lei ngandoung me nikanzek tiyon nanghei inya me ghe di wong lulul tiyon angya? Eti wong lei ngandoung on wou wang?”
\p 
\v 3 Moxo neil elox wou xel, “Ay is ambei nyon ambei teling xam, xam neil wou ay,
\v 4 gyeik ingwei Yoan lipek moux alis vex, inyon lul wei Anutu eivek tyoung gheyapu yo, o lul wei xomaxoneing o?”
\p 
\v 5 Xel di luk wouma eivek xel venaxow senghoing me neil embei, “Wangwei xey a neimbei lul on Anutu yo, on tyek teling xey, ‘Nambei nya xam seng wongis e?’
\v 6 Ekom wangwei xey a neimbei, ‘Lul on xomaxoneing o,’ on tyek moux dalus banex xey en qakous, en xel wongis bei Yoan on poropet.”
\p 
\v 7 Om xel lewexe, “Xa se woulek bei inyon lam anghei inya.”
\v 8 Yesu neil wou xel, “Ay is, tyek a se neil wou xam en lei ngandoung tiwei andi wong lulti beimambei nangya ne.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei xel xukxe yo
\p 
\v 9 Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing tine wou xomaxoneing bei, “Tambiy ti wong e xe xuk wain ti, dom wou eivek xel xukana valu memend bei xel a mi bo xuk vateivek lek. De e venaxow la dei enden lek beyeeng nge.
\v 10 Lek bouk wei uleing wain eno moxo wong xukxe ti la wou xel wei di yeiteyei wain o, en embei xel dul wain on neing valu wou e. Ekom xel wei di yeiteyei wain eno leis e me wong e lox mema bandaing.
\v 11 Moxo wong xukxe nge lox me la no, ekom xel leis e is no me wo niyalenyeing wou e de wong e lox mema bandaing.
\v 12 Moxo wong xukxe tiwei yal o lox me la no. Ekom xel leis e wo nol me nex e la myayaing.
\p 
\v 13 “Woyom xuk wain ma neil, ‘Tyek am bong ambei nya? Tyek am bong a neung moux tiwei a laleing vind eno na, bei xel se gwevek e xe qayeeng xeinghembi.’
\p 
\v 14 “Ekom gyeik xel xukana yei e neu di lam, eno xel neil wouma bei, ‘Neu moux tine tyek na qou xuk wain. Xey a leis e mey, de xe venaxow a qou xe xe xuk wain ne.’
\v 15 Om xel nex moxo la myayaing veil xuk wain de leis e mey.
\p “Om tyek xuk wain ma yon bong vati wou xel?
\v 16 Moxo tyek nam nyeis xel wei di yeiteyei xuk wain on na mey, de bong xuk wain on wou xel amba.” Gyeik xomaxoneing ngo qayeeng tiyon eno xel neil embei, “Lul ambei nyon eno e se nox qandi no.”
\p 
\v 17 Yesu yei xel kanzek, de teling bei, “Qayeeng tiwei xel byex ne qes ambei nya:
\q1 “‘Qakous mundeeng ti myaxeeng wei xel kamunda pesek,
\q2 eno wong ambei qakous tiwei nale me mi byexaxoun xomek o’\f + \fr 20:17 \ft Qapiya Lalo 118:22\f*? \rq Qapiya Lalo 118:22\rq*
\m 
\v 18 Xel dalus wei oing me teila lek qakous on tyek bo tiptip. Ekom wangwei qakous tiyon detei lek xelti on tyek bo myapapu.”
\p 
\v 19 Xel putoung wei petieing o me xel lumuki leitata yo di yimexe sakwaing en xel embei zeimaxoun e lutika, en xel woulek bei neil qayeeng pakeing tiyon lek xel. Ekom xel yaleeng en xomaxoneing.
\s1 Xel a toung takis wou Sisa
\p 
\v 20 Xel lumuki leitata me putoung wei petieing o mi yei Yesu teyei teyei, bei bong xel valu na xupekeing me gyei e teyei. Me tyoing lek bei xel bombek bei na ngo e xe qayeeng wei embei neil o, en kandek xel bong e na wou lei ngandoung wei seyap o.
\v 21 Om xel teling wou embei, “Putoung, xa woulek qayeeng wei wang mi neil me ghe mi teyoxe eno mi la bombek, me wang mi neil qayeeng la teyeima wou moux alis vex wei lei laeing o me lei maeing o. Me qayeeng zonghek eno wang mi teyoxe xel en Anutu xe kwa.
\v 22 Woyom wang wou naleim ambei nya, beip inye teyeimbei xey a toung takis wou Sisa o xe se toung?”
\p 
\v 23 Ekom Yesu woulek bei xel tyoxe e, om neil embei,
\v 24 “Talex selewa ti wou ay. Inye eti tenu me lei di yeip lek?” Xel neil elox bei, “Sisa.”
\p 
\v 25 Me moxo neil wou xel, “Lul wei Sisa, eno xam ghe bong wou Sisa. De lul wei Anutu, eno xam ghe bong wou Anutu.”
\p 
\v 26 Om xel se teyeimbei tyoxe e en qayeeng wei e neil o ti eivek moux alis vex mendghalus, om xel etek en qayeeng wei neil elox wou xel o, om xel dei kanzek.
\s1 Qandi lek veil meyeing me iingama
\p 
\v 27 Xel Sadyusi valu wei mi neil embei xel wei mey, eno tyek se qandi lek. Xel lam wou Yesu is telinyeing ti.
\v 28 Xel neil embei, “Putoung, Mose byex qayeeng ti nambei nye wou xey, wangwei tambiy ti dii vex ti ekom mey veil venei de neu ma, ond li e dii vexeiv me bong li wei mey eno neu en mendi zeim li lei xoun.
\v 29 Om xel wei lindama eno lim yuw. Tiwei myaxeeng eno ii vex ti ekom mey de neu ma.
\v 30 Woyom li nge wei yuw eno ii vexeiv on.
\v 31 De li tiwei yal eno ii vexeiv. Eivek sakwaing ambei nyon eno xel lim yuw wei lindama eno ii vex tiyon me neuyeiw ma, de xel mey.
\v 32 Dekakom vex tiyon mey loxyus is.
\v 33 Woyom gyeik bouk loxyus wei xel meyeing embei qandi lek, eno eti venei vex tiyon? En moux lim yuw eno ii vex tixemou yon.”
\p 
\v 34 Yesu neil elox wou xel, “Xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne mi iima me wong vex lox me loum wouma.
\v 35 Ekom eivek bouk loxyus eno moux alis vex wei Anutu neil embei xel teyei lek en ingwei xel embei qandi lek veil meyeing me mendei mapieing, eno tyek se diima o bong xel nox me noum wouma.
\v 36 Me tyek xel se nox me na mey no, en xel on teyei lek xel angela. Me xel on Anutu neuyeiw, en nambei xel qandi lek veil meyeing.
\v 37 Ekom Mose talex wou xey bei xel wei mey eno tyek qandi lek veil meyeing, en pavulek wei byex en ingwei nenyex tum lek xax nayaka yo, en taxe Tambiy Ngandoung Anutu wei Apraham o me Anutu wei Isaka yo me Anutu wei Yakop o.
\v 38 Moxo se Anutu wei xel meyeing, qe e Anutu wei xel wei mapieing. En eivek Anutu manghalus eno moux alis vex dalus toundei mapieing en e.”
\p 
\v 39 Xel putoung wei petieing o valu ngo qayeeng wei Yesu neil o, om xel neil wou embei, “Putoung, wa xe qayeeng on nimza.”
\v 40 De xelti se teyeimbei bong telinyeing wou Yesu en lulti no.
\s1 Eti neu Kilisi?
\p 
\v 41 Woyom Yesu neil wou xel bei, “Nambei nya moux alis vex mi neil embei Kilisi yon Dawit Neu Moux?
\v 42 Dawit venaxow neil eivek Qapiya Lalo bei,
\q1 “ ‘Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou a xe Tambiy Ngandoung bei,
\q2 “Wa mendei wou a memang payeiv
\q1 
\v 43 deka a toung wa xe xel vevek na
\q2 kwanghembi eivek wang le.” ’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 110:1\rq*
\m 
\v 44 Dawit taxe e bei ‘Tambiy Ngandoung.’ Nambei nya Kilisi yon Dawit bu?”
\s1 Kwa wei xel putoung wei petieing o
\p 
\v 45 Kale xomaxoneing dalus di ngo qayeeng wei Yesu di neil o, de neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei,
\v 46 “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en xel putoung wei petieing o, xel laleind mi vind en xel embei mi byex teimb ding me na ghavineeng. Xel laleind mi vind bei xel a mi neil bendiyeing teiv wou xel eivek beyeeng wei xel mi wong vateivek lek lulul o, me xel la mindei lek beyeeng nimza wei mya eivek xomek qekueing ama me xel la mindei lek leitata bend wei mya eivek mata wei ngandoung o.
\v 47 Xel mi tyoxe xel vexeiv me panax xel xe xomek. De xel mi wou naleind bei xel nimza om xel mi zeimemend wo ding. Bouk loxyus eno tyek xel wei nambei nyon eno tyek na qou myaveweeng ngandoung.”
\c 21
\s1 Vexeiv ti toung da wou Anutu
\p 
\v 1 Ka Yesu veilma lek me yei xel wei malew ana yo la di toung xel xe da eivek qoupek malew wei xomek vambuing o.
\v 2 De moxo yei vexeiv kanyo ti is eno toung selewa gyand nayak yayuw la eivek qoupek malew.
\v 3 De Yesu neil embei, “A neil wou xam zonghek, vexeiv kanyo toung malew ngandoung ghanaw moux alis vex valu.
\v 4 Xomaxoneing on dalus xe malew ngenong, om xel toung danghei ka la eivek deng xeikatu. De vexeiv on lulul maeing, ekom toung malew dalus wei embei devind e yo.”
\s1 Yesu neil embei xomek vambuing tyek lelolexe
\p 
\v 5 Moxo xe xel betiyeing valu yei xomek vambuing me luk en bei, “Xel qou qakous nimzamza me da wei xel toung wou Anutu yo me vunekwou xomek tiyon en.” Ekom Yesu neil embei,
\v 6 “Bouk ti tyek nam eno lulul tiwei xam ghe di wei yon, tyek xel lelolexe dalus me banex ena xonei lek tembuing de qakous ti tyek se gyeip lek nge mapu.”
\s1 Yesu neil embei nimaying ngenong tyek qandi
\p 
\v 7 Om xel teling Yesu bei, “Putoung, gyeik inya lulti yon tyek qandi? Me dee vati tyek talex lek bei lul dalus tine embim nam atyip?”
\p 
\v 8 Yesu neil embei, “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow, enok xel a tyoxe xam. Xel ngenong tyek nam lek a leing, me nam a neimbei, ‘A Mesia yo,’ me tyek xel a neimbei, ‘Bouk moxo di lam paviy.’ Ekom xam se betiwou xel.
\v 9 Gyeik ingwei xam a ngo vevek ngandoung me vevek wei seyap o ngenong qandi, yon xam seng detek. En lul beimambei yon tyek qandi tax, ekom bouk loxyus tyek sim nam daing.”
\p 
\v 10 Woyom moxo neil wou xel: “Tembuing nge tyek qandi me bong vevek wou tembuing nge, de tete lalei nge tyek bong vevek wou tete lalei nge.
\v 11 Gyeik inyon eno tyek tembuing api ngandoung, de eivek beyeeng valu eno maxep ngandoung tyek qandi me vanei ngandoung is. Me tyek xam ghe gwei dee ngandoung nelu nelu valu qandi eivek tyoung me bong yalenyeing ngandoung wou xam.
\p 
\v 12 “Ekom gyeik ingwei lul dalus on seng ghei qandi, eno tyek xel a zeimaxoun xam me bo nol wou xam. Tyek xel a qou xam me na eivek xomek qekueing ama me bong qayeeng en xam, me na toung xam ghe na eivek xeitueing, me tyek xel a qou xam me na bale wou xel king me lei ngandoung wei seyap o mendghalus. En nambei xam ghe mi betiwou ay.
\v 13 Lulti yon tyek bong ambei sakwaing wei xam ambei neil axe xoulek teyei wou xel o.
\v 14 Ekom xam seng bou naleimim ngenong atax bei tyek xam bale zeyi xow ambei nya.
\v 15 En tyek a bong qayeeng wou xam me na bong lupeyei nimza wou xam is, om xel wei embei bong qayeeng en xam eno tyek se pyalek o bakeilek qayeeng wei a wong wou xam o.
\v 16 Xam mamatam, me limyeiw, me nimpapu, me gweleeng, eno tyek xel a neil xam teyei me na toung xam eivek xel ba memend me tyek xel nyeis xam valu na mey.
\v 17 Xel xomaxoneing dalus tyek gyei xam ghe bo nol en xam ghe mi betiwou ay.
\v 18 Ekom xam lumim velus ti tyek se teyeimbei puw veil.\f + \fr 21:18 \ft Qayeeng wei luvelus ti tyek se teyeimbei puw veil eno nambei nye, xam neing tyek na mey ekom lulti se teyeimbei bo nol wou xam numim pieing.\f*
\v 19 Om wangwei xam bale nikanzek ond tyek xam mendei mapieing eivek bouk loxyus.
\s1 Yerusalem tyek lelolexe
\p 
\v 20 “Gyeik ingwei xam ghe gwei xel vevek bale ebivekwou Yerusalem, on xam ghe boulek bei bouk wei beyeeng embei lelolexe eno paviy.
\v 21 Woyom moux alis vex wei toundei eivek Yudia eno xel a pek me na lukendu. De xel wei toundei eivek Yerusalem eno xel na myayaing veil. De xel wei toundei myayaing en Yerusalem eno se na eivek lalei.
\v 22 En inye bouk wei Anutu embei bong myaveweeng o, nambei qayeeng wei xel byex eivek xoulek eno tyek bo neing lek.
\v 23 Bouk tiyon tyek bo lalei pyaweingxow en vex wei neu pouyek o me vex wei di wong luul wou neu yo! En nimaying ngandoung tyek qandi wou tembuing de Anutu xe lalei vanei tyek detei lek xomaxoneing wei Yuda yo.
\v 24 Tyek xel amey en ngeyeing vevek, me tyek xel a qou xel me na xeitueing nanghei tembuing bamba nei. De xel amba tyek bakei vaxend eivek Yerusalem me gyeiteyei deka bouk wei Anutu lax eno na boueivek le.”
\s1 Xomaxoneing Neu tyek nam
\p 
\v 25 Yesu neil no, “Dee nelu nelu tyek qandi eivek sayeiv, dentouk, me betum, de lek tembuing eno xel xomaxoneing wei tembuing tambak ne eno tyek bou naleind ngenong me gyaleeng ngandoung, en tyek xel a ngo mamileeng buklek me bong nindenduing ngandoung.
\v 26 Me lulul wei tyoung gheyapu eno tyek bo pimapi me xomaxoneing tyek gyaleeng ngandoung me mend bivek en vati wei embei nam lek tembuing o.
\v 27 Woyom lek bouk tiyon eno moux alis vex tyek gyei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux nam eivek laxap ti is nikanzek me e xe xeiyaing ngandoung.
\v 28 Gyeik ingwei lulul beimambei yon di qandi, eno xam qandi lek me ghe beil lumim lek, en bouk wei Anutu embei tul xam veil nilul eno di lam paviy.”
\s1 Xam a mi boulek xax basunghek
\p 
\v 29 Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing ti wou xel bei, “Xam ghe gwei xax basunghek me xax sapa yon is.
\v 30 Gyeik ingwei xam venaxow ghe gwei xax a byex nelu duing lek eno xam ghe boulek bei sewis di lam paviy.
\v 31 Om gyeik ingwei xam ghe gwei lulul on qandi, on xam ghe boulek bei Anutu xe tete lalei di lam paviy.
\p 
\v 32 “A neil wou xam zonghek bei, neing ayang moux alis vex wei bouk tine eno tyek se mey qe ka lulul ti beimambei yon qandi bole.
\v 33 Tyoung aluw tembuing tyek na tip, ekom axe xoulek tyek se nati.”
\s1 Xel betiyeing a mi gyeiteyei xow
\p 
\v 34 Yesu neil no, “Xam a mi gweiteyei xow, en xam se num me betiwou Kwa nol wei numeing o xam seng bou naleimim en lulul wei xe neing o, wangwei xam ghe bong ambei nyon, on tyek bouk wei Tambiy Ngandoung xe yo tyek qandi wou xam lutika nambei leliy mi eivek lepulek o.
\v 35 En tyek lulti yon qandi wou moux alis vex dalus wei toundei lek tembuing sapa yo.
\v 36 Xam a mi bale nikanzek me ghe gweiteyei xow taxombouk, me na mi zeimemamim wou Anutu, en kandek xam ghanaw lulul wei embei qandi yon. De tyek xam teyeimbei bale wou Xomaxoneing Neu Moux manghalus.”
\p 
\v 37 Teyei lek bouk titi eno Yesu mi teyoxe xel eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o. De boukeing eno la mi yeip nanghei lukendu wei xel mi neil Oliv nei.
\v 38 De satiboukeing lul eno xomaxoneing dalus mi qandi me lam xomek vambuing en embei na mi ngo e xe qayeeng.
\c 22
\s1 Yudas tup qayeeng is xel gyovaxa bei na toung Yesu eivek xel leitata memend
\p 
\v 1 Lek Bouk Wei Yaeing Belet Wei Yis Ma Veil, wei xel mi taxe bei Pasova eno lam paviy.
\v 2 Xel lumuki leitata yo me xel putoung wei petieing o di yimexe sakwaing wei xel embei nyeis Yesu e mey yo. En xel yaleeng en xomaxoneing.
\p 
\v 3 Woyom Sandang la eivek Yudas, xel mi neil embei Iskariot, xel wei xoumeeng yuw eno ti.
\v 4 Me Yudas la luk is xel lumuki leitata yo me xel belimbo wei mi yeiteyei xomek vambuing me yimexe sakwaing wei embei neil Yesu teyei me na toung e na eivek xel memend.
\v 5 Xel wo xeindlala en ingwei xel yei e yo me neil wou Yudas bei tyek xel bong malew wou e.
\v 6 Om Yudas lewexe lek qayeeng wei xel neil on, de di yimexe sakwaing wei embei bou Yesu eivek xel memend gyeik ingwei moux alis vex ngenong se toundei is e yo.
\s1 Betiyeing yayuw menyex wou yaeing
\p 
\v 7 Woyom Bouk Wei Yaeing Belet Wei Yis Ma Veil eno lam, wei xel mi leis sipsip lingheing en yaeing lek bouk wei xel mi wou naleind en Pasova yo.
\v 8 Om Yesu wong Petele luw Yoan la me neil embei, “Muw ghe na gweiwou mata wei Pasova yo en xey a gha.”
\p 
\v 9 Om luw teling wou e, “Wambei uw a na gheiwou nanghei inya?”
\p 
\v 10 Moxo neil elox, “Ka muw ghe na eivek beyeeng ngandoung eno tambiy ti di qalei memiing eivek deng ti eno tyek nam a tyip wou muw. Eno muw betiy e me ghe na eivek xomek tiwei e la eivek o.
\v 11 Me muw a neil wou tambiy wei e beeng o bei, ‘Putoung teling wang: Xomek lalei inya wei ambei gha mata wei Pasova is axe xel betiyeing o?’
\v 12 Moxo tyek talex xomek lalei myasapa wei gheyapu nei wou muw, xel menyex wou dalus woy, om muw ghe gweiwou mata nanghei inyon.”
\p 
\v 13 Luw la me yei lulul la teyei lek ingwei Yesu neil wou luw o. Om luw menyex wou mata wei Pasova yo.
\s1 Yesu wong belet aluw wain wou xel betiyeing
\p 
\v 14 Seivma la wou eivek ingwei yaeing o, om Yesu lis e xe sinaleyeiw la dei lek zek.
\v 15 Me moxo neil wou xel bei, “A laleing vind bei ambei gha mata wei Pasova ne is xam natax dekakom qalei myavanei.
\v 16 En a neil wou xam, tyek a se nox a gha no qe ka lul tine e bong neing lek eivek Anutu xe tete lalei le.”
\p 
\v 17 Ka Yesu qou mayamya wei wain o ti me wong dange wou Anutu de neil embei, “Xam a qou tine me na num eivek ama senghoing.
\v 18 En a neil wou xam tyek a se nox a num wain neing no qe ka Anutu xe tete lalei nam bole.”
\p 
\v 19 De moxo qou belet ti, me wong dange wou Anutu me dembu, me wong wou xel betiyeing de neil embei, “Inye a neing wei a wong bei e devind xam. Xam a mi bong ambei nyon en na mi bou naleimim en ay.”
\p 
\v 20 Gyeik xel ya woy eno qou mayamya wain me wong ambei nyon no me neil embei, “Mayamya tine inye qokatu vako, wei a gyand qapyex bei e devind xam o.
\v 21 Ekom tambiy tiwei embei neil a teyei me na toung ay eivek xel vevek amba memend eno toundei me ya is ay lek zek.
\v 22 Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek betiwou sakwaing wei Anutu wong wou e yo. Ekom nimaying tyek gyeip wou tambiy tiwei embei neil a teyei me na toung a na eivek xel amba memend o.”
\v 23 Xel betiyeing ngo qayeeng tiyon eno xel di teling wouma eivek xel venaxow senghoing bei, “Eti tyek bong kwa tiyon?”
\s1 Xel betiyeing pyalek ama bei eti tyek bo lei ngandoung
\p 
\v 24 Dekakom xel betiyeing pyalek ama eivek xel venaxow senghoing me neil embei, eti wo lei ngandoung en xel.
\v 25 Yesu neil wou xel bei, “Xel king wei xel amba eno xel mi wo lei ngandoung me yeiteyei moux alis vex, me xel qou leind ambei nye tambiy wei mi wo nimza wou xel o.
\v 26 Ekom xam seng bong ambei nyon, qe xelti embei bo lei ngandoung eivek xam senghoing ond e nox yusayang, de xam xe gyovaxa e teyei lek xukxe wei xam o.
\v 27 En inye eti lei ngandoung, beip inye tambiy wei toundei lek zek, o xukxe wei di duw lul yaeing o? Inyei tambiy tiwei toundei lek zek o. Ekom a toundei eivek xam senghoing nambei xukxe wei di duw o.
\v 28 Ekom xam wei ghe nale is ay gyeik ingwei axeing lam wou ay yo.
\v 29 Me a wong tete lalei wou xam, nambei ingwei mang wong wou ay yo.
\v 30 En kandek xam a mi gwa me na num lek axe zek eivek axe tete lalei me mendei lek xel siaking me ghe pepyawexe xel veleivlei xoumeeng yuw wei Israel o.”
\s1 Yesu neil embei Simon tyek dax e vun
\p 
\v 31 Yesu neil embei, “Simon, Simon, Sandang teling en embei daxe xam nambei xel mi seyex wit me wong ninavi veil o.
\v 32 Ekom Simon, a zeimemang en wang, en wa xe wongeingis e se detei. Me gyeik ingwei wa pekwi me ghe noum eno wa mi byexaxoun limyeiw.”
\p 
\v 33 Ekom Petele neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, a xeiwou xow bei tyek nana xeitueing is wang me na mey is wang.”
\p 
\v 34 Yesu lewexe bei, “A neil wou wang, Petele, gyeik ingwei qouklex seng ghei sesa vya boukeing tine eno tyek wang dax a vun luyal me na neimbei wa seng woulek ay.”
\s1 Vaxak malew, me vaxak me ngeyeing vevek
\p 
\v 35 Woyom Yesu teling xel, “Gyeik ingwei a wong xam ghe la bandaing veil vaxak malew o vaxak, o vaxalambes, eno xam seng wimexe xow en lulti?”
\p Xel lewexe bei, “Ma.”
\p 
\v 36 De moxo neil wou xel, “Ekom gweimbeeng ne wangwei wa xe vaxak malew, ond wa qou, me vaxak is ambei nyon, de wangwei wa se qou ngeyeing vevek ti, on wang bong vateivek lek teimb ding wei wang o de ghe bou ti.
\v 37 Xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye, ‘Moux alis vex yei e wo nol ambei tambiy wei nol o.’ A neil wou xam, qayeeng wei xel byex lek ay eivek qapiya eno tyek bo neing lek. Ee, en vati wei xel byex lek ay eno tyek qandi me bo neing lek.”
\p 
\v 38 De xel betiyeing neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wei, ngeyeing vevek yayuw inye.”
\p Moxo neil elox bei, “Inyon woy.”
\s1 Yesu zeimema lek lukendu Oliv
\p 
\v 39 Yesu la lukendu Oliv nambei ingwei mi wong lumama yo, me e xe xel betiyeing betiwou e.
\v 40 Moxo la tyip wou beyeeng wei yo, eno neil wou xel, “Xam a mi zeimemamim, on tyek xam se detei en axeing.”
\v 41 Moxo dula nayaka nambei ingwei xel mi nex qakous o veil xel, de ev vaxa qatu eivek me zeimema,
\v 42 “Mang, wangwei wa laleim devind ond wa zeim mayamya tine veil ay. Ekom wa se betiwou a laleing, qe wa betiwou wamaxow laleim.”
\v 43 Woyom angela wei tyoung gheyapu nei ti lam wou e me byexaxoun e.
\v 44 Yesu axe myavanei ngandoung, me zeimema nikanzek, me vanei tyip e nambei gyand me teila lek tembuing.
\p 
\v 45 Gyeik ingwei moxo zeimema woy, eno qandi lek me lox me la wou e xe xel betiyeing. Loum yei ekom xel yeip, en xel wo nimaing en xel laleind wo maying.
\v 46 Yesu teling xel, “Xam ghe weip en vati? Xam qandi lek me zeimemamim, on tyek xam se detei en axeing.”
\s1 Xel zeimaxoun Yesu
\p 
\v 47 Ka Yesu nanghei di luk eno xel ngenongakes lam tyip, tambiy tiwei xel neil embei Yudas, xel xoumeeng yuw eno ti qou xel me lam. Moxo la paviy Yesu en embei sesuvexe e,
\v 48 ekom Yesu teling e, “Yudas, wambei neil Xomaxoneing Neu Moux teyei me na toung e na eivek xel amba memend en sesuvexeing?”
\p 
\v 49 Gyeik ingwei Yesu xe xel betiyeing yei vati wei embei qandi, eno xel neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, tyek xa nyeis xel en xa xe ngeyeing vevek?”
\v 50 De xel wei xel venaxow eno ti leis xukxe wei lumuki lukanzek o me qateiv e nenya nge payeiv tip me teila.
\p 
\v 51 Ekom Yesu neil embei, “Woy! Xam seng bong kwa yon no!” De moxo zeim tambiy on nenya me wong e wo nimzalek.
\p 
\v 52 Woyom Yesu neil wou xel lumuki leitata yo, de beyeiv wei xomek vambuing o me xel teivateiv wei lam en e yo bei, “Xam ghe qou ngeyeing vevek me pebumeeng me ghe lam en xam ambei zeim tambiy wei wo vevek, o panaxeing o?
\v 53 A mindei is xam taxombouk eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o, ek xam seng zeimaxoun ay. Ekom inye xam xe seivma, wei mapetok yeiteyei yo.”
\s1 Petele ax Yesu vun
\p 
\v 54 Woyom xel zeimaxoun Yesu me qou e me la eivek lumuki lukanzek o beeng. Petele di betiy xel me di la kwanding ka.
\v 55 Ekom gyeik xel vev nenyex eivek tete lalei wei xomek tiyon masenghoing me xel xouing toundei wou, eno Petele la dei is xel.
\v 56 Xukxe vex ti yei ingwei e toundei wou nenyex tumeing o. Vex on yei e kanzek me neil embei, “Tambiy tiyon mindei is e.”
\p 
\v 57 Ekom Petele axvun me neil embei, “Vex, a se woulek e.”
\p 
\v 58 Xel dei nayaka dekakom tambiy nge yei e me neil embei, “Wang on xel wei e yo ti.”
\p Petele neil elox, “Ma, se ay ti!”
\p 
\v 59 Nambei seivma ti la veil om moux nge luk nikanzek me neil embei, “Zonghek ayang tambiy tiyon mendei is e, en inyei e nanghei Galili.”
\p 
\v 60 Petele neil elox bei, “Moux, a se woulek qayeeng tiwei wang di neil on!” Gyeik e ghei di luk eno qouklex wo vya lutika.
\v 61 Woyom Tambiy Ngandoung pekwi ma me yei Petele bombek. Woyom Petele wounalei en qayeeng wei Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou e yo: “Gweimbeeng boukeing tine qouklex seng ghei sesa vya eno tyek wang dax a vun luyal.”
\v 62 De Petele la myayaing me la eng ngenong.
\s1 Xel napexe Yesu me leis e
\p 
\v 63 Xel moux wei di yeiteyei Yesu eno xel di luk napeing lek e me petapexe e.
\v 64 Xel tup e ma zeyi nangya qaeing de neil wou e bei, “Wa baluk poropet! Eti petapexe wang?”
\v 65 Me xel lukyak ngenong lek e is.
\s1 Yesu nale wou kanzol mendghalus
\p 
\v 66 De xeiyaing nexla eno teivateiv wei xel xomaxoneing o, is xel lumuki leitata yo, me xel putoung wei petieing wei kanzol o, xel dalus qekuma, me xel qou Yesu me lam eivek xel xe qekueing ama yon.
\v 67 Me xel neil wou e, “Neil wou xa, wangwei bei inyon wa Kilisi?”
\p Ekom neil elox bei, “Wangwei a neil wou xam, on tyek xam seng bongis ay,
\v 68 me wangwei a teling wou xam en qayeeng valu, on tyek xam seng zewexe lek.
\v 69 Ekom gweimbeeng me e mi na bouk loxyus eno Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek mendei wou Anutu nikanzek mema payeiv.”
\p 
\v 70 Xel dalus teling wou e, “Inyon wa Anutu Neu Moux?”
\p Moxo neil elox, “Xam venaxow ghe neil bombek. Inye ay.”
\p 
\v 71 Woyom xel neil embei, “Xey a bei se qou pavulek valu en tambiy tine en emaxow mya neil qayeeng tine me xey a ngo woy.”
\c 23
\s1 Xel wo qayeeng en Yesu wou Pailat
\p 
\v 1 Woyom xel qendu dalus on qandi lek me qou Yesu me la wou Pailat.
\v 2 Me xel wong qayeeng en e, me neil embei, “Xa xei tambiy tine wo nol wou kwa wei xa Yudayeiw o, me peti xa bei xa se toung takis wou Sisa. De mi neil embei e Kilisi, me e yon king ti.”
\p 
\v 3 Om Pailat teling wou Yesu, “Inyon wa king wei Yudayeiw o?”
\p Yesu neil elox wou, “Ee inyon nambei wang neil on.”
\p 
\v 4 Woyom Pailat neil wou xel lumuki leitata is xel qendu ngandoung on bei, “A se xei sewokeing ti lek tambiy tine.”
\p 
\v 5 Ekom xel luk nikanzek me neil embei, “Tambiy on mi ghavineeng me la danghei danghei nei eivek Yudia, myaxeeng anghei distrik Galili me mi lam a zenz inye is, me mi teyoxe xomaxoneing me zeim xel laleind lek.”
\s1 Xel wo qayeeng en Yesu wou Herot
\p 
\v 6 Pailat ngo tine om teling wou xel, “Moux tine inye Galili ti?”
\v 7 Gyeik ingwei Pailat ngo bei Yesu yon nanghei Galili, woyom wong ela wou Herot en nambei Herot yeiteyei beyeeng danghei tiyon. De gyeik bouk kayon eno Herot toundei Yerusalem.
\p 
\v 8 Gyeik ingwei Herot yei Yesu eno wo xeilala ngandoung, en nambei mi toung ma wou en embei gyei e, en vatiyeiw wei e ngo yo, moxo wounalei bei Yesu e bong lulvako valu me e gyei.
\v 9 Herot wong telinyeing ngenong wou e. Ekom Yesu se neil qayeeng ti lox wou e.
\v 10 Xel lumuki leitata yo me putoung wei petieing o toukale inyon, me wong qayeeng en e nikanzek.
\v 11 Woyom Herot alis e xe xel vevek wong napeing wou Yesu me lukyak lek e woy, om xel qou teimb nimza maseim ti me byex lek e, dom wong e lox me la wou Pailat.
\v 12 Lek bouk kayon eno Herot aluw Pailat wo gweleeng lek ama. Takwei eno luw mi wo vevek wouma.
\s1 Pailat neil embei xel atuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng
\p 
\v 13 Pailat taxe xel lumuki leitata yo me xel gyovaxa me xomaxoneing lam qekuma.
\v 14 Me moxo neil wou xel bei, “Xam ghe qou tambiy tine me ghe lam wou ay me ghe neimbei mi zeim xel laleind lek bei xel bo vevek wou seyap. Om a wo telinyeing lumama wou e wou xam mamim, ekom a se xei sewokeing ti wou tambiy tine en vatiyeiw wei xam ghe wong qayeeng en e yo.
\v 15 De Herot is ambei nyon, om wong e loum wou xey. Xam ghe wei, tambiy tine se wong sewokeing ti bei e mey.
\v 16-17 Nambei nyon tyek a sesa moxo de woyom na bong e na.”\f + \fr 23:16-17 \ft Xel lupeyei valu wounalei bei qayeeng veweeng toundei is, lek danghei tine. Qayeeng tine eno nambei nye: Vakovek qes titi lek bouk wei Pasova, eno Pailat e mi bong xomaxoneing ti na veil xeitueing.\f*
\p 
\v 18 Ekom moux alis vex dalus poux avyend lekti me neil embei, “Leis tambiy on mey, de wong Barabas lam wou xa.”
\v 19 Barabas on tambiy wei wong vevek eivek beyeeng ngandoung me leis xel valu mey o, om xel toung e la xeitueing.
\p 
\v 20 Pailat embei bong Yesu na, om neil wou xel dalus no.
\v 21 Ekom xel di tetulexe wou taxeing me neil embei, “Tuw e lek xax pepeeng! Tuw e lek xax pepeeng!”
\p 
\v 22 Lu yayal eno moxo neil wou xel bei, “Enva? Tambiy tine wong sewokeing vati? A se xei sewokeing ti bei e mey, om tyek a sesa e de na bong e na.”
\p 
\v 23 Ekom xel wo ninkanzek me taxe la xoulekeing bei, Pailat e tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng. Me xel xe taxeing sevunexe Pailat ning qayeeng.
\v 24 Om Pailat betiwou qayeeng wei xel o me neilteyei bei Yesu e mey.
\v 25 Moxo wong tambiy tiwei toundei eivek xeitueing en ingwei wong vevek me leis xel valu mey, eno la myayaing, tambiy tiwei xel teling en o. De Pailat betiwou xel xe lalei vineing me wong Yesu wou xel vevek.
\s1 Xel tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng
\p 
\v 26 Ka xel vevek qou Yesu me la, eno xel yei tambiy ti lam anghei beyeeng myayaing nei en embei na eivek Yerusalem, moxo lei Simon wei beyeeng Sairini yo. Xel zeimaxoun e me liw xax pepeeng lek e ghandiwek de e qalei me betiwou Yesu.
\p 
\v 27 De xomaxoneing ngenongakes di betiy e, is xel vex ngenong wei laleind pyaxow en e me di wong talot me eng o.
\v 28 Yesu pekwi ma me neil wou xel bei, “Xam vex wei Yerusalem o, xam seng deeng en a ti, qe xam ghe deeng en xam venaxow de neumyeiw is.
\v 29 En bouk ti tyek nam gyeik ingwei xam a neimbei, ‘Vex wei mi mouyeeng o, vex wei se wo neu yo me vex wei se di wong luul wou neu eno xel bo xeindlala.’
\v 30 Woyom moux alis vex tyek
\q1 “‘na neil wou xel lukendu bei, “Xam qepei lek xa!”
\q1 me xel qetyei bei, “Xam sevun xa!” ’
\m 
\v 31 Gweimbeeng xomaxoneing wong nimaying ne wou ay nambei xax wei nimwis o. Om xam ghe ghok xax wei mupek o om tyek bong ambei nya wou xam loxyus?”
\p 
\v 32 Tambiy yayuw, luw xouing mi wong sewokeing, om xel qou luw me la is Yesu en xel embei na nyeis luw amey is e.
\v 33 Gyeik xel la tyip nanghei tiyon, xel mi neil embei Lukanzek, nanghei tiyon eno xel tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng, me tambiy nilul yayuw is, nge wou e mema payeiv de nge wou e mema qeinz.
\v 34 De Yesu neil embei, “Mang, wa semaleeng sewokeing wei xel o, en xel se woulek vati wei xel di wong ne.” De xel vevek di nex qakous dee me pum e xe teimb wouma.
\p 
\v 35 Xel xomaxoneing toukale me di yei e, de xel gyovaxa wo vyend wou Yesu bei, “Moxo mi vind xel ba, de wangwei e Kilisi wei Anutu beyal o, on wong e vind xow.”
\p 
\v 36 Xel vevek wong vyend wou e is ambei nyon. Xel la paviy e me wong wain senyeing wou e.
\v 37 De xel neil embei, “Wangwei wa king wei xel Yudayeiw o, ond vind xow.”
\p 
\v 38 Lek xax pepeeng pundanghou eno xel byex qayeeng bei, “INYE KING WEI YUDAYEIW O.”
\p 
\v 39 Tambiy nilul yuw wei xel teyu is Yesu, eno nge lukyak lek Yesu, “Wa Kilisi? Ond wa devind xow me uw is.”
\p 
\v 40 Ekom nilul nge neil e, “Wa seng waleeng en Anutu? En wang qalei nimaying teyei lek ambei e?
\v 41 Uw a qalei myavanei ne la teyei lek en nimaying vati wei uw a wong o. Ekom tambiy moxne se wong sewokeing ti.”
\p 
\v 42 Woyom moxo neil embei, “Yesu, wang bounaleim en ay gyeik ingwei wang nam eivek wa xe tete lalei yo.”
\p 
\v 43 Yesu lewexe wou e bei, “A neil wou wang zonghek, gweimbeeng eno tyek wang na mendei is ay eivek beyeeng nimza wei Anutu yo.”
\s1 Yesu mey
\p 
\v 44 Inye nambei seivma evlek eno mapetok ngandoung sevunexe tembuing sapa, me ela teyei lek seivma yal,
\v 45 en nambei sayeiv siing eno tip, de qaeing wei xel teyu eivek xomek vambuing eno lex ela yuw.
\p 
\v 46 Yesu taxe xoulekeing bei, “Mang, a wong axe laweeng lak eivek wa memam.” Gyeik moxo neil ambei nyon eno puw laweeng wei yus o de mey.
\p 
\v 47 Beyeiv wei xel vevek o eno yei vati wei qandi yo, me sanghoxe Anutu. Me neil embei “Zonghek ayang, tambiy tine nye bombek.”
\p 
\v 48 Gyeik xomaxoneing dalus wei qeku la toukale eno yeimend wou vatiyeiw wei qandi yo, xel laleind wo maying me qatu bambound de lox me la bend.
\v 49 Ekom Yesu xe xel gweleeng dalus, is xel vex wei betiy e me lam anghei Galili eno xel toukale kwanding me yei vatiyeiw wei qandi yo.
\s1 Xel liw Yesu eivek qakous eeng
\p 
\v 50 Tambiy ti lei Yosep, inyon kanzol wei Yudayeiw eno ti, tambiy on nimza me bombek.
\v 51 Moxo lalei se vind woueing nalei me kwa wei xel kanzol wong on. Moxo lam anghei Yudayeiw xe beyeeng nayak wei Arimatia, de moxo mindei me axe Anutu xe tete lalei.
\v 52 Yosep la wou Pailat me teling wou e en embei qou Yesu neing.
\v 53 Woyom moxo la zewax Yesu neing me qou me ouk me loum, de beliv eivek qaeing pus me qou me la liw eivek leiveeng meyeing wei xel kwelexe eivek qakous o. Xel seng ghei liw xelti eivek.
\v 54 Inyon bouk wei menyexeing wou lulul en Sabat o, de Sabat lam paviy.
\p 
\v 55 Xel vex wei lam anghei Galili is Yesu eno betiy Yosep me la yei leiveeng meyeing wei Yosep liw neing di yeip nambei nya yo.
\v 56 Woyom xel lox benbend me yeiwou lulul is wel xeimangou yo. De inyon Sabat, om xel toundei lek nambei ingwei Mose xe petieing neil o.
\c 24
\s1 Yesu qandi lek veil meyeing
\p 
\v 1 Lek bouk ti myaxeeng wei sounda tiyon satiboukeing lul, eno xel vex qou lulul wei xeimangou wei xel menyex wou yo me la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei.
\v 2 Xel yei qakous wei xel lax zeyi leiveeng meyeing eno xel tatekexe veil leiveeng meyeing mya.
\v 3 Ekom gyeik ingwei xel la lalei eno xel se yei Tambiy Ngandoung Yesu neing.
\v 4 Ka xel di wou naleind ngenong en inyon, lutika eno xel yei tambiy yayuw xe teimb on siing niseikeing nambei zivip me toukale wou xel wes.
\v 5 Xel vex yaleeng me ev vaxendkatu eivek de mend la tembuing, ekom moux yuw on neil wou xel, “Xam ghe lam di wimexe tambiy wei mapieing o eivek beyeeng wei meyeing o en va?
\v 6 Moxo se toundei inye, qe qandi lek! Xam ghe bou naleimim en qayeeng wei neil wou xam, gyeik nanghei toundei is xam eivek Galili yo.
\v 7 Neil embei, ‘Tyek xel a toung Xomaxoneing Neu Moux na eivek xel wei sewokeing o memend, en xel atuw e lek xax pepeeng de bouk yal na veil, ond tyek qandi lek no.’”
\v 8 Woyom xel wou naleind en Yesu xe qayeeng wei neil o.
\p 
\v 9 Gyeik ingwei xel loum veil leiveeng meyeing eno xel neil lulti beimambei yon wou xel betiyeing xoumeeng ti me moux alis vex dalus.
\v 10 Xel vex wei neil lulti beimambei yon wou sinaleyeiw eno inye, Maria wei Makdala yo, me Joana, me Maria wei Jems ta yo, me vex valu is xel.
\v 11 Ekom xel se wongis xel vex on, en xel xe qayeeng on wong ambei lul bandaing.
\v 12 Ekom Petele qandi lek me veimya me la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei. Dundek me yeila lalei, ekom qaeing toundei bandaing. Moxo lox me la beeng, de venaxow di wounalei bei inye vati wong ambei nye.
\s1 Moux yayuw di luk is Yesu wou sakwaing Emaus
\p 
\v 13 Lek bouk kayon eno Yesu xe xel betiyeing yayuw la beyeeng tiwei xel mi neil Emaus nei. Inyon nambei 11 kilomita nanghei Yerusalem.
\v 14 Luw di la me luk wou ma en lul sapa wei qandi natax o.
\v 15 Ka luw di luk wouma en lulul ti beimambei yon, eno Yesu venaxow la tyip me di tupwou sakwaing is luw.
\v 16 Ekom lulti wong luw se yeimend wou bei inyon Yesu.
\p 
\v 17 Moxo teling luw, “Muw ghe tupwou sakwaing eno muw ghe di luklek vati wouma me ghe lam?”
\p Luw nale me mend talex lek bei luw laleind pyaxow.
\v 18 Tambiy yuw on eno nge wei lei Kliopas, eno teling e, “Wa tambiy tixemou yon ghe la bei beyeeng amba eivek Yerusalem eno wa seng woulek vati wei qandi nanghei inyei lek bouk senghoing tine yo?”
\p 
\v 19 Yesu teling luw, “Lul vatiyeiw?”
\p Luw neil elox bei, “Uw andi luk en Yesu wei Nasaret o, moxo poropet ti, mi neil xoulek nikanzek me mi wong lulvako wou Anutu manghalus me xomaxoneing dalus mendghalus is.
\v 20 Xel lumuki leitata yo me xe xe gyovaxa toung e la eivek seyap memend me xel wong qayeeng en me neil embei e mey, om xel tuw e lek xax pepeeng,
\v 21 ekom xa di toung mami en moxo en inyon e tambiy tiwei Anutu wong e lam bei e nam a tul e xe xel Israel veil nilul o. Me lulti is no, inye bouk yal la veil en ingwei lulul tiyon dalus qandi yo.
\v 22 De gweimbeeng xel vex wei xa eno valu wong xa etek. En xel la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei satiboukeing lul,
\v 23 ekom xel se yei e neing. Xel loum neil wou xa bei, xel mend pekwi me xel yei angelayeiw wei neil embei moxo toundei mapieing.
\v 24 Woyom xel wei xa eno valu la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei, me la yei lul toundei nambei ingwei vex vex neil o. Ekom xel se yei e.”
\p 
\v 25 Yesu neil wou luw bei, “Muw ghe loung om muw naleimim se qandi lek daing me ghe wongis qayeeng dalus wei xel poropet neil o.
\v 26 Beip Kilisi se teyei bei qou myavanei beimambei ne, dekakom na qou lei ngandoung is xeiyaing?”
\v 27 Woyom neil myaxeeng wou luw en xoulek dalus wei Mose, me xel poropet o me veil luw lundlek en xoulek qes dalus wei xel neil lek e venaxow eivek xoulek o.
\p 
\v 28 Ka lal la paviy beyeeng tiwei luw embei na yo, woyom Yesu wong ambei embeim di na.
\v 29 Ekom luw neilaxoun e me neil embei, “Wa toumendei inye is uw en inye paviy soukeing, me inye embim a bouk.” Om moxo eivek la xomek lalei me la toundei is luw.
\p 
\v 30 Gyeik ingwei Yesu la dei lek lelek is luw, moxo qou belet me wong dange wou Anutu, de dembu me embei mouk bong wou luw.
\v 31 Woyom luw mend yeila me luw yeimend wou e, de moxo malang veil luw mend.
\p 
\v 32 Luw neil wouma bei, “Qayeeng wei neil eno nyuw uw laleind gyeik ingwei e di luk is uw wou sakwaing me veil uw lundlek en Anutu xe xoulek qes o.”
\p 
\v 33 De luti eno luw qandi lek me lox me la Yerusalem. Nanghei inyei eno luw yeiwou xel betiyeing xoumeeng ti is moux alis vex valu di qekuma me dei.
\v 34 Xel neil wou luw bei, “Inye zonghek ayang Tambiy Ngandoung qandi lek! Moxo talex xow wou Simon.”
\v 35 Woyom luw neil wou xel en vati wei qandi wou luw wou sakwaing o, me ingwei luw yeimend wou Yesu gyeik ingwei dembu belet o.
\s1 Yesu talex xow wou xel betiyeing
\p 
\v 36 Ka xel betiyeing nanghei di luk wouma en tine, eno Yesu venaxow lam nale eivek xel senghoing me neil wou xel, “Lalei vevopeing e mi mendei is xam.”
\p 
\v 37 Om xel etek me yaleeng en xel embeik nge xel yei meyeing ti nu.
\v 38 Moxo neil wou xel bei, “Xam ghe etek en va? Me xam laleimim wo yuw en va?
\v 39 Wei lam a memang luw xouing me a vaxang luw xouing. Inye a venaxow o! Xam axlek ay me wei. Meyeing nu eno leyeis me kanzek ma, se nambei ingwei xam ghe wei lek a ne.”
\p 
\v 40 Gyeik ingwei moxo neil ambei nye, eno talex mema luw me vaxa luw wou xel.
\v 41 Dekakom xel seng ghei wongis. En nambei xel wo xeindlala me di wou naleind ngenong, moxo teling wou xel, “Xam ghe di qou lul yaeing valu nanghei inye?”
\v 42 Xel wong woing wei nekeing eno danghei ti wou e,
\v 43 de moxo zeim me ya wou xel mendghalus.
\p 
\v 44 Moxo neil wou xel, “Inye vati wei a neil wou xam gyeik ingwei anghei toundei is xam o, lul sapa wei xel byex lek ay eivek Mose xe petieing, me xel poropet xe qapiya, me qapiya lalo, eno embo neing lek.”
\p 
\v 45 Woyom moxo veil xel lundlek bei xel boulek xoulek qes wei di yeip eivek qapiya vambuing o.
\v 46 Moxo neil wou xel bei, “Inye vati wei xel byex eivek xoulek o, Kilisi tyek na qou myavanei me na mey de qandi lek veil meyeing lek bouk yal.
\v 47 De eivek e lei eno xel a neil xoulek wou xomaxoneing wei tembuing tambak o en xel pekwi xow, me Anutu semaleeng sewokeing wei xel o. Xam ghe bong xuk tiyon nanghei Yerusalem a tax.
\v 48 Xam on ingwei xam ghe wei mamim wou lulti beimambei ne dalus woy.
\v 49 Tyek a na bong lul vati wei mang neil zonghek o wou xam, ekom xam a mi mendei eivek Yerusalem deka xam a qou nikanzek wei Anutu gheyapu yo bole.”
\s1 Yesu lek me la tyoung gheyapu nei
\p 
\v 50 Gyeik Yesu qou xel betiyeing me la beyeeng Betani nei. Moxo zeim mema luw xouing lek la de wong mata wou xel.
\v 51 Ka e di wong mata wou xel eno moxo la veil xel, de Anutu qou e me la eivek tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 52 Woyom xel wong lalo wou e, de lox me la Yerusalem is xeindlala ngandoung.
\v 53 De taxombouk eno xel mindei eivek xomek vambuing me sanghoxe Anutu.
